INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyqb8xa014std3rfzpa3qoa','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9',1265,'positive','productKnowledge','Agent clearly explained home emergency cover details including excess and claim limits','In terms of the COVID for the home emergency, it gives you 1,000 per claim. You''re allowed to make a maximum of three claims per year. I don''t think I''ve come across anyone who has exceeded that as of yet. The excesses under the home Emergency is just 50 for that side of it.',1763116954606);
