INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyqb8xa014wtd3rav8csc8t','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9',2128,'positive','closing','Agent confirmed policy active and set clear expectations for documentation','Hi there Misk. Thank you. But yeah, all fully insured from right now on that one for you. So I''ll just reconfirm your backs details. I think we had them from the other policies you might have with us.',1763116954606);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyqb8xa014xtd3rin9dpxt3','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9',2128,'positive','followUp','Agent explained renewal process and timeline clearly','And as you might be aware of the other policies, they don''t automatically renew with us so we''ll contact you about 28 days before next year. So I imagine kind of sort of early August, sorry early October next year you''ll be hearing from us with the renewal.',1763116954606);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbi000f3j6g67m4dviv','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13.',1763114604175);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbi000g3j6ga0djbrn9','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','HIGH PRIORITY: Explain cooling-off rights when customer agrees to purchase. Script: ''Just to confirm, you''ll have a 14-day cooling-off period from your policy start date. If you change your mind for any reason, you can cancel for a full refund during this time.'' Required by ICOBS 7.1.4R - this protects customers'' cancellation rights.',1763114604175);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbi000h3j6g01naby7f','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','MEDIUM PRIORITY: Provide clearer service type disclosure. You mentioned ''no advice'' but should explicitly state: ''We''re providing this on a non-advised basis, which means we''re not making a personal recommendation. You''ll need to decide if this policy meets your needs based on the information provided.'' This meets ICOBS 4.5.2R requirements.',1763114604175);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbi000i3j6gqf8bys6d','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 910): Your technical knowledge was excellent, especially explaining flood vs escape of water and identifying the flying freehold issue. To reach 10/10, proactively explain policy exclusions and limitations before the customer asks. Example: ''Just so you''re aware, this policy covers accidental damage by guests but excludes wear and tear and gradual deterioration. The 5m liability covers injury to guests but not your own injuries.''',1763114604175);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbi000j3j6g8fa09e9f','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','Path to Excellence (Closing 89): You provided clear next steps with the email quote. To reach 9/10, add a specific call-to-action and timeline. Example: ''I''ll email this quote within the next 10 minutes. It''s valid until the 10th, but if you''d like to proceed sooner, just reply to that email or call us back on this number and quote reference [REF]. Would you prefer I follow up with you tomorrow if I haven''t heard back?''',1763114604175);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbp001a3j6gj412kt7b','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. You must state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization status: ''This is Callum from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority''; (2) Call recording: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes''; (3) GDPR notice for new business: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. Our full privacy policy is available on our website.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement under ICOBS 4.5.1R.',1763114604181);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbp001b3j6gayi849cp','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always explain cooling-off rights when progressing a sale. Before ending the call, state: ''You''ll have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is your cooling-off period.'' This is mandatory under ICOBS 7.1.4R and protects customers'' cancellation rights.',1763114604181);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbp001c3j6gieqmprqi','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','HIGH PRIORITY COMPLIANCE: Provide complaints procedure information on all sales calls. State: ''If you ever need to make a complaint, you can contact us and we''ll aim to resolve it within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This is required under DISP 1.2.',1763114604181);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbp001d3j6g46f4ac4b','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','PROFESSIONALISM (scored 7/10): You handled the technical difficulties at the start adequately, but the explanation was a bit rambling. To reach 8/10, keep technical explanations brief and professional. For example: ''Apologies, we had a technical issue with the line. Thanks for your patience. Let me help you with your quotation.'' This maintains professionalism while acknowledging the issue.',1763114604181);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbp001e3j6geqw9vch2','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','NEEDS DISCOVERY (scored 7/10): You confirmed the quote details and pricing well, but didn''t explore the customer''s broader needs or circumstances. To reach 8/10, ask probing questions about their situation. For example: ''Before we finalize, can I just check - does this cover meet all your requirements? Is there anything about your circumstances that''s changed since yesterday that we should review?'' This ensures suitability and demonstrates TCF.',1763114604181);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbp001f3j6goxtzzbwe','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','FOLLOW-UP (scored 9/10): Excellent work scheduling the callback for the 27th and confirming the day of the week to avoid weekends. To reach 10/10, add a confirmation summary. For example: ''Perfect, I''ve scheduled a callback for Thursday 27th. I''ll call you that day to complete the purchase, and the price of 755.41 will still be valid. You''ll just need the deposit of 151.08 ready. Does that work for you?'' This provides complete clarity and sets clear expectations.',1763114604181);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbu00213j6gound1g38','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures. You must state: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (2) ''Pickle Insurance is authorised and regulated by the FCA'', and (3) GDPR notice: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This protects both the customer and the company legally.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbu00223j6gua4jfbed','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - scored 7/10): You did well confirming the quote details and asking if anything changed. To reach 8/10, conduct more probing discovery earlier in the call. The customer mentioned it was a ''buy to let'' property late in the conversation (7:28), which should have been explored upfront. Ask: ''Can you tell me how you''ll be using this property - will it be your main residence, a holiday home, or will you be renting it out?'' This ensures the right product from the start and demonstrates thorough needs assessment.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbu00233j6gpio2u701','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Mandatory Disclosures - scored 7/10): You did well explaining cooling-off rights, non-advised status, and FCA regulation. To reach 8/10, provide a clearer price breakdown separating premium from IPT. Instead of just ''339.02 including insurance premium tax'', say: ''The total is 339.02, which breaks down as 302.70 premium plus 36.32 insurance premium tax at 12%.'' This meets ICOBS transparency requirements more explicitly.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbu00243j6gqegweth1','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','Great rapport building with the personal comment about Moreton-in-Marsh - this humanizes the interaction. Continue using these natural moments to build trust, but ensure they don''t delay critical compliance disclosures at the call opening.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbu00253j6gj910117c','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','Excellent TCF compliance throughout - you provided clear information without pressure, obtained explicit consent for data storage, and emphasized the customer''s duty of disclosure. Your tone was helpful and transparent, which is exactly what FCA Principle 6 requires.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbz002t3j6gbbok6kud','cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. You MUST state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization, (2) Call recording notice, (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for renewals. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' This is a non-negotiable regulatory requirement.',1763114604191);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbz002u3j6glj9s4xsm','cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Professionalism - 7/10): You handled the call professionally overall and showed good customer service. To reach 8/10, improve your technical execution during data capture. When taking email addresses, use the phonetic alphabet consistently from the start (Alpha, Bravo, Charlie) rather than asking the customer to spell it multiple times. This shows confidence and efficiency. Practice: ''Can I take your email address using the phonetic alphabet please?'' This small change will make you sound more polished and save time.',1763114604191);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbz002v3j6glnmgr9z4','cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - 8/10): You maintained a friendly, conversational tone throughout and used informal language like ''Lovey jubbly'' which built good rapport. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example, when they mentioned going abroad and using farm labor, you could say: ''That sounds like a great setup - having the flexibility to travel while earning from your property. Let me make sure your cover protects you properly for that arrangement.'' This shows deeper engagement with their circumstances.',1763114604191);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbz002w3j6gkaxpdm1x','cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','Strong TCF compliance demonstrated - you respected the customer''s choice not to store card details without any pressure, clearly explained all policy features, and ensured informed consent throughout. This is excellent practice.',1763114604191);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvbz002x3j6g7u6tqvv3','cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','Good needs verification process - you systematically checked rebuild costs, contents value, and property usage. To enhance further, consider explaining WHY these figures matter: ''It''s important we get the rebuild cost right because if it''s underinsured, you might not get the full amount to rebuild in a worst-case scenario.'' This educates the customer and strengthens trust.',1763114604191);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc4003j3j6g2j0ybfv5','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance: (1) State company name and FCA authorization status, (2) Disclose call recording, (3) Provide appropriate GDPR notice for call type. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at [Company Name], authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and GDPR.',1763114604196);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc4003k3j6gmcud5i5l','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: NEVER access policy data before completing DPA verification. Always verify identity FIRST (name + DOB minimum) before discussing any policy details or allowing customer to provide property information. This is a fundamental GDPR requirement to prevent unauthorized data access.',1763114604196);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc4003l3j6g22inpwc9','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You demonstrated strong knowledge of unoccupancy rules and cover options. To reach 9/10, proactively explain the implications of each option before the customer asks. For example: ''Level 2 unoccupancy covers you for theft, malicious damage, and water damage too - which is important if pipes burst while empty. FLEE cover is cheaper but very limited. Given your husband is doing work there, I''d recommend Level 2 for peace of mind.'' This positions you as a trusted advisor.',1763114604196);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc4003m3j6gfq7pkemr','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 89): Excellent job setting immediate callback expectations. To reach 9/10, add a specific timeframe and document the action: ''I''ll call Prestige now and ring you back within the hour with the exact premium. If you don''t hear from me by [specific time], please call back on this number. I''ll also email you a summary of our discussion today.'' This adds accountability and provides written confirmation.',1763114604196);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc4003n3j6gix23nahd','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','Consider providing written confirmation of MTA changes via email immediately after the call to ensure customer has documentation of the policy change and new cover level',1763114604196);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc8004b3j6gqiyq3a1t','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Always open calls with required disclosures. You MUST state: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (2) ''We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', and (3) For existing customer service calls, acknowledge ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable under FCA and GDPR requirements. Practice this opening script until it becomes automatic.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc8004c3j6g3j1y95c2','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','Path to Excellence (Mandatory Disclosures - 7/108/10): You did an excellent job reading the comprehensive disclosure script mid-call, covering FCA status, non-advised basis, cancellation rights, IPT, and duty of disclosure. To reach 8/10, integrate the complaints procedure more explicitly by stating: ''If you wish to make a complaint, please contact us and we''ll provide our complaints procedure. If we can''t resolve it within 8 weeks, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' This ensures full DISP compliance.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc8004d3j6gy1ag03ij','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','Path to Excellence (Data Protection - 8/109/10): Great work conducting thorough DPA verification before accessing policy details - you checked address, postcode, and date of birth. To reach 9/10, verbally confirm the verification outcome to the customer: ''Thank you, I''ve now verified your identity and can access your policy details.'' This provides transparency and reassurance to the customer about data security.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc8004e3j6g4f5v3o4n','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery - 8/109/10): Excellent questioning about tenancy type, number of adults, unoccupancy, and business use - you covered all key underwriting criteria. To reach 9/10, add a summary confirmation: ''Just to confirm, you''re changing from short-term letting to a long-term let with 2 professional tenants, with a tenancy agreement in place, and the property won''t be empty for more than 30 days. Is that correct?'' This ensures mutual understanding and reduces errors.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvc8004f3j6gxo4iqj2r','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','Consider providing a breakdown of the 79.33 amendment fee (e.g., ''That''s X for the policy change, plus Y admin fee, plus Z IPT'') to enhance pricing transparency, even though the customer didn''t request it. This demonstrates TCF best practice.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcc00533j6gedmui975','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You MUST open every call with: (1) Company name and regulatory status: ''This is [Your Name] from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy''. This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance. Practice this opening until it becomes automatic.',1763114604204);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcc00543j6ge7tfdtcm','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','CRITICAL - Mandatory Disclosures: When processing cancellations, you must inform customers of their complaints rights. Say: ''If you''re unhappy with any aspect of our service, you can make a complaint. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied, you can refer the matter to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This is required by DISP 1.2.',1763114604204);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcc00553j6gsl752up6','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','Product Knowledge (scored 7/10): You demonstrated good understanding of the cancellation process but showed uncertainty with phrases like ''I think'' twice when explaining the refund calculation. To reach 8/10, ensure you''re confident about cancellation fee offsetting rules before the call. Practice saying: ''Your refund is 5, but there''s a 20 cancellation fee, so these will offset each other and no refund will be due.'' This sounds more professional and confident.',1763114604204);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcc00563j6g4epxv2oj','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','Professionalism (scored 7/10): Your rapport was excellent, but the uncertainty about needing card details (''Actually, I might need your card number'') showed poor planning. To reach 8/10, check system requirements before mentioning payment details to customers. This avoids confusion and presents a more organized service. Your friendly tone was great - maintain that while adding better preparation.',1763114604204);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcc00573j6g2jmxdwi6','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','Follow-Up (scored 8/10): Great job confirming the email follow-up within 5 minutes and explaining the refund position clearly. To reach 9/10, add a specific timeline for when the cancellation will be effective in the system. For example: ''The cancellation will be processed today and take effect immediately. You''ll receive email confirmation within 5 minutes, and the policy will show as cancelled on our system within 24 hours.''',1763114604204);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcg005s3j6gpzb59qb2','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Always open calls with full compliance elements. You MUST state: (1) Company name and regulatory status: ''You''re through to Callum at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (3) GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy''. This is non-negotiable and required by FCA regulations.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcg005t3j6gtr5v4nfj','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: NEVER access or discuss policy/claim information before completing DPA verification. Before discussing the claim, you must verify identity by asking: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only after successful verification can you access customer records. This is a fundamental GDPR requirement - accessing data without verification is a serious breach.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcg005u3j6ggomoi4m7','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 8/10): You established good rapport through your helpful and honest communication style. To reach 9/10, add more empathy statements acknowledging the customer''s situation. For example: ''I understand you need these documents urgently to process the claim - let me make sure I get these to you as quickly as possible.'' This shows you understand the impact on their work.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcg005v3j6gloumsl39','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 8/10): You provided clear timeframes for document delivery which was excellent. To reach 9/10, proactively offer a backup plan. For example: ''I''ll aim to get these to you before 5pm today. If there''s any delay, I''ll email you by 4pm to update you, so you''re not left waiting. Does that work for you?'' This demonstrates ownership and reliability.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcg005w3j6ggumngq43','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 8/10): You correctly identified the policy scope and limitations. To reach 9/10, proactively explain why the information matters to the customer''s process. For example: ''Because he only has the hosting top-up with us, you''ll need his main buildings insurance details as that''s where the structural damage claim would sit. Our top-up covers additional hosting-specific risks.'' This adds educational value.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcj006g3j6gl8ljd0d5','cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance: (1) State firm name clearly: ''You''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance'', (2) Regulatory status: ''We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (3) Call recording: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes'', (4) For existing customer service calls, brief GDPR acknowledgment: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a mandatory FCA requirement under ICOBS 4.5.1R.',1763114604212);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcj006h3j6g9tr28yoi','cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','PROFESSIONALISM - Path to Excellence (78): You handled the call professionally after the opening. To reach 8/10, ensure your greeting is clear and professional from the first word. Replace ''Are you fried?'' with a clear, confident opening: ''Good morning/afternoon, you''re through to Callum at Pikl Insurance, how can I help you today?'' This sets a professional tone immediately.',1763114604212);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcj006i3j6gcahcjvbx','cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','RAPPORT - Path to Excellence (89): You built good rapport by mentioning you were about to call the customer (''I was going to try and ring you in about 15 minutes''). To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of their situation. For example: ''I''m really glad you called - I know waiting for refunds can be frustrating, so let me get this sorted for you straight away.'' This shows empathy and urgency.',1763114604212);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcj006j3j6g9eziv1n2','cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','Excellent DPA verification process - you completed full security checks (address, postcode, DOB) before accessing any policy information. Continue this best practice on every call.',1763114604212);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcj006k3j6gcmgvset2','cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','Strong TCF compliance demonstrated by setting realistic expectations about refund timing and explaining the process transparently. Your honesty about bank processing times (3-5 working days) shows good customer treatment.',1763114604212);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcn006v3j6g6bgba2rd','cmhyowvcl006r3j6gvnjrps9m','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): You maintained a professional and collaborative tone throughout. To reach 9/10, try building even stronger rapport by acknowledging the broker''s diligence in checking the claim details. For example: ''Thanks for being so thorough in checking this, Callum - it''s really helpful when brokers verify these details with us upfront.''',1763114604215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcn006w3j6g2u7alhm8','cmhyowvcl006r3j6gvnjrps9m','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You demonstrated solid understanding of the policy structure and coverage hierarchy. To reach 9/10, provide more specific policy clause references when explaining coverage. For example: ''Under the Premier product terms, accidental damage to glass is typically covered under the main policy first, and the top-up only responds when the main policy limit is exhausted.''',1763114604215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcn006x3j6ghenevh4j','cmhyowvcl006r3j6gvnjrps9m','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 89): You agreed on clear next steps with the broker. To reach 9/10, be more specific about timelines and confirm documentation. For example: ''I''ll add a note to the claim file today and speak with Mark by end of business. I''ll email you his feedback by tomorrow afternoon. Does that work for you?''',1763114604215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcn006y3j6gnkgeq8k9','cmhyowvcl006r3j6gvnjrps9m','Consider documenting the specific policy clause references during the call to provide more authoritative guidance to brokers and ensure consistent advice across the team.',1763114604215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcq007l3j6gu9unesby','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You must open every call with: (1) Firm identification: ''You''re through to Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (3) GDPR notice for new business: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604218);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcq007m3j6gzht57bcm','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','CRITICAL - DPA Verification: Always verify customer identity (name + date of birth minimum) BEFORE collecting any personal data or discussing policy details. You collected address, postcode, and email at 1:50-2:27 but didn''t verify DOB until 18:30. This is a serious GDPR breach. Script: ''Before we proceed, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?''',1763114604218);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcq007n3j6g55vg4qsr','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','HIGH PRIORITY - Mandatory Disclosures: You missed three critical disclosures: (1) 14-day cooling-off rights: ''You have 14 days from policy start to cancel for a full refund'', (2) Price breakdown: Separate premium, IPT, and fees, (3) Complaints procedure: ''If you''re unhappy, we have a complaints process. You can also contact the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' Add these to your sales checklist.',1763114604218);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcq007o3j6g8fpojcdr','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','Objection Handling - Path to Excellence (78): You acknowledged the price objection but didn''t explore the value difference. To reach 8/10, ask: ''I understand price is important. Can I ask - does that 403 quote include the specialist holiday let hosting cover and 5m liability? Our quote includes comprehensive guest protection that standard policies don''t offer.'' This helps customer make an informed comparison rather than price-only decision.',1763114604218);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcq007p3j6gdo86o8qv','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','Follow-Up - Path to Excellence (67): You mentioned emailing the quote at 2:16 but never confirmed this at call end. To reach 7/10, always close with: ''Sarah, I''ll email that quote to you within the next hour at [email]. If you have any questions or want to proceed, just call us back on [number]. Does that work for you?'' This sets clear expectations and provides a path forward.',1763114604218);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcu008k3j6g1cfvsk96','cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with call recording disclosure. Script: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to Will at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This is essential for GDPR compliance and protects both the customer and the firm.',1763114604223);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcu008l3j6gc9v2lg14','cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 89): You built good rapport by being friendly and patient, especially when explaining the guest cover options. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''That''s great that you''re expanding your hosting business, Susan. I can see you''re being really thoughtful about getting the right cover in place before you start - that''s exactly the right approach.'' This shows you''re invested in their success.',1763114604223);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcu008m3j6g46c5smsa','cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery - 89): Excellent work identifying the discrepancy with the number of adults and exploring the hosting plans. To reach 9/10, consider asking one additional probing question about their hosting business plans: ''How many weeks per year do you typically host guests in the annex? This helps me ensure the 40-night limit on the guest cover will be sufficient for you.'' This demonstrates deeper needs analysis.',1763114604223);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcu008n3j6g50t3dpf0','cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 89): Strong explanation of blanket cover, excesses, and the difference between all-in-one and top-up policies. To reach 9/10, when explaining complex features like blanket cover, add a brief customer benefit statement: ''This blanket cover is actually better for you because even though we''ve set your rebuild cost at 510k, if it turned out to cost more, you''d still be covered up to the full million.'' This translates features into tangible benefits.',1763114604223);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcu008o3j6g98qba273','cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 89): Good job setting expectations for documents and next year''s renewal. To reach 9/10, add a proactive service touchpoint: ''I''ll also send you a quick email with the link to purchase that additional guest cover when you''re ready, along with my direct number if you have any questions when you review your documents.'' This provides additional value and accessibility.',1763114604223);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcy009a3j6g3ilec15e','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with required disclosures. You must state: (1) Call recording notice: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', and (2) GDPR notice for new business: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcy009b3j6genrmhyyn','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 89): You built good rapport by referencing the previous conversation with Rebecca and using the customer''s name throughout. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. For example: ''It''s great that you''re getting your short-stay hosting properly covered, Ian. That shows real professionalism in how you run your business.'' This creates stronger connection.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcy009c3j6g7rkg4rqa','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 910): Excellent explanation of Prestige cover limits, excesses, and exclusions. To reach 10/10, consider adding a brief benefit statement that ties features to customer needs. For example: ''The blanket cover is particularly good for hosts like yourself because it means you don''t need to worry about declaring exact rebuild costs - you''re covered up to a million automatically.'' This demonstrates mastery.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcy009d3j6gqblzt9eh','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','Path to Excellence (Mandatory Disclosures - 78): You covered most required disclosures well, including cooling-off rights, FCA authorization, and duty of disclosure. However, you didn''t explicitly mention IPT breakdown (just said ''inclusive of IPT''). To reach 8/10, state: ''Your total premium is 767.14, which includes Insurance Premium Tax at 12%.'' This ensures complete price transparency.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvcy009e3j6gf4l5geoe','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','Path to Excellence (Sales Process - 89): Strong sales process with needs confirmation, product summary, and clear pricing. To reach 9/10, add a brief suitability statement before closing. For example: ''Based on what you''ve told us about your main home and short-stay hosting, this Prestige policy provides the comprehensive cover you need for both your personal use and paying guests.'' This reinforces product fit.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvd900bf3j6gwsynuh5y','cmhyowvd800b33j6g6yqku7vc','CRITICAL: Always provide call recording disclosure at the start of every call. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement and must never be omitted (ICOBS 2.2.3R).',1763114604237);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvd900bg3j6guv6wc8np','cmhyowvd800b33j6g6yqku7vc','Path to Excellence (Call Opening 48): You handled the rest of the call well, but the opening needs immediate attention. To reach compliance standard: (1) State company name clearly, (2) Add ''This call is being recorded'', (3) For renewals, briefly acknowledge data already held: ''As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' Practice this opening until it becomes automatic.',1763114604237);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvd900bh3j6gcofintkv','cmhyowvd800b33j6g6yqku7vc','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): You did well using the customer''s name and maintaining a friendly tone throughout. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. For example, when discussing the holiday let: ''It sounds like you''ve had a good year with the property if there haven''t been any claims - that''s great to hear.'' This shows you''re engaged with their individual circumstances.',1763114604237);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvd900bi3j6g12m28pb2','cmhyowvd800b33j6g6yqku7vc','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You explained contents cover limitations clearly when asked. To elevate to 9/10, proactively suggest considerations: ''While there''s not much in the property now, you might want to think about contents cover if you add furniture or appliances for guests in future. We can always add it mid-term if needed.'' This demonstrates forward-thinking advice.',1763114604237);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvd900bj3j6gha3x7i66','cmhyowvd800b33j6g6yqku7vc','Excellent work on the comprehensive regulatory disclosures mid-call - you covered FCA authorization, cancellation rights, complaints procedure, non-advised status, IPT, and duty of disclosure. This demonstrates strong compliance knowledge. Ensure this same thoroughness applies to the call opening.',1763114604237);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdf00c63j6gqjkfizvd','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. Must state: ''Good afternoon, Will speaking from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdf00c73j6g9d0lhtbu','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','OBJECTION HANDLING (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: You handled the pricing objection honestly, which is great. To reach 8/10, after explaining broker limitations, reinforce the value proposition: ''While we can''t discount the premium, what you''re getting is specialist cover that standard insurers won''t provide, plus our panel of insurers all understand home swapping, so you won''t face issues at claims time.'' This turns the objection into a value statement.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdf00c83j6gug16jd3h','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','CLOSING (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: You provided helpful information and the customer was satisfied. To reach 8/10, always confirm next steps before closing: ''So just to confirm, you''re going to contact Home Protect, and if they can''t help or you''d like to proceed with our quote, you can call us back on [number] or complete the purchase online. Does that work for you?'' This ensures clarity and keeps the door open.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdf00c93j6gmikqfztn','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','FOLLOW-UP (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: Good job offering competitor information. To reach 8/10, set a specific follow-up action: ''I''ll send you a summary email with Home Protect''s details and our insurer panel list. If you don''t hear back from them within a few days, feel free to call me directly.'' This shows proactive service.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdf00ca3j6gnhj8vpam','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','MANDATORY DISCLOSURES (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: You explained broker status well. To reach 8/10, briefly mention remuneration: ''As a broker, we receive commission from the insurer when you purchase, but this doesn''t affect your premium - it''s already included in the price.'' This meets ICOBS transparency requirements.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdi00cq3j6g6tg9ntgz','cmhyowvdh00cj3j6g2z7msudv','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: You must open every call with: (1) Full firm identification including regulatory status (''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA''), (2) Call recording disclosure (''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes''), and (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for existing customers (''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy''). This is mandatory under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13. Practice this opening until it becomes automatic.',1763114604246);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdi00cr3j6g25y4hora','cmhyowvdh00cj3j6g2z7msudv','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 8/10): You built good rapport by being friendly, using the customer''s name, and showing patience. To reach 9/10, add more personalized empathy statements that acknowledge the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I completely understand your concern, Eloise - receiving those letters can be worrying. Let me put your mind at ease by checking this thoroughly for you.'' This shows deeper emotional connection.',1763114604246);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdi00cs3j6g6elkpolb','cmhyowvdh00cj3j6g2z7msudv','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery - 8/10): You asked appropriate clarifying questions about the payment method and timing. To reach 9/10, probe slightly deeper when customers mention concerns. For example: ''You mentioned you received both an email and a letter - have you made a payment since receiving those, or were you expecting them to be automatically collected?'' This ensures complete understanding before investigating.',1763114604246);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdi00ct3j6g9l0dr17v','cmhyowvdh00cj3j6g2z7msudv','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 8/10): You confirmed the account was clear and the customer was satisfied. To reach 9/10, proactively set expectations for future communications. For example: ''Just so you know, Eloise, you can disregard those letters as they crossed with your payment. Your next statement will show everything is up to date. If you receive any further correspondence that concerns you, please don''t hesitate to call us back.'' This prevents future anxiety.',1763114604246);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdi00cu3j6gore8jqpi','cmhyowvdh00cj3j6g2z7msudv','Consider documenting this interaction on the customer''s account notes, including that you explained the letters were generated before payment cleared. This creates an audit trail and helps any future agent who speaks with this customer.',1763114604246);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdl00di3j6gtdp7qmn8','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures: ''Good afternoon, Pikl Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. How can I help?'' This is mandatory under FCA requirements and protects both the customer and the firm.',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdl00dj3j6gwlzk9sjn','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','COMPLIANCE - Credit Disclosure: When discussing monthly payment options, provide clear Consumer Credit Act disclosures including total amount payable, APR, and number of instalments. For example: ''If you pay monthly at 37% APR over 12 months, your total cost would be X, which is Y more than paying annually. Would you like me to email you the full credit agreement terms?''',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdl00dk3j6gqwtl19zs','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 8/10): You built good rapport by acknowledging the previous conversation and showing willingness to help. To reach 9/10, add more personalized empathy statements. For example: ''I can see you''re trying to balance getting comprehensive cover for your Airbnb business while keeping costs manageable - that''s completely understandable. Let me work through all the options with you to find the best solution.''',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdl00dl3j6guc0ytfl5','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 8/10): You demonstrated solid knowledge of excess options and policy features. To reach 9/10, proactively explain the trade-offs when presenting options. For example: ''Increasing your excess to 350 saves you 100 annually. Based on your claim history of one 800 claim in 20 years, this could be cost-effective, but it means you''d pay the first 350 of any future claim. What feels right for your situation?''',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdl00dm3j6gi0s0ereg','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 8/10): You provided clear next steps and multiple contact options. To reach 9/10, add a specific timeframe and confirm understanding. For example: ''I''ll email this updated quote within 10 minutes with the monthly payment breakdown. The quote is valid for 30 days. Shall I give you a call back tomorrow afternoon to discuss, or would you prefer to review it and contact us when ready?''',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ec3j6gbhib8ljh','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP - Call Opening: Must include call recording disclosure at start of every call. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' Also state: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement under PRIN and SM&CR. (Current score: 5/10  Target: 10/10)',1763114604253);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ed3j6g3fopyj1q','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','HIGH PRIORITY - GDPR Privacy Notice: Enhance data protection disclosure to include customer rights. Add: ''You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. We retain your information for [X years] in line with regulatory requirements. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This completes GDPR Article 13 requirements. (Current score: 9/10 dataProtectionCompliance  Target: 10/10)',1763114604253);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ee3j6gcwrk3der','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','HIGH PRIORITY - Mandatory Disclosures: When policy proceeds to sale, must explain: (1) 14-day cooling-off rights per ICOBS 7.1.4R, (2) Price breakdown showing premium + IPT + fees separately, (3) Complaints procedure and FOS rights. Create a checklist to ensure all disclosures are covered before completing sale. (Current score: 5/10 mandatoryDisclosures  Target: 9/10)',1763114604253);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ef3j6g8i2ld6bs','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','Path to Excellence - Needs Discovery (89): You conducted excellent eligibility screening with clear yes/no questions. To reach 9/10, add more exploratory questions about the customer''s specific hosting plans and concerns. Example: ''Tell me more about your hosting plans - how many nights per year are you expecting to let? This helps me ensure we have the right level of cover for your needs.'' This demonstrates deeper customer-centricity.',1763114604253);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdp00eg3j6g1gozmuad','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','Path to Excellence - Product Knowledge (89): You handled the complex construction situation well by recognizing the need to consult the insurer. To reach 9/10, proactively explain the implications: ''Because the annex is still under construction, the insurer may need to apply different terms or exclude it until completion. Let me check exactly what cover we can provide now versus after the roof is finished.'' This shows expert-level knowledge application.',1763114604253);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdp00eh3j6gnrfw55xn','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','Excellent professionalism throughout - you maintained composure with a complex, evolving property situation and avoided making assumptions. Your approach of ''check first, then advise'' demonstrates strong TCF principles. Keep this customer-first mindset in all interactions.',1763114604253);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdx00f63j6g9m4cl58w','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance (scored 3/10): Must provide mandatory call opening disclosures. At the start of EVERY call, state: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement under ICOBS and GDPR. Path to 8/10: Implement a scripted opening that includes all required elements consistently.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdx00f73j6gms44koj5','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','CRITICAL - Mandatory Disclosures (scored 4/10): Must explain cooling-off rights for new business sales. When providing a quote, state: ''If you decide to proceed, you''ll have a 14-day cooling-off period from your policy start date. This means you can cancel for a full refund if you change your mind.'' Also explain complaints procedure: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint which we''ll respond to within 8 weeks. You also have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' Path to 8/10: Create a checklist of mandatory disclosures and confirm each one is covered before ending sales calls.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdx00f83j6gjs99n7og','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','Sales Process Compliance (scored 6/10): Good job conducting eligibility questions and explaining product structure. To reach 8/10, strengthen the needs assessment by documenting why this specific product meets the customer''s needs. For example: ''Based on what you''ve told me about renting through Sykes and needing guest liability cover, this dual policy structure with contents plus guest top-up is designed specifically for your situation because...'' This demonstrates clear suitability assessment required under IDD.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdx00f93j6gwyrurb4g','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','Needs Discovery (scored 7/10): You did well asking clarifying questions about the property structure and caravan details. To reach 8/10, probe deeper into the customer''s specific concerns and priorities earlier in the call. For example, after learning about the Sykes rental, ask: ''What are your main concerns about insuring this property - is it protecting your contents, liability for guests, or damage to the caravan itself?'' This helps tailor your explanation more effectively.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvdx00fa3j6gs06y6vm1','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','Follow-Up (scored 7/10): Good job explaining the customer can call back or email. To reach 8/10, be more specific about next steps and timelines. For example: ''I''ve sent the quote to your email. Please review the policy wording tonight, and if you''d like to proceed before your guests arrive Saturday, give us a call by 5pm tomorrow so we can get your cover in place. Do you have any questions about what to look for in the documents?'' This creates clearer expectations and urgency.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve500gr3j6glzjj6c9j','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','CRITICAL - DPA Verification: You MUST verify customer identity (name + DOB minimum) BEFORE discussing any policy details or pricing. This is a fundamental GDPR requirement. Score: 0/10. What the law requires: GDPR Article 5 and DPA 2018 require verification before accessing personal data. What to say: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Why it matters: This prevents unauthorized access to customer data.',1763114604269);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve500gs3j6g8kb7tbx1','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: Your call opening missed all mandatory elements. Score: 3/10. You must state: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (2) ''Pickle Insurance is authorized and regulated by the FCA'', and (3) For renewals, acknowledge data held: ''As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' Practice this opening until it becomes automatic.',1763114604269);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve500gt3j6gxn12hy0z','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','Objection Handling - Price Increase: Score 5/10. You acknowledged the price increase but didn''t explore solutions. Path to 8/10: (1) Show empathy: ''I completely understand your frustration with a 30% increase, especially with no claims'', (2) Explore options: ''Let me review your cover to see if we can adjust your excess or coverage to bring the price down'', (3) Demonstrate value: ''Let me also check if there are any discounts you might qualify for.'' This shows you''re working FOR the customer, not just defending the price.',1763114604269);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve500gu3j6gbktie0sb','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','Needs Discovery & Retention: Score 6/10. You mentioned checking details but didn''t actually do it. Path to 8/10: Ask probing questions: ''When did you last review your sums insured? Property values have increased significantly. Let me verify your rebuild cost is accurate - you might be over-insured.'' Then: ''Have you added any home improvements? Sometimes we can find savings by updating your profile.'' This demonstrates expertise and creates retention opportunities.',1763114604269);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve500gv3j6gxn6ecw0k','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','TCF & Customer Outcomes: Score 6/10. You gave up too easily when the customer said they''d look elsewhere. Path to 8/10: ''Before you go, I''d really like to help. Can I take 2 minutes to review your policy? I want to make sure you''re comparing like-for-like cover. Some cheaper policies exclude things like accidental damage or have much higher excesses. Let me also check our panel one more time - sometimes prices update.'' This shows you''re putting the customer''s interests first.',1763114604269);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve800hm3j6gp5qcu56k','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance elements. For new business sales, you MUST state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization status: ''This is [Name] calling from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority''; (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes''; (3) GDPR privacy notice: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve800hn3j6gnsf3gq5z','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always explain cooling-off rights for new business sales. After taking payment, state: ''You have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period, and you''ll find full details in your policy documents.'' This is required by ICOBS 7.1.4R and protects customers'' cancellation rights.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve800ho3j6gomw83xb5','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always provide complaints procedure information. Before ending the call, state: ''If you ever need to make a complaint, you can contact us and we''ll provide our complaints procedure. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service within 6 months.'' This is required by DISP 1.2 and ensures customers know their rights.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve800hp3j6g8g8xz850','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','Path to Excellence (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built excellent rapport by recognizing the customer''s number and maintaining a warm, conversational tone throughout. To reach 9/10, incorporate more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. For example: ''I''m glad we could get this sorted for you today, Patrick. With your policy starting on the 17th, you''ll have complete peace of mind for your new property.'' This creates a stronger emotional connection.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowve800hq3j6gxr6v7z97','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','Path to Excellence (Sales Process - currently 6/10): You handled the payment process smoothly and confirmed key details. To reach 8/10, conduct a more thorough needs assessment even on continuation calls. Ask: ''Before we finalize, can I just confirm - is there anything about your circumstances that''s changed since we last spoke that might affect your cover needs?'' This ensures suitability and demonstrates TCF compliance.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowved00ic3j6gsogpxl7d','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','CRITICAL - Call Recording Disclosure: You MUST state call recording disclosure at the start of EVERY call. Immediately after greeting, say: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement. Practice this until it becomes automatic in your opening script.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowved00id3j6g92qsft7t','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','CRITICAL - DPA Verification Sequence: NEVER collect policy reference or access any policy data before completing DPA verification. Correct sequence: (1) Greeting + call recording disclosure, (2) Ask for full name AND date of birth, (3) THEN ask for policy reference. Say: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' This protects both the customer and the company from data breaches.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowved00ie3j6gzy55241r','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','FCA Regulatory Status: Add FCA authorization to your greeting. Say: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Rebecca speaking, how can I help?'' This meets ICOBS requirements and builds customer confidence.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowved00if3j6gyoowabjy','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','GDPR Privacy Notice for Renewals: For renewal calls, include a brief acknowledgment: ''As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This shows compliance without requiring the full GDPR notice needed for new business.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowved00ig3j6gyxqf6nj1','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','Path to Excellence - Rapport (89): You did well using positive language (''Perfect. Lovely'') and thanking the customer. To reach 9/10, personalize the interaction more. For example: ''Thank you Mr Pattison, I can see your renewal is coming up. Let me find the best person to review your buildings and contents cover with you and make sure everything still meets your needs.'' This shows you''re focused on their specific situation.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvei00j63j6ghh9hw5er','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with firm identification, regulatory status, and call recording disclosure. Script: ''Good morning, this is Rebecca calling from [Company Name], authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a mandatory FCA requirement under ICOBS 4.5.1R.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvei00j73j6gi99679o6','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','HIGH PRIORITY: Provide complaints procedure at end of all calls, especially cancellations. Script: ''If you have any concerns about our service, please contact our complaints team. If we can''t resolve it within 8 weeks, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This is required by DISP 1.2.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvei00j83j6gvzzofqrz','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','Path to Excellence (Data Protection - currently 10/10): Excellent DPA verification process. You verified identity BEFORE accessing any policy data, which is perfect compliance. Continue this standard on every call.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvei00j93j6g6c3djr0a','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','Path to Excellence (TCF - currently 9/10): Great job explaining refund process clearly and proactively offering to calculate the amount. To reach 10/10, consider acknowledging any potential customer concern about charges upfront: ''I want to be transparent - there''s a 20 cancellation charge, but let me calculate your full refund so you know exactly what to expect.'' This builds even stronger trust.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvei00ja3j6gj178uue1','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery - currently 8/10): Good questioning about cancellation reason and claims. To reach 9/10, explore whether customer needs alternative cover: ''I understand you''re cancelling. Just to make sure you''re protected - do you have alternative insurance arranged, or would you like information about other options?'' This ensures customer isn''t left uninsured.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvel00jy3j6gb0wsvo1n','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You MUST open every call with: (1) Firm name and regulatory status: ''You''re through to Callum at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (3) Brief GDPR notice for existing customers: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy''. This is non-negotiable regulatory requirement.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvel00jz3j6gy1i20wl0','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','CRITICAL - Mandatory Disclosures: When making mid-term adjustments that change cover, you must explain: (1) Clear price breakdown (premium + IPT separately), (2) Cooling-off rights if material change: ''You have 14 days to cancel this change if you''re not satisfied'', (3) Complaints procedure: ''If you''re unhappy, contact us first. If unresolved after 8 weeks, you can refer to the Financial Ombudsman Service''. Script example: ''The additional premium is 59.70, which includes X premium and X Insurance Premium Tax. You have 14 days to cancel this change for a pro-rata refund.''',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvel00k03j6g85c6itup','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','Product Knowledge (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: You demonstrated good use of the RICS calculator and understood fixtures/fittings coverage. To reach 8/10, eliminate hesitation about product eligibility. Before the call, review notes from previous advisors (Rebecca''s note was there) so you can confidently confirm ''Yes, we can add buildings insurance for fixtures and fittings'' without needing to check. This builds customer confidence immediately.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvel00k13j6gdc0o4psy','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','Closing Techniques (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: You appropriately didn''t pressure the customer and agreed to send details by email. To reach 8/10, provide a clearer action plan: ''I''ll email you the full quote and policy summary within 20 minutes. Please review the policy wording section on pages X-Y which covers your specific concerns about leaks and damage. If you''re happy to proceed, you can call us back on [number] or reply to the email, and we''ll process this immediately. The price is guaranteed until [time] today.'' This gives the customer clear next steps and urgency without pressure.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvel00k23j6g4vg0aiij','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','Sales Process Compliance (scored 6/10) - Path to 8/10: You conducted good needs discovery and explained the product. To reach 8/10, ensure you: (1) Explicitly confirm suitability: ''Based on what you''ve told me about the 500 freeholder excess, this buildings cover for fixtures and fittings meets your need for more affordable protection'', (2) Confirm what documents you''re sending: ''I''ll email you the quote summary, policy wording, and Insurance Product Information Document'', (3) Explain the cover scope clearly: ''This covers the structure of your flat - walls, ceilings, doors, fitted kitchen, bathroom - but not the building''s external structure, which remains the freeholder''s responsibility.''',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowves00lg3j6g3hjijnva','cmhyowver00l33j6g4nw0o2rl','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance elements: (1) Firm name and FCA authorization status: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Jessup Pickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority''; (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes''; (3) GDPR notice appropriate to call type. This is a fundamental FCA requirement under PRIN 2A.5.1R and ICOBS 2.2.2R. Score: 0/10  Target: 10/10',1763114604293);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowves00lh3j6gxo69c23s','cmhyowver00l33j6g4nw0o2rl','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge 78): You handled the payment investigation well and resolved the customer''s confusion. To reach 8/10, improve your initial confidence when discussing payment systems. Instead of ''I don''t think we''d know any longer. Have those monthly instalments'', say: ''Let me check your payment details for you. Your monthly payments are managed by our partner Premfina, and I can access your payment schedule now.'' This demonstrates immediate competence and reduces customer anxiety.',1763114604293);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowves00li3j6gkb95f61j','cmhyowver00l33j6g4nw0o2rl','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport 89): You built good rapport with phrases like ''that''s not to worry at all'' and showed patience during holds. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''re managing multiple properties with hosting - that''s quite an undertaking! Let me make sure we have everything properly covered for you.'' This shows you understand their broader context.',1763114604293);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowves00lj3j6gbb6lj933','cmhyowver00l33j6g4nw0o2rl','Reduce hold times and system delays: Customer was placed on hold twice for extended periods (3m50s and 3m43s). Prepare key information before placing customers on hold, and if delays are unavoidable, offer callbacks: ''This investigation may take a few minutes - would you prefer I call you back once I have all the details?''',1763114604293);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowves00lk3j6glb1ocztf','cmhyowver00l33j6g4nw0o2rl','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up 89): You clearly explained the transfer to quotes team and set time expectations (25-30 minutes). To reach 9/10, add a summary of what information the quotes team will need: ''The quotes team will need details about your property at 4 South Street - the rebuild value, security features, and your hosting plans. Having these ready will help speed things up. I''ll transfer you now.''',1763114604293);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvev00lz3j6g40weoq4l','cmhyowveu00lr3j6gq3xp4jlq','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: This was a voicemail, not an actual call. When a live conversation occurs, ensure all call opening compliance requirements are met: firm identification with regulatory status (''Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA''), call recording disclosure, and appropriate GDPR notice for the call type.',1763114604296);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvev00m03j6gpgc6jyf0','cmhyowveu00lr3j6gq3xp4jlq','Excellent voicemail technique demonstrated - clear identification, purpose stated, follow-up plan communicated, and callback details provided. This is the expected standard for voicemail messages (8/10). To reach 9/10, consider adding a brief value statement, such as: ''I have some competitive quotes ready to discuss that could save you money on your insurance.''',1763114604296);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvev00m13j6glq5hvf84','cmhyowveu00lr3j6gq3xp4jlq','When leaving voicemails for quote follow-ups, consider mentioning any time-sensitive elements (e.g., ''Your quote is valid for 30 days'') to create appropriate urgency without pressure selling.',1763114604296);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvev00m23j6gujja468h','cmhyowveu00lr3j6gq3xp4jlq','Ensure the callback number is stated slowly and clearly - consider repeating it twice to ensure the customer can note it down accurately.',1763114604296);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf000mi3j6glddthjwp','cmhyowvez00m93j6g839950w9','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: This was a voicemail message, not a live call. No compliance assessment is possible as there was no customer interaction. Scores of 8/10 reflect ''not applicable'' rather than performance evaluation.',1763114604300);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf000mj3j6g1dzi08a9','cmhyowvez00m93j6g839950w9','For future voicemail messages: Consider mentioning the quote reference number or policy type to help the customer recall the specific quote being discussed.',1763114604300);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf000mk3j6gpvdumxns','cmhyowvez00m93j6g839950w9','Voicemail best practice: The message was clear and professional. Continue providing callback number and availability hours as demonstrated here.',1763114604300);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf000ml3j6g1p1vssnk','cmhyowvez00m93j6g839950w9','When customer returns the call, ensure full call opening compliance is delivered including: firm identification with regulatory status, call recording disclosure, and appropriate GDPR notice for the call type.',1763114604300);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf300n23j6gzja01qya','cmhyowvf200ms3j6gzuuq85za','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE NOTE: This call cannot be properly assessed for compliance as it is a voicemail message left by an agent (Rebecca from Pickle Insurance) on a customer''s (Megan''s) voicemail system. The voicemail greeting is Megan''s personal message, not an agent interaction. Standard call opening compliance requirements (FCA authorization statement, call recording disclosure, GDPR notice) do not apply to outbound voicemail messages.',1763114604303);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf300n33j6gbv8zzrgn','cmhyowvf200ms3j6gzuuq85za','POSITIVE: Rebecca demonstrates excellent follow-up discipline by using multiple channels (phone call + email) to chase outstanding documentation. This shows good customer service and process management.',1763114604303);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf300n43j6g8q7v6nj3','cmhyowvf200ms3j6gzuuq85za','POSITIVE: The message is clear, professional, and provides all necessary information (reason for call, next steps, contact number). Rebecca appropriately creates urgency (''as soon as possible'') without applying pressure, which aligns with TCF principles.',1763114604303);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf300n53j6gldze62hj','cmhyowvf200ms3j6gzuuq85za','ENHANCEMENT OPPORTUNITY: When leaving voicemails about outstanding requirements, consider briefly mentioning the consequence or benefit of providing the documentation. For example: ''We need this letter to complete your policy setup and ensure your cover is fully active.'' This helps customers understand the importance and motivates timely response.',1763114604303);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf600nt3j6gtg9ch0sn','cmhyowvf500nb3j6g979vzfd7','CRITICAL: Always provide call recording disclosure at the start of every call. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is an FCA requirement under COBS 11.8 and must be stated before proceeding. (Score: 6/10  8/10)',1763114604306);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf600nu3j6gcul0qruw','cmhyowvf500nb3j6g979vzfd7','Path to Excellence (Call Opening 68): You handled the rest of the call professionally, but the opening missed the recording disclosure. To reach 8/10, add this to your greeting: ''Good morning, you''re through to [name] at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This takes 3 seconds and ensures full compliance.',1763114604306);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf600nv3j6gxtorryak','cmhyowvf500nb3j6g979vzfd7','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 910): You demonstrated excellent knowledge of policy features, rebuild calculations, and cover limits. To reach 10/10, consider proactively explaining the benefits of features before customers ask. For example, when mentioning home emergency cover, add: ''This is particularly valuable for landlords as it means any emergency affecting your tenants can be resolved quickly, protecting your rental income and tenant relationship.''',1763114604306);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf600nw3j6gl69nb856','cmhyowvf500nb3j6g979vzfd7','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery 89): You asked good questions about changes and ran the rebuild calculator. To reach 9/10, probe deeper into the Airbnb usage: ''How many days per year do you typically rent the property? Are there any peak seasons? This helps ensure your hosting cover is optimized for your actual usage pattern.''',1763114604306);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvf600nx3j6gat2k3ndk','cmhyowvf500nb3j6g979vzfd7','Excellent TCF compliance demonstrated by making card storage optional and respecting customer choice without pressure. This is best-practice customer treatment - continue this approach.',1763114604306);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfa00ol3j6grk0xo9oo','cmhyowvf800o43j6g0rh86aak','COMPLIANCE GAP - Call Opening: While you identified the firm name clearly, you missed the call recording disclosure at the very start. For renewals, open with: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This ensures immediate transparency and GDPR compliance from the first moment.',1763114604310);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfa00om3j6g535rchvc','cmhyowvf800o43j6g0rh86aak','Path to Excellence (Data Protection - 89): You handled DPA verification well by collecting name, DOB, and address before accessing policy details. To reach 9/10, explicitly confirm completion of verification before proceeding: ''Thank you Amanda, I''ve verified your identity and can now access your policy details.'' This provides clear audit trail and reassures the customer.',1763114604310);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfa00on3j6gm5z2spwk','cmhyowvf800o43j6g0rh86aak','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 89): You demonstrated solid knowledge of the rebuild calculator, policy features, and add-ons. To elevate to 9/10, proactively explain the benefit of key features: ''The 5 million public liability is particularly important for hosting properties as it protects you if a guest is injured or their property is damaged. This gives you significant peace of mind.'' This shows deeper understanding of customer needs.',1763114604310);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfa00oo3j6gpbce8s2u','cmhyowvf800o43j6g0rh86aak','Path to Excellence (Closing - 89): You completed the renewal efficiently and confirmed next steps. To reach 9/10, add a final value statement: ''Just to confirm, you''re now covered from 16th November with comprehensive buildings and contents insurance including hosting cover, all for 864.76. You''ve got excellent protection for your rental property at a competitive price.'' This reinforces the value and leaves the customer confident.',1763114604310);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfa00op3j6g22fa9hn4','cmhyowvf800o43j6g0rh86aak','Efficiency Opportunity: The call included two extended holds (4+ minutes total). While necessary for system updates, consider explaining what you''re doing during holds or keeping the customer informed: ''I''m just updating the rebuild figure in our system, this will take about 2 minutes.'' This maintains engagement and reduces perceived wait time.',1763114604310);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfd00pb3j6gb80ldah9','cmhyowvfc00ow3j6ga6svk69k','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance. You MUST state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization status, (2) Call recording disclosure, and (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for renewals. Script: ''Good morning, this is [Agent Name] from [Company Name], we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy. Am I speaking to Mrs. Abdul?'' This is non-negotiable and protects both the customer and the firm.',1763114604314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfd00pc3j6gy5l6mrm5','cmhyowvfc00ow3j6ga6svk69k','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - 8/10): You built good rapport by using the customer''s name frequently and maintaining a friendly, conversational tone. To reach 9/10, acknowledge positive customer comments more explicitly to deepen connection. When the customer said ''insurance should come down if you''ve had no claims,'' you agreed but could have added: ''Absolutely right, and I''m really pleased we''ve been able to reward your claims-free year with a reduction. It''s great to see loyal customers like yourself benefit.'' This validates their perspective and strengthens the relationship.',1763114604314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfd00pd3j6gbfvv16tm','cmhyowvfc00ow3j6ga6svk69k','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - 8/10): You confirmed all key policy details and checked for changes effectively. To reach 9/10, probe slightly deeper on usage patterns for holiday lets. For example: ''You mentioned you have more than two adults staying - do you ever have larger groups or events? This helps ensure your liability limits are appropriate for your actual usage.'' This demonstrates consultative expertise and may uncover additional coverage needs.',1763114604314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfd00pe3j6gsohchxfb','cmhyowvfc00ow3j6ga6svk69k','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Closing - 8/10): You successfully renewed the policy and confirmed payment details clearly. To reach 9/10, add a brief value summary before final confirmation: ''So just to recap, you''re fully covered for your holiday let property with 1 million rebuild cost, your premium has decreased by [amount] thanks to your claims-free year, and we''ll spread payments over 12 months. You''re all set for another year of worry-free cover.'' This reinforces the value and leaves the customer with confidence in their decision.',1763114604314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfd00pf3j6g6d1i7jgc','cmhyowvfc00ow3j6ga6svk69k','Consider offering to email policy documents immediately after the call rather than just mentioning they''ll arrive. This provides instant confirmation and improves customer experience. For example: ''I''ll send your policy documents to your email within the next few minutes - please check your inbox and junk folder.''',1763114604314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfi00ps3j6g55tcvk0q','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosures: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We process your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct or delete your data.'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13.',1763114604318);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfi00pt3j6gqtv20ndi','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Complete DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. Must obtain minimum of name + date of birth + postcode before looking up quotes or policy information. Say: ''Before I access your details, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' This is required under GDPR Article 5.',1763114604318);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfi00pu3j6gwgadmh92','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built good rapport with friendly, polite language. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''ve been looking at the quote with your wife and want to move forward - that''s great, let me make sure we get you sorted quickly.'' This shows you''re actively listening to their unique circumstances.',1763114604318);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfi00pv3j6g1sp6glb4','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - currently 7/10): You asked good clarifying questions about property ownership. To reach 8/10, probe deeper into why the quote expired and what the customer''s timeline is. For example: ''I see the quote expired - were you comparing different options, or was there something specific holding you back? This helps me ensure we get you the right cover.'' This uncovers potential concerns early.',1763114604318);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfi00pw3j6g3iq3vf40','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): Excellent job setting clear callback expectations with timeframe and named colleague. To reach 9/10, confirm the best contact number and summarize what will happen: ''So Keith will call you back within 30 minutes on this number to discuss your quote QPK3-24L-4AAVS-SCHI and help you proceed with the policy. Is there anything specific you''d like him to focus on?'' This ensures complete clarity and customer preparedness.',1763114604318);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfm00qi3j6gcgtkz3l5','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures. You must state: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement. Practice this as your standard opening script: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Jasmine speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?''',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfm00qj3j6g5tsde9a1','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','MANDATORY DISCLOSURES: When processing cancellations, explain the refund calculation method. For example: ''You''ll receive a pro-rata refund for the unused portion of your policy, minus any administration fees. The cancellations team will confirm the exact refund amount when they call you back.'' This ensures transparency per ICOBS requirements.',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfm00qk3j6ghiu2lag1','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport 910): You built excellent rapport with warm language like ''Oh, bless you'' and ''That''s lovely, thank you so much.'' To reach 10/10, add a brief empathetic acknowledgment of the customer''s situation: ''I''m sorry to hear the property has been sold - that must have been quite a process. Let me help you close this policy smoothly today.'' This deepens the personal connection.',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfm00ql3j6g7q4kvszr','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Professionalism 910): Your communication was polished and courteous throughout. To achieve 10/10, eliminate filler phrases like ''bear with me two seconds'' (used 4 times). Replace with: ''I''m just accessing your policy now'' or ''Let me check that for you.'' This sounds more confident and professional.',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfm00qm3j6gvpkhtbu7','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up 89): You clearly set callback expectations within 30 minutes. To reach 9/10, provide the customer with a reference number for the cancellation request: ''I''ve logged your cancellation request as reference CAN12345. The team will call you within 30 minutes to finalize everything.'' This gives the customer confidence and a tracking mechanism.',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfq00r93j6glt9c1dhl','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance statement: ''You''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement.',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfq00ra3j6gpsa6nn7t','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Complete DPA verification (full name + DOB or address + postcode) BEFORE accessing any policy information or customer data. Never search for policies using email alone without prior verification. This protects against data breaches under GDPR.',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfq00rb3j6gzfmhgwtu','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 89): You built good rapport with phrases like ''That''s absolutely fine'' and ''We can have a little look at that for you.'' To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''re preparing information for your accountants - I''ll make sure we get you exactly what you need quickly so you''re not held up.''',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfq00rc3j6g9r8ubqd1','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 89): You demonstrated solid knowledge of product offerings and limitations. To reach 9/10, proactively mention relevant product features without being asked. For example, when discussing smallholdings: ''For properties like yours, we can also cover outbuildings, farm equipment, and even loss of rental income if that''s relevant to your situation.''',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfq00rd3j6gnruyi23m','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 89): You confirmed the document would be resent to the correct email. To reach 9/10, provide a specific timeframe and offer a callback option: ''I''ll resend those documents within the next hour. If you don''t receive them by end of business today, please call us back on [number] and ask for me directly.''',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfz00rv3j6grmc4zcew','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a mandatory FCA requirement and protects both the customer and the firm.',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfz00rw3j6g60x8kjhx','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Complete full DPA verification BEFORE accessing any policy data. Must verify at minimum: full name + date of birth OR full name + postcode. Script: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Current practice of using name only is a GDPR breach.',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfz00rx3j6giuhasa7n','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','PROFESSIONALISM: While friendly rapport is excellent, avoid overly familiar terms like ''my love'' which may not suit all customers or professional standards. Use ''Ms/Mr [surname]'' or first name only. To maintain warmth while staying professional, try: ''That''s perfect, Leigh. Let me get that sorted for you right away.''',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvfz00ry3j6gzw5p981r','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You explained the hosting top-up clearly and mentioned the important requirement about the main insurer. To reach 9/10, proactively check if the customer has questions about the online process or offer to stay on the line while they access the link. Example: ''Before you go, do you have any questions about completing the online form? I''m happy to talk you through what information you''ll need.''',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg200sm3j6g0msh39g2','cmhyowvg100s73j6g4z9hvvku','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with required regulatory disclosures. You must state: (1) Company name and regulatory status: ''You''re through to Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (2) Call recording notice: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', and (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for existing customers: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604339);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg200sn3j6gwv0n5m24','cmhyowvg100s73j6g4z9hvvku','RAPPORT BUILDING (scored 9/10) - Path to Excellence: You demonstrated excellent warmth and empathy throughout, particularly when apologizing for the reference number confusion (''Oh, bless you. Sorry'') and validating the customer''s diligence (''it''s always better to be safe than sorry''). To reach 10/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''A month-long home exchange sounds wonderful - I can see why you want to make absolutely sure everything''s covered properly. Let me get you the exact answer you need.'' This deepens the personal connection.',1763114604339);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg200so3j6gsguv9wiv','cmhyowvg100s73j6g4z9hvvku','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE (scored 8/10) - Path to Excellence: You explained the 90-day hosting cover clearly and took appropriate time to research the sublease question rather than guessing. To reach 9/10, provide slightly more comprehensive explanations upfront. For example, when explaining the sublease answer, add: ''The key thing our policy looks at is whether you remain the primary resident and the arrangement stays within the 90-day limit. The sublease document itself doesn''t affect coverage - it''s the actual usage pattern that matters.'' This proactive detail prevents follow-up questions.',1763114604339);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg200sp3j6gfgmfu3o7','cmhyowvg100s73j6g4z9hvvku','FOLLOW-UP (scored 8/10) - Path to Excellence: You offered multiple contact channels (phone and email) which is great. To reach 9/10, be more specific about what to do if circumstances change. For example: ''If your dates extend beyond a month or you have any other exchanges planned this year, just give us a quick call to make sure you''re tracking within your 90-day allowance. We can help you keep count.'' This shows proactive customer care.',1763114604339);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg600tb3j6ghfv4dpch','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance elements. You MUST state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization status: ''This is Will calling from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (3) Brief GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604342);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg600tc3j6gp3y2jkfh','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Complete proper DPA verification BEFORE accessing any policy data. Current practice of only asking for address/email is insufficient. You must verify: (1) Full name, (2) Date of birth, (3) Address or postcode. Script example: ''For security, can I take your full name and date of birth please? And can you confirm the postcode on the policy?'' Only after verification say: ''Thank you, I can now access your policy details.''',1763114604342);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg600td3j6gieezwukw','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','HIGH PRIORITY: Always provide complaints procedure information during policy changes/cancellations. Script: ''If you have any concerns about how we''ve handled this, you can make a complaint by contacting our complaints team. If you''re not satisfied with our response within 8 weeks, you can refer the matter to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This is required under DISP 1.2.',1763114604342);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg600te3j6ggqxeq9c9','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','Path to Excellence (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built good rapport by being friendly and using the customer''s name. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. Example: ''I can see you''ve completed the sale of the property - congratulations on that. Let me make sure we get this cancellation processed smoothly for you so there''s one less thing to worry about.'' This shows deeper engagement with their circumstances.',1763114604342);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvg600tf3j6gtml0x54r','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): You clearly explained the email confirmation and accounts follow-up timeline. To reach 9/10, provide a specific contact method if they have questions. Example: ''You''ll receive confirmation today and accounts will contact you in 3-5 days. If you have any questions in the meantime, you can reply to that email or call us on [number] and quote your policy reference.'' This gives customers more control and confidence.',1763114604342);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvga00tw3j6gkulbwkk7','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (2) ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the FCA'', and (3) brief GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is mandatory under FCA and GDPR requirements.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvga00tx3j6gzjtekb9d','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','DATA PROTECTION: Complete DPA verification (name, DOB, address) BEFORE accessing any policy information on screen. Say: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' This prevents unauthorized data access.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvga00ty3j6gdpq1u5sb','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built good rapport with polite, friendly communication. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''re running a holiday let business - that''s great. Let me make absolutely sure you''ve got the right protection in place for your guests and property.'' This shows deeper engagement with their needs.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvga00tz3j6gfgeuaxiv','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge - currently 8/10): Excellent explanation of coverage details. To reach 9/10, proactively mention any exclusions or limitations. For example: ''You''re covered for guest damage through your hosting add-on. Just so you''re aware, this covers accidental damage but not malicious damage - that would fall under your main buildings cover.'' This demonstrates comprehensive expertise.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvga00u03j6gakl4v60d','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): Good call closure. To reach 9/10, offer proactive next steps. For example: ''Is there anything else about your policy you''d like me to clarify? Also, your renewal is coming up in [X months] - we''ll be in touch before then, but feel free to call if your circumstances change.'' This adds value and sets future expectations.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgg00uf3j6gk5x8lnoa','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','CRITICAL - Data Protection Breach: Never access customer policy data without first verifying the caller''s identity and authority. Even for broker-to-broker calls, implement DPA verification (e.g., ''Can I take your name and broker reference number please?''). This is a serious GDPR breach that could result in regulatory action and data breach reporting requirements.',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgg00ug3j6glk1cyewe','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: Ensure GDPR privacy notice is included in IVR or agent greeting. The current recording disclosure mentions ''accuracy of information purposes'' but omits required data protection rights. Add: ''We process your personal data in accordance with GDPR. You have rights to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.''',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgg00uh3j6gk85ww1fe','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','Implement broker authentication protocol: Create a standard verification process for broker-to-broker calls that includes broker firm name, FCA reference number, and caller name before accessing any customer policy data. This protects both the customer and the firm from unauthorized access.',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgg00ui3j6gt37ysus0','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','Path to Excellence (Professionalism 89): You maintained excellent courtesy and efficiency. To reach 9/10, add a brief confirmation of the action taken: ''I''ve backdated that policy to [date] as requested. You''ll receive a confirmation email shortly.'' This provides additional assurance and documentation of the change.',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgk00v93j6g9uwkfwbq','cmhyowvgi00ur3j6g97t43ame','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must provide call opening compliance elements at start of EVERY call: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (2) ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (3) GDPR notice: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13.',1763114604356);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgk00va3j6gg7krnltv','cmhyowvgi00ur3j6g97t43ame','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - 78): You did well clarifying the customer''s complex situation with renovations and future holiday let plans. To reach 8/10, ask more structured discovery questions earlier: ''Let me understand your full situation - you mentioned renovations, when do they complete? Will you live there or let it immediately? This helps me find the right cover for each stage.'' This ensures you capture all needs upfront.',1763114604356);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgk00vb3j6g6rjutpoq','cmhyowvgi00ur3j6g97t43ame','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge - 78): Good job acknowledging uncertainty about builders insurance and seeking help. To reach 8/10, develop familiarity with common product variations: ''For unoccupied properties under renovation, we typically offer specialist unoccupied property insurance which covers the building during works. Let me check our options for your situation.'' This shows broader product awareness.',1763114604356);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgk00vc3j6g9656usw5','cmhyowvgi00ur3j6g97t43ame','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Professionalism - 78): You handled the difficult line quality and customer abroad situation well. To reach 8/10, avoid informal terms like ''my love'' which, while friendly, may not suit all customers or professional standards. Stick to ''Benedict'' or neutral terms like ''for you''. This maintains consistent professionalism.',1763114604356);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgk00vd3j6gjdw10a9v','cmhyowvgi00ur3j6g97t43ame','Excellent TCF compliance - you clearly explained eligibility criteria without pressure, verified information when uncertain, and maintained positive rapport even when declining business. This is exemplary treating customers fairly practice.',1763114604356);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgp00vw3j6gx3etvpjv','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: Must provide mandatory call opening elements at start of EVERY call. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help?'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgp00vx3j6g645r8ixp','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','CRITICAL - Data Protection: ALWAYS conduct DPA verification BEFORE accessing any policy data. After taking the policy reference, say: ''Thank you. Before I access your account, I need to verify your identity. Can you confirm your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Never access customer data without verification - this is a GDPR breach. What the law requires: GDPR Article 5 requires lawful processing with appropriate security. What to say: ''For data protection, I need to verify your identity before accessing your policy. Can you confirm your full name, date of birth, and postcode?'' Why it matters: This prevents unauthorized access to sensitive personal and financial information.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgp00vy3j6gt3eie9il','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','Path to Excellence (Rapport - currently 8/10): You did well using the customer''s name and showing patience. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. For example: ''Thank you for calling about your Sykes rental property renewal, Victoria. I can see you''ve been with us for [time period] - we really appreciate your continued trust. Let me get you to our renewals specialist who can review the best options for you.'' This builds stronger connection and loyalty.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgp00vz3j6gs8l1tojh','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): Good job explaining the transfer process. To reach 9/10, provide the specialist''s name earlier and set expectations about what will happen next. For example: ''I''m going to transfer you to Jas from our renewals team. She''ll review your current cover, discuss any changes to your property or circumstances, and go through your renewal options with you. This usually takes about 10-15 minutes. Is now a good time?'' This reduces customer anxiety and improves experience.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgp00w03j6gm4suq93o','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','Efficiency Opportunity: While transferring to a specialist is appropriate, consider whether first-line agents could be trained to handle straightforward renewals. This would reduce customer wait time and improve first-contact resolution rates.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wi3j6gkrxrxwcu','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures. Must state: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is an FCA requirement and protects both customer and firm.',1763114604364);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wj3j6g00cdjy6w','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','Path to Excellence (Rapport 910): You built excellent rapport with warm language (''my lovely'', ''thank you so much''). To reach 10/10, add one personalized comment acknowledging the customer''s life event: ''Congratulations on selling your house, Tracy. I hope the move goes smoothly. Now let me help you sort out the insurance side of things.'' This creates memorable, human connection.',1763114604364);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wk3j6ghz6phaos','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','Path to Excellence (Mandatory Disclosures 78): You handled the call efficiently, but before transferring to cancellations, briefly mention: ''My colleague will explain any refund due and confirm the cancellation date with you.'' This sets expectations and demonstrates transparency, meeting TCF requirements more fully.',1763114604364);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wl3j6geqsploja','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 89): You confirmed the transfer clearly. To reach 9/10, add: ''Callum will provide you with a cancellation reference number and confirm everything in writing within 24 hours.'' This gives the customer confidence about documentation and next steps.',1763114604364);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wm3j6gu8ul9593','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','Excellent DPA verification technique - you collected address and DOB before accessing any policy data. Continue this best practice on every call to maintain GDPR compliance.',1763114604364);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xb3j6gq1qe04m0','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must provide complete call opening compliance elements at start of every call. Required script: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This is a fundamental regulatory requirement under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13.',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xc3j6go91jvue3','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always conduct full DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data or policy information. Required process: Collect name, date of birth, and postcode minimum. Say: ''For data protection, can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verification should you access systems. Current practice (name only) is a serious GDPR breach.',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xd3j6g92id7p8q','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','PROFESSIONALISM (scored 7/10): Good use of empathetic language and professional tone. To reach 8/10, eliminate filler words like ''sort of'' which appeared 6 times in this short call. Replace with confident, direct language. Instead of ''We would have to go through the quote with you sort of from the top,'' say ''We''ll need to go through the quote with you from the beginning to ensure accuracy.''',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xe3j6gvy3qcve0','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','CLOSING (scored 6/10): You appropriately explained the time requirement, but lost the opportunity when customer hesitated. To reach 8/10, use assumptive closing with specific options. Instead of accepting ''I''ll call back,'' say: ''I understand you''re heading to work. I have availability today at 5pm or tomorrow at 9am - which works better for you? I''ll book you in now and send a confirmation text.''',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xf3j6g57bc18wg','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','FOLLOW-UP (scored 6/10): No follow-up plan was established. To reach 8/10, always secure a commitment before ending the call. Say: ''Before you go, let me book you an appointment slot so we don''t lose your quote. I can hold your details and call you at [specific time]. What''s the best number to reach you on?'' Then confirm the appointment details and send written confirmation.',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh000xw3j6gxz2q90fp','cmhyowvgz00xn3j6gzp87efrf','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: You MUST provide a compliant call opening on EVERY call. Required elements: (1) Firm name and FCA authorization: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' (2) Call recording: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes.'' (3) GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable regulatory requirement.',1763114604372);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh000xx3j6gpysdba3v','cmhyowvgz00xn3j6gzp87efrf','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: You MUST complete DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. Never accept a policy reference or look up customer details until you''ve verified identity. Required script: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only after verification can you proceed. This prevents unauthorized data access and is a GDPR requirement.',1763114604372);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh000xy3j6gmydw2g24','cmhyowvgz00xn3j6gzp87efrf','PROFESSIONALISM - Path to Excellence (Current: 7/10): You built good rapport and were friendly throughout the call. To reach 8/10, maintain warmth while using more universally professional language. Replace terms like ''my love'' with ''Anna'' or neutral phrases. Example: ''Perfect Anna, I''ll get someone to call you just before 12. Does that work for you?'' This ensures professionalism while keeping the friendly tone.',1763114604372);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh000xz3j6g1qv028kw','cmhyowvgz00xn3j6gzp87efrf','FOLLOW-UP - Path to Excellence (Current: 8/10): Excellent work confirming the callback timeframe and verifying the contact number. To reach 9/10, add one more element: explain what the specialist will do on the callback. Example: ''I''ll arrange for one of our property insurance specialists to call you before 12. They''ll review your current holiday let policy and provide you with a quote for long-term rental cover. Is there anything specific you''d like them to prepare before they call?'' This sets even clearer expectations and demonstrates proactive service.',1763114604372);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh300ym3j6gvmo05dci','cmhyowvh200y73j6gaakdd6an','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required regulatory disclosures. You must state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization status: ''Good morning, you''re through to Willett Pickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority''; (2) Call recording notice: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes''; (3) Brief GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604376);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh300yn3j6g3l68yvxr','cmhyowvh200y73j6gaakdd6an','CLOSING (scored 7/10) - Path to Excellence: You handled the customer''s query well and invited further contact. To reach 8/10, provide more specific next steps. For example: ''I''m glad that''s clarified the excess for you. When you''re ready to proceed with the quote, you can complete it online or give us a call and we''ll process it for you. Do you have any other questions about the cover before you decide?'' This gives the customer clear direction and checks for any remaining concerns.',1763114604376);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh300yo3j6gtivk3epj','cmhyowvh200y73j6gaakdd6an','FOLLOW-UP (scored 7/10) - Path to Excellence: You offered general availability for questions, which is good. To reach 8/10, be more specific about the customer''s journey. For example: ''You mentioned you were looking at quotes online - have you saved that quote? It will be valid for 30 days. If you need any help completing it or have questions about the cover, just call us back on this number.'' This confirms their next action and provides a timeframe.',1763114604376);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh300yp3j6gc5yschr6','cmhyowvh200y73j6gaakdd6an','Strong product knowledge demonstrated - you clearly explained the different excess amounts for guest claims (100) versus standard claims (200). Continue this clear differentiation when explaining policy features.',1763114604376);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvh300yq3j6gfm4mq7v0','cmhyowvh200y73j6gaakdd6an','Excellent TCF compliance - you asked probing questions to understand the customer''s specific situation (furnished holiday let) rather than making assumptions. This customer-centric approach ensures appropriate cover recommendations.',1763114604376);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvha00ze3j6g6g9l0yn7','cmhyowvh900z13j6grk4omltt','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Complete the call opening properly. You must state: (1) Full firm name ''Pikl Insurance'', (2) ''Authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (3) Call recording disclosure, AND (4) GDPR privacy notice: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This is required by FCA rules and GDPR Article 13. Current score: 4/10. Path to 8/10: Include all four elements in a clear, structured opening.',1763114604383);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvha00zf3j6g3cy9jy07','cmhyowvh900z13j6grk4omltt','FOLLOW-UP IMPROVEMENT: When unable to provide cover, always offer alternatives or referrals to maintain customer service excellence. Current score: 6/10. What you did well: You were honest about limitations. To reach 8/10, say: ''I''m sorry we can''t help with company-owned properties, but I''d be happy to recommend a specialist commercial broker who can assist you. Would that be helpful?'' This turns a dead-end into a value-added interaction.',1763114604383);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvha00zg3j6gnshbuast','cmhyowvh900z13j6grk4omltt','NEEDS DISCOVERY: Strong questioning to identify the corporate ownership issue quickly. Current score: 7/10. What you did well: Asked clarifying questions about property type and ownership. To reach 8/10: Even when you can''t help, ask one more question to understand their full needs: ''Just so I can point you in the right direction, is this a single property or do you have multiple holiday lets in the company?'' This shows genuine interest and helps with better referrals.',1763114604383);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvha00zh3j6ggr9rbgrf','cmhyowvh900z13j6grk4omltt','RAPPORT BUILDING: Excellent use of customer name and friendly tone throughout. Current score: 8/10. What you did well: Natural conversational style and appropriate apology for callback delay. To reach 9/10: Add empathy when delivering bad news: ''I understand you''ve taken time to call us and your neighbour recommended us, so I''m really sorry we can''t help with company-owned properties on this occasion.'' This acknowledges their effort and disappointment.',1763114604383);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhf00zz3j6gqqb3v44f','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','CRITICAL: NEVER use profanity on customer calls under any circumstances. The phrases ''Jesus Christ'' and ''fucking'' were audible to the customer and constitute a severe professionalism breach. This could result in complaints and regulatory scrutiny. Always assume the customer can hear everything you say.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhf01003j6g4lnynstr','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','CRITICAL: Complete ALL call opening compliance requirements before proceeding: (1) Identify firm name and regulatory status, (2) State call recording disclosure, (3) Provide appropriate GDPR notice for call type. This is non-negotiable FCA/ICOBS compliance. Script: ''Good morning, this is [name] from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.''',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhf01013j6g9a6z7abi','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','CRITICAL: ALWAYS complete DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. You accessed the customer''s email address and renewal information without verifying identity. This is a GDPR breach. Script: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?''',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhf01023j6gzmqswa0d','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','When experiencing technical difficulties, communicate professionally with the customer: ''I apologize, I''m experiencing a brief technical issue with my system. Please bear with me for just a moment while I resolve this.'' Never express frustration audibly or use inappropriate language.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhf01033j6gvgsxtbx5','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','Develop a structured call approach: (1) Compliant opening, (2) DPA verification, (3) Needs discovery, (4) Solution presentation, (5) Clear next steps. This call lacked structure and missed fundamental compliance requirements.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhj010s3j6go9xs6arh','cmhyowvhi010e3j6g85nwr6af','EXCELLENT COMPLIANCE: You demonstrated exemplary compliance throughout this call - thorough DPA verification before accessing data, comprehensive mandatory disclosures, and clear non-advised status. This is a model renewal call that meets all FCA and ICOBS requirements.',1763114604391);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhj010t3j6gzesdjoje','cmhyowvhi010e3j6g85nwr6af','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - 89): You built good rapport with professional, friendly communication. To reach 9/10, incorporate more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example, when they mentioned selling their primary residence: ''That must be quite a transition period for you - I''m glad we can keep your holiday let covered seamlessly during this time.'' This shows deeper empathy and strengthens the relationship.',1763114604391);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhj010u3j6gcqgmdfsx','cmhyowvhi010e3j6g85nwr6af','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - 89): You conducted thorough discovery and identified the key change in circumstances. To elevate to 9/10, probe slightly deeper on implications: ''Since you''ve moved temporarily and your correspondence address will change, would you like me to update that now, or will you contact us once you''re settled in your new home? I want to make sure all documents reach you.'' This demonstrates proactive problem-solving.',1763114604391);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhj010v3j6gjpwbp9i0','cmhyowvhi010e3j6g85nwr6af','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge - 910): Outstanding explanation of hot tub coverage under buildings and public liability - clear, confident, and accurate. To reach 10/10, consider adding a brief risk management tip: ''Just ensure your hot tub maintenance records are up to date, as insurers may request these if there''s ever a claim related to equipment failure.'' This adds consultative value beyond the transaction.',1763114604391);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhj010w3j6gq27gj4kg','cmhyowvhi010e3j6g85nwr6af','PROCESS ENHANCEMENT: When the customer mentioned their correspondence address will change, consider flagging this for immediate update or setting a reminder to follow up. While you acknowledged it, proactively offering to update it during the call would demonstrate exceptional service and ensure policy documents reach the correct address.',1763114604391);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvho011g3j6gssahsxdq','cmhyowvhm01123j6gqin9qy9q','COMPLIANCE GAP - Call Opening: While you provided call recording disclosure and GDPR verification, you missed firm identification at the start. To reach 8/10, open with: ''Good afternoon, this is Keith calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and monitoring purposes.'' This ensures immediate regulatory compliance and builds customer confidence from the first moment.',1763114604396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvho011h3j6gig9b1m74','cmhyowvhm01123j6gqin9qy9q','Needs Discovery (7/10  8/10): You allowed the customer to self-direct their decision without exploring their specific needs for the property hosting insurance. To improve, ask probing questions like: ''Can you tell me more about your hosting arrangements? How frequently do you have guests? What concerns you most about having guests in your property?'' This would demonstrate thorough needs assessment and ensure the product truly fits their requirements.',1763114604396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvho011i3j6geoqhogce','cmhyowvhm01123j6gqin9qy9q','Product Knowledge (8/10  9/10): You explained policy features clearly and confidently. To reach 9/10, proactively address common customer concerns before they ask. For example: ''Many property hosts ask about what happens if a guest causes damage beyond the excess - with this policy, you''re covered up to 80,000 for buildings and 40,000 for contents, so you have substantial protection.'' This demonstrates expertise and anticipates customer needs.',1763114604396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvho011j3j6g5ozqofn0','cmhyowvhm01123j6gqin9qy9q','Follow-Up (9/10  10/10): Excellent work explaining the non-auto-renewal process and setting clear expectations. To achieve 10/10, add a specific action item: ''I''ll also send you a calendar reminder link for 28 days before renewal, so you have plenty of time to review your needs. Would that be helpful?'' This shows exceptional customer service and proactive support.',1763114604396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvho011k3j6gdcrbbh6r','cmhyowvhm01123j6gqin9qy9q','Continue your excellent TCF compliance - you consistently checked customer understanding, avoided pressure, and ensured informed consent throughout. This is exemplary practice that protects both the customer and the firm.',1763114604396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhr01253j6gxd9m3clv','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','CRITICAL - DPA Verification: You MUST verify customer identity (name + date of birth minimum) BEFORE accessing any policy details. In this call, you accessed the policy using the policy number without DPA verification - this is a serious GDPR breach. Script: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?''',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhr01263j6gb5j2qs22','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: Every call must include: (1) Call recording disclosure, (2) FCA regulatory status, (3) Brief GDPR notice for service calls. Script: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?''',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhr01273j6gvalo55ey','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','Product Knowledge - Cooling-Off Periods: You initially stated 30 days but corrected to 14 days after checking. Ensure you know key policy terms before the call. The 14-day cooling-off period applies from policy start date or receipt of documents (whichever is later). Path to Excellence (78): You did well recognizing your error and checking with management. To reach 8/10, memorize core policy terms (cooling-off periods, cancellation fees, refund calculations) so you can provide accurate information immediately without needing to check.',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhr01283j6gjp3opkmi','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','Communication Clarity: The customer had difficulty hearing you twice during the call. Ensure you''re speaking clearly, at appropriate volume, and check your headset/audio setup. Path to Excellence (78): You handled the audio issues professionally by acknowledging them. To reach 8/10, proactively ask ''Can you hear me clearly?'' at the start of calls, and slow down your speech slightly when explaining complex information like refund policies.',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhr01293j6gu7yu838j','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','Closing & Follow-Up: While you offered to transfer to cancellations, the call ended without clear confirmation of next steps or whether the transfer would happen. Path to Excellence (78): You correctly identified the need to transfer. To reach 8/10, provide a clear summary before transfer: ''Julie, I''m going to transfer you now to our cancellations team who will process this for you today. If we get disconnected, their direct number is [X]. Is there anything else before I transfer you?''',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhv012w3j6g6g6zwnyq','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You MUST open every call with: (1) Full firm identification including regulatory status (''This is Callum from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA''), (2) Call recording disclosure (''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes''), and (3) GDPR notice appropriate for call type. For renewals, a brief acknowledgment is acceptable: ''This is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable regulatory requirement.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhv012x3j6gluwqbr27','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','CRITICAL - Data Protection: You accessed policy information and assisted with a purchase WITHOUT conducting DPA verification first. You must ALWAYS verify identity (minimum: full name + date of birth) BEFORE accessing any customer data or policy details. This is a serious GDPR breach. Script: ''Before I can access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?''',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhv012y3j6gywl13jxb','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','HIGH PRIORITY - Mandatory Disclosures: For renewal purchases, you must explain: (1) 14-day cooling-off rights (''You have 14 days to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind''), (2) Complaints procedure (''If you''re unhappy, we have a complaints process and you can escalate to the Financial Ombudsman Service''), and (3) Price breakdown if discussing costs. Build these into your closing script.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhv012z3j6gzd7w56cy','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','Path to Excellence - Rapport (89): You did well staying on the line and showing patience while the customer navigated the website. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''re already familiar with our process from your building insurance - that''s great. Let me make sure this top-up goes smoothly for you.'' This builds stronger connection.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhv01303j6gg4u0var3','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','Path to Excellence - Product Knowledge (89): You guided the customer effectively through the online journey. To elevate to 9/10, proactively explain WHY certain questions are asked to build confidence. Example: ''The next question asks about sharing because it affects your liability cover - since you''re letting the whole property, we''ll make sure you have full protection.'' This demonstrates deeper expertise.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhz013s3j6g8w46paki','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. Required script: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement.',1763114604407);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhz013t3j6glez8kqj2','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','Professionalism (scored 7/10) - Path to Excellence: You handled the call professionally overall and showed good empathy. However, the ''First world problem'' comment at 02:53 could be perceived as dismissive when the customer expressed genuine financial concerns about council costs. To reach 8/10, acknowledge customer concerns more seriously: ''I can hear those additional costs are a real concern for you. Let me make sure we get you the best value on your insurance today.'' This validates their feelings while staying professional.',1763114604407);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhz013u3j6gdgwn4fii','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','Excellent TCF Practice: Your proactive switch to Aviva to save the customer 24.85 demonstrates outstanding Treating Customers Fairly principles. This is exactly the behavior regulators want to see - putting customer interests first. Continue this practice and use it as an example of good conduct.',1763114604407);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhz013v3j6grlyt84l3','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','Data Protection Excellence: Your handling of card storage consent was exemplary - you clearly stated it was optional, explained the purpose and duration, and immediately accepted the customer''s refusal without pressure. This is gold-standard GDPR compliance.',1763114604407);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvhz013w3j6g7s3cac9c','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','Needs Discovery Enhancement (scored 8/10) - Path to Excellence: You verified key information well (occupancy, claims, circumstances). To reach 9/10, consider one additional probing question about their usage patterns: ''You mentioned it''s a second property - has the frequency of use changed at all this year, or are you still using it the same amount?'' This could uncover underwriting-relevant changes while showing deeper interest in their situation.',1763114604407);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi2014j3j6gf1s0l820','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures. You must state: (1) Company name and regulatory status: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', and (3) GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi2014k3j6ga20xdupf','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Closing - 78): You handled the customer''s inquiry well and confirmed their understanding. To reach 8/10, provide a clearer call-to-action at the end. For example: ''I''m glad I could clarify the public liability cover for you. Your quote is valid for 30 days. Would it be helpful if I sent you a summary email with the quote details and a direct link to purchase when you''re ready? That way you''ll have everything to hand when you''ve finished comparing.'' This creates a clear next step while respecting their decision-making process.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi2014l3j6g9d78424f','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up - 78): You offered future assistance which is good. To reach 8/10, be more specific about follow-up options. Try: ''Your quote reference is [repeat number] and it''s valid for 30 days. If you have any questions while comparing, feel free to call back and ask for me directly, or you can purchase online anytime. Would you like me to email you the quote summary as well?'' This provides multiple clear pathways for the customer to proceed.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi2014m3j6gy4rs75se','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','Excellent DPA verification process - you correctly requested postcode, name, and date of birth before accessing quote details. Continue this best practice on every call.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi2014n3j6gqmf1g89s','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','Strong product knowledge demonstrated when explaining the guest host top-up and its flexibility. You clearly explained the 99.99 add-on, the 5 million public liability cover, and the option to purchase separately. This transparency builds trust and helps customers make informed decisions.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi6015a3j6gk3a1vklp','cmhyowvi4014w3j6g0ru4kwzu','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. You must state: (1) Company name clearly, (2) ''We are authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (3) ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes''. For renewals, add: ''This is a renewal call and we already hold your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604415);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi6015b3j6gi4ecwvoh','cmhyowvi4014w3j6g0ru4kwzu','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport 910): You built exceptional rapport through warmth, patience, and appropriate humor with the customer''s personal disclosures. To reach 10/10, add one more layer of personalization by referencing specific details later in the call. Example: When discussing next year''s renewal, you could say: ''And of course, we''ll make sure both you and Richard receive the renewal documents so either of you can handle it - whatever works best for you both.'' This shows you''ve truly listened and remembered their circumstances.',1763114604415);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi6015c3j6gai4kcho1','cmhyowvi4014w3j6g0ru4kwzu','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge 89): You demonstrated solid knowledge of policy features, sums insured, and blanket cover limits. To reach 9/10, proactively explain the benefit of features rather than just stating them. Example: Instead of ''We do also have your hosting cover on there as well this year'', say: ''Your hosting cover is included again this year, which is particularly valuable for your situation since you mentioned lending the property to others - it means you''re protected even when friends or family are staying there.'' This shows deeper understanding of how features apply to their specific needs.',1763114604415);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi6015d3j6glb2pucfh','cmhyowvi4014w3j6g0ru4kwzu','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery 89): You thoroughly verified sums insured and property usage. To elevate to 9/10, ask one additional forward-looking question to uncover emerging needs. Example: ''You mentioned the property is used by 2-4 adults - are you expecting that pattern to continue next year, or might there be any changes to how you use the property?'' This demonstrates proactive risk management and may uncover coverage adjustments needed.',1763114604415);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvi6015e3j6gfz30a0u2','cmhyowvi4014w3j6g0ru4kwzu','Excellent handling of the customer''s request to add her husband as an authorized contact - you gathered all necessary details (full name, DOB) for proper security verification in future calls. This shows strong attention to data protection requirements.',1763114604415);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvib01623j6gwz0pbnir','cmhyowvia015l3j6g36rm5bdi','COMPLIANCE GAP: Always provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call. Script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is required for GDPR lawful processing and should be stated before any substantive conversation begins.',1763114604419);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvib01633j6gdorqr6bh','cmhyowvia015l3j6g36rm5bdi','Path to Excellence (Call Opening 78): You handled the call professionally, but missed the opening compliance elements. To reach 8/10, incorporate the full opening script: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This ensures full regulatory compliance from the outset.',1763114604419);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvib01643j6ghf3m2zmz','cmhyowvia015l3j6g36rm5bdi','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): You built good rapport with polite, professional language and time management. To reach 9/10, add more personalized engagement based on the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''ve been hosting with us for a year now - how has that been going for you?'' This deepens the connection and shows genuine interest.',1763114604419);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvib01653j6gqyhkiwvw','cmhyowvia015l3j6g36rm5bdi','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You explained the policy features clearly and accurately. To reach 9/10, proactively highlight key benefits relevant to their specific use case. For example: ''Since you mentioned the property can host up to 4 adults, the 5 million public liability cover is particularly valuable - it protects you if a guest has an accident on the property.'' This demonstrates expert application of product knowledge.',1763114604419);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvib01663j6gzzyvpame','cmhyowvia015l3j6g36rm5bdi','Excellent DPA verification - you completed full security checks before accessing any policy information. This is gold-standard data protection practice and should be maintained on every call.',1763114604419);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvig016u3j6gpzk532x8','cmhyowvif016d3j6g8c6g2fej','COMPLIANCE GAP: Always provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call. You handled the rest of the call excellently, but this is a regulatory requirement. Script: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This protects both the customer and the company.',1763114604424);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvig016v3j6gudvcjlu8','cmhyowvif016d3j6g8c6g2fej','Path to Excellence (Rapport 910): You built excellent rapport with natural humor (''That''s what they all say'') and compliments (''Excellent phonetics''). To reach 10/10, add one more personalized touch that references the customer''s specific situation. Example: ''I can see you''ve been with us for [X] years now - we really appreciate your loyalty, Catherine. Let''s make sure everything''s still perfect for your property.''',1763114604424);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvig016w3j6gpzdhou6z','cmhyowvif016d3j6g8c6g2fej','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 910): Your follow-up was thorough and clear. To reach 10/10, add a proactive service touch. Example: ''I''ve also made a note that you''re a landlord - if your circumstances change or you acquire another property, just give us a call and we''ll get you sorted straight away.''',1763114604424);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvig016x3j6gleb44ayt','cmhyowvif016d3j6g8c6g2fej','Strong performance overall: You demonstrated excellent professionalism, handled the customer''s multitasking situation with humor, and provided comprehensive regulatory disclosures. Your verification process was textbook perfect, and you treated the customer fairly throughout.',1763114604424);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvil017f3j6gn5oxh8ux','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: You must ALWAYS conduct DPA verification (minimum: full name + date of birth) BEFORE accessing any policy data. This is a fundamental GDPR requirement. Even for broker-to-underwriter calls, verify the caller''s identity and authority to access customer data. Say: ''Before I access the policy, can I take your full name and confirm you''re authorized to discuss this customer''s details?'' Failure to do this is a serious data protection breach.',1763114604429);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvil017g3j6g4knm4ojq','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','PROFESSIONALISM (scored 6/10): You built excellent rapport, which is great, but the extended conversation about OGI shortcuts (F10/F11 discussion) was excessive for a business call. To reach 8/10, keep friendly banter brief and focused on the customer''s needs. Example: ''That''s a great tip about the shortcuts - I''ll try that later. Now, let me get this quote sorted for you.'' This maintains warmth while staying efficient.',1763114604429);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvil017h3j6g3x1lsa94','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','Path to Excellence - RAPPORT (scored 9/10): You excelled at building connection through shared experience (''Mine''s 1887. That''s why I''m moving'') and helpful advice about system shortcuts. To reach 10/10, balance this warmth with slightly tighter call control. You''re already doing brilliantly - just ensure the friendly chat doesn''t extend call time unnecessarily.',1763114604429);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvil017i3j6g8zp1g98q','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','Path to Excellence - NEEDS DISCOVERY (scored 8/10): You systematically gathered all required information (postcode, address, property type, bedrooms, build year, sums insured). To reach 9/10, consider confirming back the key details to ensure accuracy: ''Just to confirm, that''s a 5-bedroom mid-terrace built in 1903 with buildings cover of 810,926 - is that correct?'' This demonstrates thoroughness and prevents errors.',1763114604429);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvil017j3j6gilf2iyfz','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','FOLLOW-UP (scored 8/10): You provided a clear reference number using phonetic alphabet, which is excellent practice. To reach 9/10, also confirm the next steps: ''I''ve emailed this quote to you with reference JB25110GMX. The customer has until 6th December to accept. Any questions, just give me a call.'' This ensures complete clarity on the process.',1763114604429);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvip01883j6g1dvn8abd','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: ALWAYS open calls with full compliance statement: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604433);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvip01893j6g4288eus5','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: NEVER access customer policy data before completing DPA verification. You must ask for at least two verification points (e.g., date of birth + postcode, or security questions) BEFORE looking at any account information. This is a GDPR breach with serious regulatory consequences.',1763114604433);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvip018a3j6gy8mk78dn','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','PROFESSIONALISM - Path to Excellence (78): You maintained good professionalism overall and appropriately escalated to a senior. To reach 8/10, avoid overly casual language like ''mate'' when dealing with professional B2B contacts from insurers like AXA. Instead use: ''Thank you for your patience. Have a good evening.'' This maintains appropriate professional boundaries in broker-to-broker communications.',1763114604433);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvip018b3j6g8l5iymry','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE - Path to Excellence (78): You demonstrated good understanding of the policy structure and payment arrangements. To reach 8/10, develop deeper knowledge of the cancellation process requirements so you can handle these requests without escalation. Familiarize yourself with: when written authority is needed vs phone authorization, partial key timeout procedures, and backdate cancellation rules.',1763114604433);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvip018c3j6gslry3l2s','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','Continue your excellent practice of confirming risk addresses and policy details - this shows attention to detail and helps prevent errors in policy administration.',1763114604433);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviu018y3j6gp680ecme','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: Must provide ALL required disclosures at call start: (1) Call recording notice: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes'', (2) Regulatory status: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (3) GDPR privacy notice for new business: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763114604438);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviu018z3j6grqmvvsln','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','CRITICAL - Data Protection: Complete DPA verification (name + date of birth + address confirmation) BEFORE collecting any other personal information or accessing policy details. The sequence should be: (1) Call opening disclosures, (2) DPA verification, (3) Proceed with quotation. Currently, you collected extensive data before verifying identity at 24:17 into the call.',1763114604438);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviu01903j6gt19djokt','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','HIGH - Mandatory Disclosures Missing: No mention of (1) 14-day cooling-off rights for new policies (ICOBS 7.1.4R), (2) Complaints procedure and Financial Ombudsman Service rights (DISP 1.2), (3) Commission/remuneration disclosure. These must be provided during the sales process, ideally before quote presentation.',1763114604438);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviu01913j6gvtyzhngq','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','Path to Excellence (Closing - 7/10): You handled the technical issue professionally and set expectations for callback. To reach 8/10, provide a specific timeframe: ''I''ll contact the insurer now and call you back within 2 hours, by 1pm today. If I haven''t reached you by then, I''ll leave a voicemail with next steps.'' This gives the customer certainty and demonstrates ownership.',1763114604438);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviu01923j6gyw3mvi3h','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery - 8/10): Excellent work uncovering the customer''s specific requirements around rental days and occupancy limits. To reach 9/10, summarize the needs back to the customer before proceeding: ''Just to confirm, you need coverage for up to 100 rental days per year, up to 10 adults and 10 children, with flexibility beyond Admiral''s 90-day and 2-per-bedroom limits. Is there anything else that''s important to you?'' This ensures complete understanding and builds trust.',1763114604438);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviu01933j6gq9bshuo8','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','Sales Process: When unable to provide immediate quote, explain why clearly and document the customer''s requirements. Consider sending a summary email of what was discussed while they wait for the callback to maintain engagement.',1763114604438);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviy019u3j6gmeebwhee','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We process your personal data in accordance with our privacy policy - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.'' This is required by GDPR Article 13 and FCA regulations.',1763114604442);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviy019v3j6gzyol59ga','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Conduct proper DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. Must verify at minimum: full name + date of birth + postcode. Script: ''Before I access your details, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' This is required by GDPR Article 5 and Data Protection Act 2018.',1763114604442);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviy019w3j6g9eyt7rgy','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport 910): You built excellent rapport through patience, empathy, and helpful alternatives. To reach 10/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific frustration. Example: ''I can really understand how frustrating this must be - you''ve taken the time to get a quote online and now you''re finding out we can''t help. Let me make absolutely sure I get you to someone who can cover this property today.'' This shows deeper empathy and commitment.',1763114604442);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviy019x3j6gulkx8ie8','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge 89): You correctly identified the commercial premises issue and checked with the panel. To reach 9/10, explain the underwriting rationale to educate the customer. Example: ''The reason we can''t cover this is that properties above commercial premises have different risk profiles - things like fire risk from business operations below. That''s why you need a specialist insurer like Home Protect who understand these risks.'' This demonstrates expert-level knowledge.',1763114604442);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowviy019y3j6g4x622lra','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up 89): Excellent job providing alternative provider details. To reach 9/10, offer to send the details via email/SMS for their records and ask if they''d like any other information. Example: ''Would it be helpful if I sent you Home Protect''s details by email so you have them to hand? Is there anything else about the type of cover you need that I can clarify before you call them?'' This ensures complete customer support.',1763114604442);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b33j6g2i4whm9w','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','CRITICAL: Always open calls with required disclosures: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b43j6g3rxf0sfw','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','CRITICAL: Proactively explain cooling-off rights during the sales process, not just when customer asks about cancellation. Required script: ''You have 14 days from your renewal date to cancel for a pro-rata refund if you change your mind. After 14 days, there''s a 30 cancellation charge.'' This must be stated before taking payment.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b53j6g9ctq4fvi','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','HIGH PRIORITY: Missing complaints procedure disclosure. Must state: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint by calling [number] or writing to [address]. If we can''t resolve it within 8 weeks, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' This is required by DISP 1.2.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b63j6g0h3bory0','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','Path to Excellence (Rapport 910): You built exceptional rapport through personalized conversation and the Victoria film analogy. To reach 10/10, maintain this warmth while ensuring all compliance requirements are met seamlessly. Example: ''I love that we can take time to get this right for you - no rush at all. Before we continue, I should mention this call is recorded and your data is held securely under our privacy policy.''',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b73j6gz82ddakj','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You explained products well but showed uncertainty about claims timeframes. To reach 9/10, have ready answers for common queries or know exactly where to direct customers. Example: ''The claims team can advise on specific timeframes - their number is [X]. Generally, you should report claims as soon as possible, but let me transfer you now if you''d like to discuss that phone claim.''',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b83j6gb7nuxz6n','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery 78): Good exploration of unspecified items and bicycle coverage. To reach 8/10, use more structured discovery questions earlier in the call. Example: ''Before we review your renewal, let me ask - have there been any changes to your circumstances? Any new valuable items? Any changes to how you use the property?'' This ensures nothing is missed.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyowvja01b93j6gajwrmo7a','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','Path to Excellence (Objection Handling 78): You empathized well with the customer''s cost concerns about installment APR. To reach 8/10, provide more context about why installment costs exist and offer alternatives. Example: ''I completely understand - the APR does seem high. This reflects the administrative cost of spreading payments. If you''re able to pay annually, you''d save 45.60. Would it help to discuss whether that''s possible?''',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7jzg000qtd3rleczp8dr','cmhyp7jzc000ltd3rbbwbildf','NOT APPLICABLE - This is a voicemail message, not an agent-customer interaction. No agent was present on the call.',1763115102701);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7jzg000rtd3rqyspjkfy','cmhyp7jzc000ltd3rbbwbildf','The customer (Keith from Pikl Insurance) was attempting to reach Paul Hill regarding an online quote.',1763115102701);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7jzg000std3r9to1n56u','cmhyp7jzc000ltd3rbbwbildf','This call should be categorized as a missed call/voicemail and routed for callback follow-up.',1763115102701);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7t7s0015td3ru6lqvyw4','cmhyp7t7n0010td3r99fetjy8','NOT APPLICABLE - No live agent-customer interaction occurred. This was a voicemail exchange only.',1763115114664);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7t7s0016td3r6eiljmj0','cmhyp7t7n0010td3r99fetjy8','For future QA purposes, only calls with actual agent-customer dialogue should be submitted for analysis.',1763115114664);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7t7s0017td3raoovmdbt','cmhyp7t7n0010td3r99fetjy8','If analyzing outbound call attempts, consider tracking connection rates and callback protocols separately from call quality metrics.',1763115114664);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7u15001jtd3rgkzop9qn','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','CRITICAL: This appears to be a voicemail greeting rather than a live customer call. If this is an agent''s voicemail, it must include: (1) Company name and regulatory status, (2) Alternative contact methods with phone numbers, (3) Expected response timeframe, (4) Emergency claims contact if applicable. Example: ''You''ve reached [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. I''m unable to take your call right now. Please leave a message or call our main office on [number]. For claims emergencies, call [claims number]. I''ll return your call within 24 hours.''',1763115115721);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7u15001ktd3rwz89xpvh','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','CRITICAL: Never use personal voicemail for customer-facing insurance lines. All customer calls must be handled through compliant call recording systems that capture interactions for regulatory purposes per FCA requirements.',1763115115721);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7u15001ltd3rzm8yme6z','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','CRITICAL: Directing customers to text messages instead of phone calls may breach accessibility requirements and Treating Customers Fairly principles - some customers cannot or prefer not to use text messaging. Always provide multiple contact options.',1763115115721);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7u15001mtd3r6eqtyksd','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','If this was intended as a live call greeting, this represents a fundamental failure to engage with the customer. Agent requires immediate retraining on basic call handling procedures, regulatory opening requirements, and professional customer service standards.',1763115115721);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7u15001ntd3rbmlrac8s','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','Escalate to compliance team immediately - this recording suggests systemic process failures that could result in regulatory action if customer calls are being handled this way.',1763115115721);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7yru002ctd3rg2r5wy7p','cmhyp7yrr0024td3rzdwke7wu','NOT APPLICABLE - This is a voicemail message, not a live customer interaction. No QA scoring or coaching can be performed on voicemail messages as there is no agent-customer dialogue, no needs discovery, no compliance requirements to fulfill, and no opportunity to demonstrate call handling skills.',1763115121867);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7yru002dtd3r8d6cvfvp','cmhyp7yrr0024td3rzdwke7wu','PROCESS NOTE: Voicemail messages should be excluded from QA scoring systems as they do not represent actual call handling performance. Only live customer interactions should be evaluated.',1763115121867);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7yru002etd3rokcd0ckr','cmhyp7yrr0024td3rzdwke7wu','FOLLOW-UP TRACKING: Ensure the promised afternoon callback is logged in the system and completed. Track whether customer returns the call or agent successfully reaches them on next attempt.',1763115121867);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7ytu002otd3r7il6dg06','cmhyp7ytr002itd3rljqj4o2c','CRITICAL: Update voicemail greeting immediately - it incorrectly identifies ''Help Bank'' instead of the correct company name. This creates customer confusion and potential compliance issues with firm identification requirements under ICOBS.',1763115121938);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7ytu002ptd3r1e02xq5w','cmhyp7ytr002itd3rljqj4o2c','Ensure voicemail greeting includes proper firm identification: ''You''ve reached [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA.'' This meets regulatory requirements even when unavailable.',1763115121938);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7ytu002qtd3rqv7g9oqt','cmhyp7ytr002itd3rljqj4o2c','Consider implementing a call routing system or backup coverage to minimize missed customer calls, especially for time-sensitive renewal inquiries.',1763115121938);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp7ytu002rtd3rdw1j3axe','cmhyp7ytr002itd3rljqj4o2c','When leaving voicemails for customers, consider mentioning the urgency of renewal timelines to encourage prompt callback and avoid coverage gaps.',1763115121938);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp80bb0037td3r1a69fv8y','cmhyp80b8002wtd3r6qwy7ngq','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: This was a voicemail, not a live call. Opening compliance requirements (firm identification with regulatory status, call recording disclosure, GDPR notice) cannot be delivered via voicemail. When customer returns the call, ensure ALL opening compliance elements are covered at the start of the live conversation.',1763115123864);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp80bb0038td3rsye1vfra','cmhyp80b8002wtd3r6qwy7ngq','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Professionalism 89): Rebecca delivered a clear, professional voicemail. To reach 9/10, consider adding a brief reference to data protection even in voicemails, such as: ''When you call back, please have your policy reference ready so we can assist you quickly and securely.'' This demonstrates proactive data protection awareness.',1763115123864);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp80bb0039td3rmu62oi4u','cmhyp80b8002wtd3r6qwy7ngq','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up 89): Good job providing the callback number and reason for contact. To reach 9/10, add a timeframe for action, e.g., ''Please call us back within the next 3 working days so we can get your quote to you while the pricing is still valid.'' This creates urgency and shows customer-focused service.',1763115123864);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp80bb003atd3ri0x5d1c0','cmhyp80b8002wtd3r6qwy7ngq','Consider leaving a brief alternative contact method in voicemails (e.g., email address or website) to give customers multiple ways to respond, improving accessibility and customer service.',1763115123864);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp80bb003btd3regxytsx0','cmhyp80b8002wtd3r6qwy7ngq','When customer calls back, verify the correct email address using DPA verification first, then confirm the new email address by having the customer spell it out to avoid future delivery issues.',1763115123864);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp84jw003rtd3r2z0tdlkr','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE CONTEXT: This was a voicemail message, not a live call. Compliance scores reflect the inability to meet regulatory requirements in this format. Consider whether voicemail is appropriate for insurance quotes requiring full disclosures.',1763115129357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp84jw003std3ry3kbq4a6','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','Voicemail Rapport (scored 5/10): The message was functional but impersonal. To reach 7/10, add warmth and personalization. Example: ''Hi Alexander, this is Keith from Pickett Insurance. Thanks for requesting a quote with us - I''ve been working on getting you the best options for your [insurance type] cover.'' This builds connection even in a voicemail.',1763115129357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp84jw003ttd3r3xhq1o5e','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','Voicemail Closing (scored 4/10): The callback request lacked urgency or value proposition. To reach 7/10, create a compelling reason to call back. Example: ''I''ve found some really competitive options for you that I think you''ll be pleased with. Give me a call on 0800-254-5171 so we can discuss how much you could save.'' This motivates action.',1763115129357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp84jw003utd3rf96y430c','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','Follow-Up Strategy (scored 6/10): Provided contact details but no timeline or alternative contact method. To reach 8/10, add specificity and options. Example: ''I''ll try you again tomorrow afternoon, but if you''d prefer, you can call me back on 0800-254-5171 or email keith@pickettinsurance.co.uk. I''m here Monday to Friday, 9 to 5.'' This gives customer control and multiple touchpoints.',1763115129357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp84jw003vtd3rv03jjkzo','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','Consider operational policy: For quote follow-ups requiring detailed discussions and mandatory disclosures, voicemail may not be the most appropriate channel. Recommend attempting live contact multiple times before leaving voicemail, or using email to send quote documents with full compliance information included.',1763115129357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8ens004std3rw3jq4w1h','cmhyp8eno004ctd3rupyyr7in','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Must include full call opening compliance script. Required elements: (1) Firm name with regulatory status: ''This is Jess calling from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes'', (3) GDPR notice: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763115142457);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8ens004ttd3rt3rqdfoe','cmhyp8eno004ctd3rupyyr7in','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 8/10): You built excellent rapport with friendly reassurance (''absolutely fine, no worries at all'') and patient repetition when asked. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. Example: ''I can see you''re setting up holiday let insurance for an investment property - that''s great, and I''m here to make sure we get you the right cover for your business needs.''',1763115142457);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8ens004utd3r0ncc0pvi','cmhyp8eno004ctd3rupyyr7in','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - 8/10): You demonstrated strong knowledge of the website journey and policy types. To reach 9/10, provide slightly more context about why the top-up policy is suitable. Example: ''The top-up policy is perfect for your situation because you already have landlord insurance for the building and long-term rental risks, and this adds the specific short-term guest liability and contents cover you need for holiday lets.''',1763115142457);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8ens004vtd3r8srh1dn2','cmhyp8eno004ctd3rupyyr7in','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 8/10): Good offer of ongoing support. To reach 9/10, be more specific about next steps and set clearer expectations. Example: ''Once you complete the online form, you''ll receive your quote immediately by email. If you''re happy to proceed, you can purchase online or call us back on [number] and we''ll process it for you. The whole journey should take about 5-10 minutes.''',1763115142457);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8i2i005etd3rq7tcffr9','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures: ''You''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We process your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13.',1763115146875);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8i2i005ftd3rokjpgpi5','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Never collect customer data (including name) before completing DPA verification and establishing lawful basis for processing. For new customers, explain why you need their information first: ''To provide you with a quote, I''ll need to collect some personal information. Is that okay with you?'' This ensures GDPR compliance.',1763115146875);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8i2i005gtd3rqt69wjhk','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - 78): You did well asking about the listing grade to understand the property type. To reach 8/10, after the customer clarified it''s NOT listed, ask follow-up questions to understand what they meant: ''No problem! Just to make sure I understand your property correctly, can you tell me what type of building it is and roughly when it was built?'' This prevents confusion and gathers essential underwriting information.',1763115146875);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8i2i005htd3rq5i5shkt','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Closing - 78): You handled the call quality issue professionally and arranged a callback. To reach 8/10, provide more specific next steps: ''Perfect, I''ll call you back in the next 2 minutes on this number. When I call back, I''ll get some details about your Airbnb property and provide you with a quote. Does that work for you?'' This sets clear expectations.',1763115146875);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8i2i005itd3rl573l0bq','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','Positive feedback: Excellent rapport building with warm tone and empathetic language (''Oh, bless you''). Your reassurance that you can help with their Airbnb property insurance built immediate confidence. Continue this approach while ensuring compliance requirements are met first.',1763115146875);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8khd0061td3rpguioxuv','cmhyp8kh9005otd3ryqqyk0jy','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Always open calls with full compliance statement including: (1) Firm name and regulatory status: ''This is Rebecca from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (3) GDPR notice appropriate to call type. This is non-negotiable and must be done on EVERY call to meet FCA and GDPR requirements.',1763115150002);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8khd0062td3rcw8q4gwk','cmhyp8kh9005otd3ryqqyk0jy','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Always conduct DPA verification BEFORE accessing or discussing any policy details. Even on callback situations, verify identity with minimum of name + date of birth. Say: ''Before I discuss your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can you confirm your full name and date of birth please?'' Accessing data without verification is a serious GDPR breach.',1763115150002);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8khd0063td3rbuk5ckv1','cmhyp8kh9005otd3ryqqyk0jy','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 910): You demonstrated excellent knowledge by clarifying the confusing credit agreement documentation and explaining the difference between drawing amount and total payable. To reach 10/10, proactively offer to send a summary email confirming the figures discussed, which would provide additional customer reassurance. Example: ''Kevin, I''ll send you a quick email summarizing what we''ve discussed today with the correct figures highlighted, so you have it for your records.''',1763115150002);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8khd0064td3rmbdal7ec','cmhyp8kh9005otd3ryqqyk0jy','Path to Excellence (TCF Compliance 910): Excellent work acknowledging the document was unclear and validating the customer''s confusion. To reach 10/10, consider escalating the feedback about confusing documentation to prevent future customer confusion. Example: ''I''m going to feed this back to our team because you''re right, that section isn''t clear. We should look at improving it for all our customers.''',1763115150002);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8rha007gtd3r8cekwoi8','cmhyp8rh5006ytd3r06rdl17n','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP - Call Opening: You must provide call recording disclosure and GDPR privacy notice at the start of every call. For new business sales, state: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This is required by GDPR Article 13 and FCA regulations. Practice this as your standard opening script.',1763115159071);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8rha007htd3rwzrj9yj7','cmhyp8rh5006ytd3r06rdl17n','Path to Excellence (Call Opening Compliance 68): You provided excellent disclosures mid-call but missed the opening requirements. To reach 8/10, integrate the call recording and GDPR notice into your greeting: ''Good afternoon, Picker Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is recorded for quality purposes. We process your data in line with our privacy policy. How can I help?'' This takes 5 seconds and ensures full compliance from the start.',1763115159071);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8rha007itd3roin68j2k','cmhyp8rh5006ytd3r06rdl17n','Path to Excellence (Professionalism 910): You demonstrated excellent professionalism throughout - polite, clear, and organized. To reach 10/10 exemplary standard, add one more layer of personalization when confirming the policy start date. For example: ''Perfect, so we''ll have you covered from the 11th November. That gives you peace of mind for your second home right when you need it.'' This shows you understand the customer''s specific situation beyond just processing the transaction.',1763115159071);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8rha007jtd3rfgn9jm0x','cmhyp8rh5006ytd3r06rdl17n','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): You built good rapport with friendly tone and efficient service. To elevate to 9/10, acknowledge the customer''s positive experience with your colleague Keith at the start: ''Lovely to hear Keith has looked after you well with that quote. Let me help you get that finalized today.'' This builds continuity and shows you value the customer relationship across your team.',1763115159071);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp8rha007ktd3rg34m0563','cmhyp8rh5006ytd3r06rdl17n','Excellent Data Protection Practices: Your handling of DPA verification, payment card security (pausing recording), and explicit consent for data storage was exemplary. This is best-in-class practice - continue this approach on every call.',1763115159071);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp989c0089td3rq8tdhiev','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. You MUST state: (1) Company name and regulatory status: ''You''re through to [Company Name], authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (2) Call recording: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes'', (3) GDPR notice appropriate to call type. This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement under ICOBS and protects both you and the customer.',1763115180817);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp989c008atd3rozjzqrsk','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Complete full DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. After taking the name, immediately ask: ''For data protection, can I take your date of birth and postcode please?'' Only after verification should you access their quote or policy details. Current practice risks GDPR breach.',1763115180817);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp989c008btd3rryqr9hv5','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Closing - 7/10): You handled the transfer well by explaining you''d check with the quotes team. To reach 8/10, provide a specific timeframe and confirm the customer''s availability. Try: ''I''ll check with our quotes team now - this should take about 2 minutes. Are you happy to hold, or would you prefer I call you back within 10 minutes?'' This gives the customer control and sets clear expectations.',1763115180817);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp989c008ctd3rb4k6qp0y','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up - 7/10): You explained the next step but didn''t confirm what happens after speaking to the quotes team. To reach 8/10, add: ''Once I''ve checked availability, I''ll either transfer you directly to complete your policy, or if everyone''s busy, I''ll arrange a callback within the hour. Does that work for you?'' This creates a complete follow-up plan.',1763115180817);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp989c008dtd3rdzb9ce4w','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - 8/10): Great use of warm language like ''Oh, bless you'' and ''Lovely'' which created a friendly atmosphere. To reach 9/10, personalize further by acknowledging their specific situation: ''Great that you''re ready to go ahead with your quote, Ben. Let me get you sorted straight away.'' This shows you''re focused on their individual need.',1763115180817);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9avq008ztd3ryq9e3ude','cmhyp9avm008ltd3r84xwfbih','EXCELLENT data protection compliance - you properly verified identity with agreement number, name, address and postcode before accessing any policy details. This is textbook DPA compliance. Keep this standard on every call.',1763115184215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9avq0090td3r127yh28q','cmhyp9avm008ltd3r84xwfbih','Strong product knowledge demonstrated when explaining the confusing pre-contract credit documentation. To reach 10/10, consider proactively offering to email a simplified payment breakdown to the broker for their customer records. Example: ''Rebecca, would it help if I emailed you a simple one-page breakdown of the payment schedule you can share with Mr. Talentire? That way he has it in plain English.''',1763115184215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9avq0091td3rc9nnr6rb','cmhyp9avm008ltd3r84xwfbih','Good rapport building with the broker partner. To elevate to 9/10, try acknowledging the broker''s role more explicitly and positioning yourself as their support partner. Example: ''I really appreciate you taking the time to call us on behalf of your customer - it shows great service on your part. Let me make sure we get this cleared up for both of you.''',1763115184215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9avq0092td3rolb65b12','cmhyp9avm008ltd3r84xwfbih','You handled the documentation confusion well and were transparent about it being a known issue. Consider escalating this feedback internally - if multiple brokers are raising the same concern about confusing documentation, this is a TCF risk that should be addressed at a process level. Document this pattern for your team leader.',1763115184215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9avq0093td3rdbn9iz9j','cmhyp9avm008ltd3r84xwfbih','The call closing was professional and friendly. To reach 9/10, consider adding a brief follow-up offer: ''If Mr. Talentire has any other questions after you explain this to him, please don''t hesitate to call us back directly.'' This reinforces your support and prevents repeat confusion.',1763115184215);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9c14009mtd3r4kkvhp80','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','CRITICAL: Always conduct DPA verification BEFORE accessing any policy data. You must verify the customer''s identity (name + date of birth minimum) before discussing policy details. This is a fundamental GDPR requirement and data breach risk. Script: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?''',1763115185704);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9c14009ntd3ra83pjg5z','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','CRITICAL: Include mandatory call opening elements every time: (1) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (2) Regulatory status: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (3) GDPR notice for renewals: ''This is a renewal so we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' These are non-negotiable FCA and GDPR requirements.',1763115185704);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9c14009otd3rjk6nx84v','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','HIGH PRIORITY: Provide mandatory disclosures for renewals including: (1) 14-day cooling-off rights: ''You''ll have 14 days to cancel from when your policy starts if you change your mind'', (2) Complaints procedure: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can complain to us and escalate to the Financial Ombudsman Service if needed.'' Required by ICOBS 6.1.5R and DISP.',1763115185704);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9c14009ptd3rhcj6pr6z','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','Path to Excellence (Closing - 7/10): You did well directing the customer to complete the renewal online and the customer was satisfied. To reach 8/10, confirm the customer''s understanding and set a specific timeframe: ''So you''ll complete that online renewal in the next few minutes, and if you haven''t heard from us within 24 hours with your policy documents, please give us a call back.'' This creates accountability and clear expectations.',1763115185704);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9c14009qtd3rqrrai9jp','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 7/10): Good job offering support if problems arise. To reach 8/10, be more specific about follow-up: ''Once you''ve completed the online process, you''ll receive a confirmation email within 10 minutes. If you don''t receive that, or if you have any questions during the process, call us back on this number and ask for Keith or any team member.'' This provides concrete milestones and reassurance.',1763115185704);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9e1w00abtd3rust2menr','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory statement: ''Good morning, you''re through to [name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We process your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.'' This is mandatory under FCA and GDPR requirements.',1763115188324);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9e1w00actd3r8jqvzwlg','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always conduct DPA verification BEFORE collecting or discussing any customer data. Ask for: full name, date of birth, and postcode/policy number. Say: ''For data protection, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Never access or record customer information without verification.',1763115188324);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9e1w00adtd3r542mgfi2','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','PROFESSIONALISM (scored 7/10): You built good rapport with friendly language, but avoid terms of endearment like ''my love'' as they may not suit all customers. To reach 8/10, maintain warmth through personalized service instead: ''When would you like the policy to start, Sianwyn?'' This keeps it professional while showing you''re engaged.',1763115188324);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9e1w00aetd3rnsjyo12o','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','CLOSING (scored 7/10): You asked if customer needed anything else, which is good. To reach 8/10, provide clearer next steps and contact details: ''So your next step is to check with your current insurer about hosting. Once confirmed, you can get a quote from our team on 0800 XXX XXXX or visit our website. Would you like me to email you those details?'' This gives the customer a clear action plan.',1763115188324);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9e1w00aftd3r0nnvhnw7','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','FOLLOW-UP (scored 7/10): You ended politely but without documenting actions. To reach 8/10, summarize and confirm: ''Just to recap - you''ll check with your electricity company about hosting cover, then contact our quotes team for a full home and annex quote. I''ll make a note on your file. Is there anything else I can clarify?'' This ensures customer understanding and creates an audit trail.',1763115188324);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9f0o00aytd3rfgag7oh6','cmhyp9f0k00altd3r62l1yhfc','COMPLIANCE: Always provide firm identification and regulatory status at the very start of the call, before any other conversation. Script: ''Hi, this is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for training and regulatory purposes.'' This must come BEFORE DPA verification.',1763115189576);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9f0o00aztd3rjx2qq629','cmhyp9f0k00altd3r62l1yhfc','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): You built good rapport with friendly, professional tone. To reach 9/10, add more empathy acknowledgment when customers identify problems. Try: ''I really appreciate you taking the time to go through this carefully and spotting that error - that attention to detail is exactly what we need. Let me get this sorted for you right away.'' This validates their effort and strengthens trust.',1763115189576);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9f0o00b0td3r1hkaeh24','cmhyp9f0k00altd3r62l1yhfc','Path to Excellence (Closing 89): You provided clear next steps which is excellent. To elevate to 9/10, add a specific timeframe and confirmation method. Example: ''I''ll call Premfina within the next hour and have the corrected documents emailed to you by end of today. Can I confirm your email address is still [email]? I''ll also follow up with a quick call once it''s sent to make sure you''ve received it.'' This adds accountability and reassurance.',1763115189576);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9f0o00b1td3r7m0k2qio','cmhyp9f0k00altd3r62l1yhfc','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You correctly identified the policy price and discrepancy. To reach 9/10, proactively explain what caused the error to build customer confidence. Example: ''This looks like Premfina may have pulled an incorrect figure from their system - your actual policy premium is 326, so over 11 months with their interest, it should be around 350 total, not 1,326. I''ll ensure they have the correct figure before resending.''',1763115189576);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bltd3rqe5fhhfa','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. Must state: ''Good afternoon, this is Jess calling from Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement.',1763115190314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bmtd3rlum74605','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Enhance DPA verification by collecting TWO identifiers (name + date of birth OR postcode). Current practice of name-only verification is insufficient. Script: ''For data protection, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' This must be completed BEFORE accessing any policy details.',1763115190314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bntd3r5f63ro56','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','HIGH PRIORITY: Include complaints procedure disclosure at call close. Script: ''If you ever need to make a complaint, you can contact us and we''ll provide our complaints procedure. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer the matter to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' Required by DISP 1.2.',1763115190314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9fl600botd3rykz42cxh','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','Path to Excellence (Rapport - 8/10): You built good rapport with polite, reassuring language like ''that''s absolutely fine'' throughout. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. Example: ''I can see you''re running an Airbnb, that''s great - we''ll make sure your policy properly covers that arrangement so you''re fully protected.'' This shows deeper engagement with their circumstances.',1763115190314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bptd3ro8xfpnlr','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - 8/10): You clearly explained next steps and timeline. To reach 9/10, confirm the communication method and set a specific expectation. Example: ''I''ll email your renewal quote to [email] by 5pm today. If you haven''t received it by tomorrow morning, please give us a call on [number]. Does that work for you?'' This creates accountability and reassures the customer.',1763115190314);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9gsx00cbtd3r1z5qnjq9','cmhyp9gsu00bxtd3re51zdp4k','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance elements. Even on callback/service calls, you must state: ''This is [Agent Name] calling from [Company Name], authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes.'' This is non-negotiable for regulatory compliance and protects both you and the customer.',1763115191890);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9gsx00cctd3r2083cveh','cmhyp9gsu00bxtd3re51zdp4k','COMPLIANCE: When discussing policy changes, cancellations, or refunds, briefly mention complaints rights: ''If you have any concerns about how this has been handled, we have a complaints procedure and you can contact the Financial Ombudsman Service if needed.'' This ensures customers know their rights under DISP requirements.',1763115191890);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9gsx00cdtd3renzqlxtp','cmhyp9gsu00bxtd3re51zdp4k','Path to Excellence (Professionalism - currently 8/10): You demonstrated good transparency about the refund uncertainty. To reach 9/10, provide even more proactive clarity: ''Let me check the exact refund status with accounts right now so I can give you a definite answer before we end this call. Would you mind holding for 30 seconds?'' This shows exceptional customer service by removing uncertainty immediately.',1763115191890);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9gsx00cetd3reucfkub4','cmhyp9gsu00bxtd3re51zdp4k','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): You did well setting expectations for accounts contact. To reach 9/10, provide more specific details: ''You''ll receive an email from our accounts team by close of business tomorrow at the latest with your refund confirmation. The refund will show in your account within 5-7 working days. I''ll also send you a summary email right now with my direct extension and all the reference numbers.'' This gives the customer complete clarity and confidence.',1763115191890);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9je100cwtd3rkfk6njw1','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE CONTEXT: This call is an internal colleague-to-colleague handover, NOT a customer-facing call. The compliance framework (call opening, DPA verification, disclosures) does not apply to internal communications. However, ensure all compliance elements ARE present when the agent calls the customer back.',1763115195241);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9je100cxtd3rkj1mwh5d','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','PROFESSIONALISM (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: You handled the internal handover well and showed good teamwork. To reach 8/10, demonstrate more confidence in your record-keeping and customer history. Instead of saying ''I''m not sure which one he means'' or ''I think it was Callum'', check the CRM thoroughly before taking the call. Example: ''I''ve checked the notes - I spoke to him yesterday about the top-up quote, reference XYZ123. I''ll pull that up and call him right back.''',1763115195241);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9je100cytd3rwcqp1wns','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','Improve system knowledge and CRM navigation to quickly locate customer quotes and history. The hesitation about which quote and who spoke to the customer suggests gaps in record-keeping or system familiarity.',1763115195241);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9je100cztd3r20dil243','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','Address the email system issues urgently - multiple mentions of emails bouncing, going to archive, or being deleted indicates a critical operational problem that affects customer service and compliance (customers not receiving policy documents).',1763115195241);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9je100d0td3rpxfpp60g','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','When calling the customer back, ensure full compliance: firm identification, call recording disclosure, DPA verification BEFORE accessing policy data, and all mandatory disclosures if proceeding with a sale.',1763115195241);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9k5x00dgtd3rg6ggigce','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always complete DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. Required process: (1) Request policy reference, (2) Ask for full name AND date of birth, (3) Verify both match system, (4) THEN access policy details. This is a fundamental GDPR requirement and data breach risk.',1763115196245);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9k5x00dhtd3r6zl3ftdb','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Include mandatory call opening elements in EVERY call: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This meets FCA and ICOBS requirements.',1763115196245);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9k5x00ditd3run2r5w9e','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','PROFESSIONALISM - Path to Excellence: You demonstrated good rapport and warmth (8/10), but avoid overly familiar terms like ''my love'' which can be perceived as unprofessional or inappropriate in a regulated financial services environment. To reach 9/10, maintain warmth through personalized service and empathy while keeping language professional. Example: ''Is that okay with you, Dan?'' or ''Does that work for you?'' instead of ''All right, my love?''',1763115196245);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9k5x00djtd3rqlqn050g','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','Continue your excellent practice of setting clear expectations during transfers - mentioning the colleague''s name (Rebecca) and explaining the process helps customer feel valued and informed.',1763115196245);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9k5x00dktd3rgpcdz07i','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','FOLLOW-UP - Path to Excellence: You scored 8/10 for clearly explaining the transfer process. To reach 9/10, add a brief summary of what the specialist will help with: ''Rebecca from our quotes team will be able to discuss the details of your quote and answer any questions about the pricing and cover options. I''ll transfer you now.''',1763115196245);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9t3u00e7td3rkiy0hver','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Must provide full regulatory call opening. Required script: ''Good morning/afternoon, this is [Full Name] calling from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763115207834);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9t3u00e8td3r3p5jgt2p','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Must complete DPA verification BEFORE collecting any customer data. Required script: ''Before I can help you today, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Never collect data without establishing lawful basis first - this is a GDPR Article 6 requirement.',1763115207834);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9t3u00e9td3rketzowip','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','PROFESSIONALISM - Path to Excellence (Current: 7/10): You built excellent rapport, but the opening was too casual for a regulated financial services call. You used ''Hi, lovelies'' and ''Ess'' instead of your full professional name. To reach 8/10: Use a professional greeting while maintaining warmth: ''Good afternoon, this is Esme calling from Pikl Insurance. How can I help you today?'' This balances professionalism with approachability. The term ''lovelies'' and repeated use of ''lovely'' throughout, while friendly, may not suit all customers in a professional insurance context.',1763115207834);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9t3u00eatd3rtgio4jso','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','RAPPORT - Path to Excellence (Current: 9/10): Outstanding rapport building throughout - you were warm, reassuring, and made the customer feel comfortable with phrases like ''that''s absolutely fine'' and ''no worries at all.'' To reach 10/10: Add one personalized comment that shows you''ve really listened to their specific situation. For example: ''It sounds like you''ve done a lot of work preparing the cottage for rental - we''ll make sure we get you the right cover to protect that investment.'' This shows deeper engagement with their circumstances.',1763115207834);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9t3u00ebtd3r5cnj7t40','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','NEEDS DISCOVERY - Path to Excellence (Current: 8/10): You asked good clarifying questions about property type, insurance scope, and timeline. To reach 9/10: Ask one additional probing question about their rental plans to ensure comprehensive coverage. For example: ''You mentioned you''re preparing for short-term rentals - will this be holiday lets or longer-term tenancies? This helps us ensure you have the right liability cover in place.'' This demonstrates thorough risk assessment.',1763115207834);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9waz00eztd3rloe8c97m','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance (scored 7/10): You provided call recording disclosure, which is good. However, you must state the firm''s full regulatory status at the start of every call. To reach 8/10, say: ''Hi, it''s Rebecca from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This is required by ICOBS 4.5.1R and builds customer confidence.',1763115211979);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9waz00f0td3rgviq0r5d','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','CRITICAL - Mandatory Disclosures (scored 4/10): Multiple required disclosures were missing. You correctly stated non-advised status, but failed to explain: (1) 14-day cooling-off rights, (2) complaints procedure and FOS rights, (3) detailed price breakdown with IPT and fees. To reach 6/10, add: ''You have 14 days to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. If you''re unhappy, we have a complaints procedure and you can escalate to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' For 8/10, provide this naturally throughout the conversation.',1763115211979);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9waz00f1td3rpqe0o9vj','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','CRITICAL - Sales Process Compliance (scored 5/10): You attempted to proceed with a sale without establishing whether the customer could legally purchase the policy due to existing insurance. To reach 7/10, conduct thorough fact-finding BEFORE quoting: ''Before we proceed, I need to understand your current insurance arrangements. Do you have any existing buildings or contents insurance on this property? Can you check your mortgage documents to confirm?'' This prevents mis-selling and regulatory breaches.',1763115211979);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9waz00f2td3r3u6w943d','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','Needs Discovery (scored 6/10): You asked basic questions but missed critical information about the customer''s existing insurance situation until late in the call. To reach 8/10, use a structured discovery approach at the start: ''Let me understand your current situation. You mentioned this is a rental property - do you currently have any insurance in place? What about your mortgage requirements?'' This would have identified the dual insurance issue immediately.',1763115211979);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9waz00f3td3rlg5jp26r','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','Product Knowledge (scored 7/10): You understood dual insurance rules but struggled to explain mortgage-linked insurance clearly, using personal anecdotes instead of professional guidance. To reach 8/10, provide authoritative explanations: ''Mortgage lenders typically require buildings insurance, but this is arranged separately by you as the property owner. Your mortgage offer will specify this requirement. Let me help you check your mortgage documents to confirm what''s in place.'' This demonstrates expertise and helps the customer.',1763115211979);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyp9waz00f4td3rwf260up0','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','Closing & Follow-Up (both scored 6/10): The call ended abruptly without clear next steps or documentation of the customer''s complex situation. To reach 8/10, provide structured closure: ''I understand you need to check your existing insurance arrangements, particularly regarding your mortgage and the probate situation. I''ll save this quote until [specific date]. Can I send you an email outlining what you need to check with your mortgage provider? Let''s schedule a follow-up call for [specific date/time] once you have that information.'' This shows professionalism and ensures the customer knows exactly what to do next.',1763115211979);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa0nz00fstd3rg4eii5b2','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance statement: ''Good morning, this is [name] from Tickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We process your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.'' This is a non-negotiable regulatory requirement under FCA rules and GDPR.',1763115217632);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa0nz00fttd3r167focv1','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always conduct DPA verification (name + date of birth minimum) BEFORE discussing any policy details or taking personal information like email addresses. This is a fundamental data protection requirement under GDPR and company policy.',1763115217632);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa0nz00futd3rtps0dosn','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','CLOSING - Path to Excellence (78): You handled the technical issue professionally and set follow-up expectations. To reach 8/10, provide more specific timeframes and action steps. Instead of ''at some point this afternoon, early this afternoon,'' say: ''I''ll personally call you back by 2pm today with a solution, and you''ll also receive a confirmation email within the hour with my direct contact details.'' This gives the customer concrete expectations and demonstrates ownership.',1763115217632);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa0nz00fvtd3r31hk3r7b','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','Continue your excellent practice of explaining product concepts clearly (top-up vs all-in-one) and warning customers about potential dual insurance - this demonstrates strong TCF compliance and customer-first thinking.',1763115217632);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa0nz00fwtd3r6sb32h4g','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','When technical issues arise, document the specific problem and customer details immediately in the CRM to ensure seamless handover if a colleague needs to follow up.',1763115217632);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa7gw00gitd3rnzgwryf6','cmhypa7gs00g4td3r478tnsw7','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with call recording disclosure. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement under ICOBS and must be stated before proceeding with the call.',1763115226449);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa7gw00gjtd3r2fg6s1nq','cmhypa7gs00g4td3r478tnsw7','PROFESSIONALISM - Path to Excellence (78): You handled the poor line quality well with patience and apologies. To reach 8/10, develop a proactive strategy for poor connections. Try: ''I''m noticing we have a challenging line today. Would you prefer I call you back on a different number, or shall we continue? I want to make sure you can hear all the important policy details clearly.'' This shows customer care and ensures compliance with information provision requirements.',1763115226449);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa7gw00gktd3rw12doiks','cmhypa7gs00g4td3r478tnsw7','RAPPORT - Path to Excellence (89): You built solid rapport through patience and helpfulness. To reach 9/10, add more personalized touches based on the customer''s specific situation. For example, when she mentioned guests who pay her, you could have said: ''That''s great that the guest top-up is working well for you. If your guest arrangements ever change, just let us know and we can adjust your cover accordingly.'' This shows you''re listening and care about her specific needs.',1763115226449);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa7gw00gltd3rcdnqswvs','cmhypa7gs00g4td3r478tnsw7','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE - Path to Excellence (89): You demonstrated strong knowledge of policy features and finance terms. To reach 9/10, proactively explain the value of features rather than just listing them. For example: ''The blanket cover of up to 1 million for buildings gives you peace of mind - even if your rebuild costs increase unexpectedly due to market changes, you''re protected well beyond your sum insured.'' This helps customers understand why features matter to them.',1763115226449);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypa7gw00gmtd3rrmmkea1d','cmhypa7gs00g4td3r478tnsw7','Consider adding a brief GDPR acknowledgment for renewal calls, such as: ''As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' While not strictly required for renewals, it demonstrates best practice data protection awareness.',1763115226449);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypaa5700h7td3r3edvtnnd','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You must open every call with required regulatory disclosures at the START of the call, not midway through. Required opening: ''Good morning, this is Keith calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This protects both the customer and the firm from regulatory breaches.',1763115229915);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypaa5700h8td3rs5fznlse','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','Professionalism - Managing Difficult Call Conditions: While you handled the customer''s distractions professionally by being patient, you scored 5/10 because the call quality was significantly compromised. To reach 7/10, politely acknowledge the distraction and offer to reschedule: ''I can hear you''re quite busy at the moment. Would it be better if I called you back at a more convenient time? This is important information about your insurance.'' This shows respect for the customer while ensuring they can focus on critical policy decisions.',1763115229915);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypaa5700h9td3rcrumo9d1','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','Needs Discovery Enhancement: You scored 7/10 for identifying the letting type change, which was excellent. To reach 8/10, probe deeper with follow-up questions: ''You mentioned changing from short-term to long-term letting. Can I just check - is this a single tenant on an AST agreement? And how long is the tenancy term?'' This ensures you capture all relevant underwriting information and demonstrate thoroughness.',1763115229915);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypaa5700hatd3rzoly586e','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','TCF Compliance - Customer Understanding: You scored 7/10 for fair treatment. To reach 8/10, pause after key information and check understanding: ''I''ve just explained the change to your policy and the new price. Can I check that all makes sense, and do you have any questions before we proceed?'' This ensures the customer isn''t being rushed and fully understands what they''re purchasing.',1763115229915);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypaa5700hbtd3rj0dbjbmj','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','Mandatory Disclosures - FOS Rights: While you mentioned the complaints number, you didn''t explicitly state Financial Ombudsman Service rights. To reach 8/10, add: ''If we can''t resolve your complaint within 8 weeks, or you''re unhappy with our response, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This is a regulatory requirement under DISP 1.2.',1763115229915);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypafou00i0td3rb3gisqmf','cmhypafop00hktd3rguq4kpkn','CALL OPENING COMPLIANCE (78): You identified the company name clearly, which is excellent. To reach 8/10, add a brief call recording disclosure at the start: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes.'' While renewals don''t require full GDPR notices, this disclosure is still required for all calls under FCA guidelines.',1763115237103);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypafou00i1td3rq9gitroc','cmhypafop00hktd3rguq4kpkn','RAPPORT BUILDING (89): You built good rapport with polite language and used the customer''s name effectively. To reach 9/10, incorporate more personalized acknowledgment of their specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''ve been with us for another year with your holiday let business - thank you for your continued trust. Let''s make sure everything still fits your needs perfectly.''',1763115237103);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypafou00i2td3r450a9qm8','cmhypafop00hktd3rguq4kpkn','NEEDS DISCOVERY (89): Excellent work clarifying the property usage and guest numbers. To elevate to 9/10, consider asking one additional open question about changes to their business: ''Have there been any changes to how you operate the holiday let this year, such as booking platforms, guest types, or rental periods?'' This could uncover additional coverage needs.',1763115237103);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypafou00i3td3rr1h9sn5l','cmhypafop00hktd3rguq4kpkn','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE (89): You demonstrated solid understanding of the policy components. To reach 9/10, provide more context when explaining coverage: ''Your public liability of 5 million covers you if a guest is injured or their property is damaged during their stay - this is particularly important for holiday lets as guests can make claims for accidents on the premises.''',1763115237103);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypafou00i4td3rv2kurncg','cmhypafop00hktd3rguq4kpkn','PROFESSIONALISM (89): Your communication was consistently professional and courteous. To reach 9/10, work on smoother transitions between sections. The phrase ''Calm down. Right.'' at timestamp 12:10 appears unclear - ensure all language is crystal clear and avoid any phrases that could be misinterpreted.',1763115237103);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahie00jctd3rjusm3byj','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must provide call recording disclosure at call opening. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement under ICOBS 2.2.3R.',1763115239463);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahie00jdtd3rxv85dg8b','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must state regulatory status at call opening. Required script: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This is mandatory under ICOBS 4.5.1R to ensure customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm.',1763115239463);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahie00jetd3r2cg8sf6n','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','HIGH PRIORITY COMPLIANCE: Provide GDPR privacy notice at call opening. For existing customer service calls, a brief acknowledgment is acceptable: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy'' or ''We hold your details on file from your previous inquiry.''',1763115239463);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahie00jftd3rtp3ien5l','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','Product Knowledge - Path to Excellence (78): You demonstrated good understanding of contents vs buildings insurance and appropriately sought clarification when unsure. To reach 8/10, develop deeper knowledge of landlord insurance products and leasehold scenarios. When you encounter a ''gap'' situation like this, confidently explain: ''In leasehold properties where the freeholder covers buildings and you''re letting unfurnished, you''d typically need landlord''s liability insurance and potentially fixtures/fittings cover. While we don''t offer this specific product, I can recommend specialists.'' This shows expertise even when declining business.',1763115239463);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahie00jgtd3ra8311ieh','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','Closing Technique - Path to Excellence (78): You handled the decline well and provided alternatives, which is excellent. To reach 8/10, be more definitive and structured in your explanation. Instead of ''it kind of sounds like it''s not something we could insure,'' say: ''Based on what you''ve described, this falls outside our product range because [clear reason]. However, I''ve identified two specialist providers who focus on this exact scenario. Would you like their details?'' This provides clarity and confidence while still helping the customer.',1763115239463);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahib00irtd3rhxlt2and','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must provide call opening compliance elements. Start every call with: ''Good afternoon, Pickle Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. We''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. How can I help you today?'' This is a regulatory requirement under ICOBS and GDPR.',1763115239460);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahib00istd3ryebwhvz8','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge 78): You demonstrated good understanding of leasehold vs freehold responsibilities and correctly consulted a colleague on complex matters. To reach 8/10, eliminate contradictory statements like ''it would be an all in one policy... two separate policies completely.'' Practice explaining the host top-up structure: ''You''ll need TWO separate policies: 1) Contents insurance for your belongings, and 2) Our Host Top-Up for 99.99 which adds holiday let liability cover. They work together but are purchased separately.''',1763115239460);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahib00ittd3rtg966efj','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Closing 67): You helped clarify the customer''s options but ended abruptly. To reach 7/10, provide clear next steps: ''So to summarize, you''ll need contents insurance plus our 99.99 host top-up. You can get quotes for both at pickle.co.uk. Would you like me to email you a summary of what we discussed today, or do you have any other questions before you go online?''',1763115239460);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahib00iutd3rji5kn4b5','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up 67): Currently no follow-up was offered. To reach 7/10, always offer to send information: ''Can I take your email address to send you a summary of our products and a link to get your quote? I can also include our product guide for holiday let insurance.'' This keeps the customer engaged and provides a reference point.',1763115239460);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypahib00ivtd3rfjstxpj3','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','Improve clarity when explaining product structure - avoid contradictory statements. Use numbered lists: ''You need two things: Number 1, contents insurance. Number 2, our host top-up for 99.99.'' This prevents customer confusion and reduces repeat explanations.',1763115239460);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00k8td3rzr94tw34','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always provide full firm identification at call opening including ''authorized and regulated by the FCA'' statement. This is a mandatory ICOBS requirement for all insurance calls. Script: ''Good morning, I''m Will calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.''',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00k9td3r8d07xw0m','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Provide GDPR privacy notice at start of new business calls. Required by GDPR Article 13. Script: ''Before we proceed, I need to let you know we collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or I can send it to you.''',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00katd3r0g5mowsl','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','HIGH PRIORITY COMPLIANCE: Always explain 14-day cooling-off rights when selling new policies (ICOBS 7.1.4R). Script after accepting payment: ''Just to confirm, you have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is your cooling-off period.''',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00kbtd3rw54x3axw','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery - scored 7/10): You confirmed no changes to requirements, which was good. To reach 8/10, probe more deeply even on callback situations. Example: ''Great that nothing''s changed. Just to double-check - you mentioned unlimited hosting. Can you tell me roughly how many days per month you expect to host guests? This helps me ensure the cover is exactly right.'' This builds confidence and catches potential issues early.',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00kctd3rdrk1r9ta','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','Path to Excellence (Closing - scored 7/10): The subsidence issue prevented completion, but you handled it professionally. To reach 8/10, conduct full underwriting checks BEFORE presenting quotes to avoid customer disappointment. When issues arise, provide more specific timelines: ''I''ll call the insurer within the next 30 minutes and aim to call you back by [specific time]. If it takes longer, I''ll text you an update.''',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00kdtd3r7oji2k65','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','PROCESS IMPROVEMENT: The subsidence postcode issue should have been identified during initial quote preparation. Implement a checklist to verify all underwriting requirements (subsidence, flood zones, claims history) before presenting quotes to customers. This prevents customer frustration and demonstrates professionalism.',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypalxd00ketd3rj2kk38a4','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge - scored 8/10): Excellent explanation of blanket cover, excesses, and exclusions. To reach 9/10, proactively explain WHY these features benefit the customer. Example: ''The blanket 1m cover is particularly valuable for you because with the annex rental income, you want to ensure full rebuild protection without worrying about sum insured limits.''',1763115245186);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb2rt00l2td3rngs40tlb','cmhypb2ro00kntd3r78ytjcdd','COMPLIANCE GAP - Call Opening: At the start of the call, you identified the company but missed two critical disclosures: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'' and (2) ''We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' While you mentioned FCA authorization later at timestamp 835, best practice is to include this in your opening script. To reach 8/10, add to your greeting: ''Good afternoon, Pickle Insurance in partnership with Go Compare, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded. This is Rebecca, how can I help?''',1763115267017);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb2rt00l3td3r3qg49c8b','cmhypb2ro00kntd3r78ytjcdd','Rapport Building (8/10  9/10): You built good rapport with professional, friendly communication and showed empathy when correcting the price in the customer''s favor (''at least it saved you a bit of money''). To reach 9/10, incorporate more personalized conversation based on the customer''s specific situation. For example, when discussing the Airbnb annex, you could say: ''That''s great you''re doing Airbnb hosting - it''s really important we get the right cover for both your home and your guests, so let me make sure everything is protected properly for you.''',1763115267017);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb2rt00l4td3rdzm1hkbb','cmhypb2ro00kntd3r78ytjcdd','Product Knowledge (9/10  10/10): Excellent demonstration of knowledge across buildings, contents, hosting top-up, and add-on products. You explained coverage limits, excesses, and exclusions clearly. To reach 10/10, consider proactively explaining why certain exclusions exist to add educational value. For example: ''Storm damage to driveways isn''t covered because they''re exposed surfaces that naturally wear over time - the policy focuses on sudden, unexpected damage to the main structure.''',1763115267017);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb2rt00l5td3rgn93f7ln','cmhypb2ro00kntd3r78ytjcdd','Sales Process Compliance (9/10  10/10): You conducted thorough needs assessment and eligibility verification, which was excellent for this specialist product. To reach 10/10, when explaining the rebuild value (timestamp 346), add more customer education: ''The website calculated 657,000 based on your property details. This is the cost to completely rebuild if destroyed, not the market value. If you''ve made significant improvements or extensions, you might want to get a professional valuation to ensure you''re fully covered.''',1763115267017);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb2rt00l6td3rca0zha2f','cmhypb2ro00kntd3r78ytjcdd','Follow-Up (9/10  10/10): Excellent - you clearly explained document delivery, Premfina next steps, and provided your name for future contact. To reach 10/10, add one more proactive touchpoint: ''I''ll also send you a quick email summary of what we discussed today, including your policy start date and the key coverage points. If you have any questions when you review the documents, just reply to that email or call us on [number].''',1763115267017);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb4c600lqtd3ro50b4vml','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You must state call recording disclosure at the start of every call. Say immediately after greeting: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a non-negotiable FCA requirement. Current score: 6/10. To reach 8/10: Add call recording disclosure. To reach 10/10: Also include full GDPR notice for new business calls.',1763115269047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb4c600lrtd3rcl78tf5f','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','CRITICAL - Mandatory Disclosures: You missed several required disclosures when providing the quote. You MUST explain: (1) 14-day cooling-off rights: ''You have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind''; (2) Complaints procedure: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can complain to us and if not satisfied, refer to the Financial Ombudsman Service''; (3) Price breakdown: Separate premium, IPT, and any fees. Current score: 5/10. Adding these three elements would bring you to 9/10.',1763115269047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb4c600lstd3rl95gq7lr','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','Closing Technique - Path to Excellence: You handled the price objection professionally by offering to save the quote (good baseline = 7/10). To reach 8/10: Acknowledge the competitor price and explore value differences: ''I understand Direct Line is 6 cheaper. Let me check what our policy includes that might add value - do you know if their policy includes accidental damage or legal expenses?'' To reach 9/10: Create urgency or add value: ''The price is guaranteed for 30 days, but I could also check if adding home emergency cover might give you better overall value than their basic policy.''',1763115269047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb4c600lttd3rlr0prfxl','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','Sales Process - Price Transparency: When quoting prices, always break down: ''The total is 175.88, which includes X premium, X Insurance Premium Tax, and X broker fee.'' This meets ICOBS transparency requirements and builds trust. Current score: 6/10. Adding clear breakdown would reach 8/10.',1763115269047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypb4c600lutd3rnwbm0cay','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','Needs Discovery - Excellent Work: You conducted thorough property and tenancy verification (8/10 performance). To reach 9/10: Add one probing question about customer priorities: ''What''s most important to you in your landlord insurance - price, claims service, or comprehensive cover?'' This helps position value over price and shows deeper customer focus.',1763115269047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypbe4300mjtd3r3odau8e5','cmhypbe3z00m3td3ry7u0hua5','EXCELLENT RAPPORT BUILDING (9/10): Keith demonstrated outstanding rapport throughout the call with humor, empathy, and patience. He acknowledged the customer''s confusion (''It is a little bit. Although, I mean...''), used humor about Welsh pronunciation, and showed genuine care when the customer mentioned her father''s passing. To reach 10/10, consider adding one more personalized touch at the end, such as: ''I hope sorting this insurance out takes some of the stress off during what must be a difficult time managing your father''s estate. We''re here if you need anything else.''',1763115281715);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypbe4300mktd3r91ryr4v7','cmhypbe3z00m3td3ry7u0hua5','STRONG NEEDS DISCOVERY (8/10): Keith conducted thorough fact-finding and adapted well when the customer revealed she was new to short-term letting. He asked relevant questions about hosting plans and occupancy. To reach 9/10, probe slightly deeper into the customer''s business plans earlier in the call. For example, after she mentions planning to do hosting: ''That''s great - have you thought about how many weeks per year you''re planning to let it out? This helps me ensure we''re recommending the right level of cover for your situation.''',1763115281715);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypbe4300mltd3rir79g6pe','cmhypbe3z00m3td3ry7u0hua5','EXCELLENT PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE (9/10): Keith demonstrated expert knowledge of complex products including guest cover, blanket cover limitations, and policy exclusions. He explained technical concepts clearly (e.g., contents vs buildings definition). To reach 10/10, when explaining the seven-bedroom limitation, add more proactive guidance: ''Because you have seven bedrooms, you won''t get the blanket cover buffer. Given the property value, you might want to consider increasing your buildings sum insured by 10-15% as a safety margin - would you like me to quote that option?''',1763115281715);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypbe4300mmtd3rv5ntltim','cmhypbe3z00m3td3ry7u0hua5','STRONG CLOSING (9/10): Keith secured commitment smoothly and handled the Aviva bedroom restriction professionally by putting the customer on hold to verify rather than proceeding with uncertainty. To reach 10/10, add a confidence-building summary before payment: ''Just to confirm, you''re fully covered for buildings, contents, and guest hosting from November 8th. You''ve got 5 million public liability for guests, and all the accidental and malicious damage cover you need. You''re in great hands with Aviva.''',1763115281715);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhypbe4300mntd3rfn7dpuzy','cmhypbe3z00m3td3ry7u0hua5','CALL OPENING COMPLIANCE (8/10): Keith identified the firm clearly but did not provide an explicit call recording disclosure or GDPR privacy notice at the opening. For new business sales, full compliance requires: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Before we start, I need to let you know that we''ll collect your personal data to provide your insurance quote. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data at any time. Our full privacy policy is on our website.'' Add this immediately after the greeting to reach 10/10.',1763115281715);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7rqc00nbtd3rdkwbxgkk','cmhyq7rqa00n8td3r6gga97pj','CRITICAL: No call content available for assessment. This appears to be a technical issue with call recording or transcript generation.',1763116792357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7rqc00nctd3rcbuvfmz9','cmhyq7rqa00n8td3r6gga97pj','Ensure all calls are properly recorded and transcribed for quality assurance and regulatory compliance purposes.',1763116792357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7rqc00ndtd3r39a6dvf3','cmhyq7rqa00n8td3r6gga97pj','If this is a system test, please provide a complete call transcript with agent and customer dialogue for meaningful QA analysis.',1763116792357);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7xny00nvtd3rke1shzo0','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always provide call recording disclosure immediately after greeting. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a mandatory FCA requirement under ICOBS.',1763116800046);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7xny00nwtd3rowbz7jyl','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: State regulatory status in opening: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This is required under ICOBS 4.5.2R to ensure customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm.',1763116800046);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7xny00nxtd3rdqkepgns','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','COMPLIANCE: Provide GDPR privacy notice appropriate to call type. For new business: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.''',1763116800046);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7xny00nytd3rx3i92rc3','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','Rapport (7/10 - Path to 8/10): You provided a warm, professional greeting which is excellent. To reach 8/10, ensure you complete the full compliant opening before attempting to discover needs. Example: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?''',1763116800046);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq7xny00nztd3ro698aw2t','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','When customers don''t respond initially, consider waiting 2-3 seconds before the second attempt, then if still no response, try: ''I''m having trouble hearing you - can you hear me okay?'' This shows patience and troubleshoots the issue.',1763116800046);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq82f300ogtd3r3sv23t5h','cmhyq82f000o8td3rnyg3gqll','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with required regulatory disclosures. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to Jess at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is mandatory under FCA regulations and GDPR.',1763116806207);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq82f300ohtd3rdsn5yqho','cmhyq82f000o8td3rnyg3gqll','Path to Excellence (Professionalism 89): You handled the technical issue professionally and calmly. To reach 9/10, add reassurance about callback timing. Example: ''I''ll call you back within the next 2 minutes on this number. If I can''t reach you, I''ll try again in 10 minutes. Does that work for you?''',1763116806207);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq82f300oitd3rtzm1w87v','cmhyq82f000o8td3rnyg3gqll','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 89): Good job committing to call back. To elevate to 9/10, confirm the callback number and get customer agreement. Example: ''I''ll ring you back on [number ending in XXX] in just a moment. Is that the best number to reach you on?''',1763116806207);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq82f300ojtd3rd66eevig','cmhyq82f000o8td3rnyg3gqll','Technical issue handling was excellent - you remained calm and solution-focused. Continue this approach when facing unexpected call challenges.',1763116806207);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq85ov00oxtd3rranbkqgt','cmhyq85os00ootd3r8iwgpwmj','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Every call must open with firm identification, regulatory status, and call recording disclosure. Even on reconnected calls, you must state: ''This is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes.'' This is non-negotiable under FCA rules.',1763116810447);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq85ov00oytd3r5o4z0271','cmhyq85os00ootd3r8iwgpwmj','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 89): You did well setting clear callback expectations (10-20 minutes). To reach 9/10, confirm the customer''s preferred contact number and offer an alternative if the timeframe doesn''t work: ''I have you down on 07XXX XXX XXX - is that still the best number? And if 10-20 minutes doesn''t suit, I can schedule a specific time that works better for you.''',1763116810447);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq85ov00oztd3rts4e8t9o','cmhyq85os00ootd3r8iwgpwmj','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): Good empathy shown for the disconnection. To elevate to 9/10, acknowledge the customer''s original reason for calling: ''I''m sorry about the disconnection, Mark. I know you were calling about [original query]. We''ll make sure the next available advisor has all your details so you don''t need to repeat yourself.''',1763116810447);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq85ov00p0td3rl42khbd2','cmhyq85os00ootd3r8iwgpwmj','Path to Excellence (Professionalism 89): Your tone was warm and professional. To reach 9/10, avoid filler words like ''kind of'' when giving timeframes. Say confidently: ''The next available advisor will call you back in approximately 10 to 20 minutes.''',1763116810447);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8jdo00pqtd3r7ltjr7ut','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Never access or discuss policy information without first completing DPA verification (name + DOB minimum). This is a fundamental GDPR requirement and must be done on every call before accessing customer data. Score: 0/10 requires immediate remediation and retraining.',1763116828189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8jdo00prtd3rqzcwzfye','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE BREACH: Every call must open with mandatory disclosures: (1) Firm identification (''This is [Agent] from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA''), (2) Call recording notice (''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes''), (3) GDPR notice appropriate to call type. This is non-negotiable regulatory requirement. Score: 0/10 requires immediate remediation.',1763116828189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00pstd3r4bh3zi44','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','PROFESSIONALISM FAILURE: The phrase ''I don''t know what he''s going on about then'' is completely unprofessional and dismissive. Always maintain respectful, professional language. Instead say: ''Let me review your account to understand the premium changes and explain them clearly to you.'' Score: 2/10 requires coaching on professional communication standards.',1763116828189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00pttd3r23xdld5y','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','NEEDS DISCOVERY: The confusion about ''he'' vs the actual customer needs clarification. Always confirm: ''Am I speaking with the policyholder [Name]?'' and ''How can I help you today?'' to establish clear understanding of the customer and their needs. Score: 2/10.',1763116828189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00putd3rmun5782n','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','CALL STRUCTURE: Implement proper call opening, middle, and closing structure. Opening must include compliance elements, middle should address customer needs with clear explanations, closing must summarize actions and confirm customer satisfaction. This call had no discernible structure. Score: 2/10 across multiple dimensions.',1763116828189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8m1l00qftd3rtra3cf4h','cmhyq8m1i00q4td3r1s1o8a2v','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must include proper call opening with all required elements: (1) Firm identification with regulatory status: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (3) GDPR notice appropriate for call type. For service calls, brief acknowledgment is acceptable: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is a fundamental regulatory requirement under FCA rules and GDPR.',1763116831641);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8m1l00qgtd3r6loa4qva','cmhyq8m1i00q4td3r1s1o8a2v','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up scored 7/10): You handled the immediate query well and the customer seemed satisfied. To reach 8/10, add a clear invitation for further support. For example: ''If you have any issues completing the form or need any other help, just give us a call back and we''ll be happy to assist.'' This ensures the customer knows support is available and improves their experience.',1763116831641);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8m1l00qhtd3r2a10870q','cmhyq8m1i00q4td3r1s1o8a2v','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge scored 8/10): You demonstrated solid understanding of the online form structure and guided the customer effectively through their specific annex/separate building scenario. To reach 9/10, consider being more definitive in your guidance rather than using phrases like ''I think'' or ''probably''. For example: ''Yes, select primary residence for your main home. The next section will ask about the annex specifically where you can provide details about the separate building.'' This builds greater customer confidence.',1763116831641);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8m1l00qitd3r4hz994xh','cmhyq8m1i00q4td3r1s1o8a2v','Consider documenting this interaction type in your CRM system - customer attempting online quote for host insurance with annex property. This helps track customer journey and any follow-up needs if they don''t complete the online form.',1763116831641);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8mgt00r1td3r8fqgxl3m','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Call recording disclosure MUST be made at the very start of the call, before any data protection verification or policy discussion. Current practice (disclosing at 36 seconds after DPA verification) breaches FCA requirements. Script to use immediately after greeting: ''This call is being recorded for training, monitoring, and regulatory purposes.'' This protects both the customer and the firm legally.',1763116832189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8mgt00r2td3rtzoab18a','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','COMPLIANCE: Add firm identification and regulatory status at call opening. Even on callback situations, state: ''Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA.'' This meets ICOBS 4.5.1R requirements and builds customer confidence in the firm''s legitimacy.',1763116832189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8mgt00r3td3rzv6b0rzi','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','Path to Excellence (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built good rapport through politeness and transparency. To reach 9/10, add more empathy acknowledgment when discussing the cancellation. For example: ''I understand cancelling a policy can be frustrating, so I''ll make sure this refund is processed as smoothly as possible for you.'' This shows you care about the customer''s experience beyond the transaction.',1763116832189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8mgt00r4td3riidu7oss','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): You clearly explained the refund timeline and receipt. To reach 9/10, proactively offer a contact method if issues arise. For example: ''If you don''t see the refund within 5 working days, please call us back on [number] and quote your policy reference. We''ll track it immediately.'' This demonstrates ownership and builds trust.',1763116832189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8mgt00r5td3rz6hrppcv','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','Excellent data protection practice pausing the call recording for card details. This shows strong understanding of PCI-DSS requirements and protects customer financial data. Continue this best practice on all calls involving payment card information.',1763116832189);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8oua00rotd3r564irxc3','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with full regulatory compliance script: ''Good morning/afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. How can I help you today?'' This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8oua00rptd3r0phtlrx7','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always conduct DPA verification BEFORE accessing or discussing any policy details. Ask: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only proceed once verified. Accessing customer data without verification is a serious GDPR breach with potential ICO penalties.',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8oua00rqtd3rrujmohno','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','PROFESSIONALISM: Eliminate casual language (''nice one'', ''yeah, nice'', ''to be fair''). Use professional insurance terminology and structured communication. Example: ''Thank you for calling. I can see you''re enquiring about a Coach House property quote. Let me review the details and ensure we have the right coverage for your needs.''',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8oua00rrtd3rrbte992t','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','NEEDS DISCOVERY: When customers mention property details (second home, pub, Coach House), ask probing questions to understand their insurance needs. Example: ''I can see this is a Coach House property. Can you tell me more about how the property is used? Is it your main residence or a second home? This helps ensure we provide appropriate coverage.''',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8oua00rstd3rhgut07tc','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','CLOSING & FOLLOW-UP: Always provide clear next steps and set customer expectations. Example: ''I''m going to email you the quote document within the next 10 minutes. Please review the coverage details, and I''ll call you back tomorrow at 2pm to discuss any questions. Does that work for you?''',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8qh500s9td3rgij77i2m','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance: You MUST include all required elements at call opening: (1) Full firm identification with regulatory status: ''You''re through to Jess at Pickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (3) GDPR notice appropriate for call type. This is non-negotiable for FCA compliance.',1763116837386);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8qh500satd3r8ecsu3s0','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','CRITICAL - Data Protection Compliance: You accessed the customer''s policy data (using their quote reference and confirming their name ''Daniel'') WITHOUT conducting DPA verification first. You MUST verify identity BEFORE accessing any personal data. Required script: ''Before I access your quote, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' This is a serious GDPR breach that could result in regulatory action.',1763116837386);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8qh500sbtd3rcylbqq0p','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','Path to Excellence - Rapport (Currently 8/10): You did an excellent job maintaining a warm, friendly tone throughout with phrases like ''lovely'', ''no worries at all'', and ''whenever you''re ready''. To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''That''s great that you''re ready to get your cover in place, Daniel. Let me make sure we get this sorted quickly for you today.'' This builds even stronger connection.',1763116837386);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8qh500sctd3rzx1j1p4r','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','Path to Excellence - Follow-Up (Currently 8/10): You clearly explained the transfer process and provided the colleague''s name (Rebecca), which is excellent. To reach 9/10, add a brief summary of what will happen next: ''Rebecca will take payment from you and confirm all your policy details. The whole process should take about 5-10 minutes. Is there anything you''d like me to clarify before I transfer you?'' This sets clearer expectations.',1763116837386);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8qh500sdtd3r76vlo8vv','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','Maintain your professional and efficient call handling style - your ability to quickly identify customer needs and route them appropriately is a real strength. Once compliance gaps are addressed, you''ll be delivering excellent service.',1763116837386);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8tr400sutd3rvizry6zr','cmhyq8tr200sntd3r146nzk0e','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always conduct DPA verification (name + date of birth minimum) BEFORE accessing any policy details. In this call, you accessed the policy using the policy number without verifying the caller''s identity. This is a serious GDPR breach. Script: ''Thank you for your policy number. Before I access your account, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?''',1763116841633);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8tr400svtd3rx6ainnvj','cmhyq8tr200sntd3r146nzk0e','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required regulatory disclosures. You must state: (1) Company name and regulatory status: ''You''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA'', (2) Call recording: ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (3) GDPR notice for service calls: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This protects both the customer and the firm.',1763116841633);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8tr400swtd3ruxh136gg','cmhyq8tr200sntd3r146nzk0e','EXCELLENT customer service recovery - you handled the missing email issue professionally, took ownership, investigated promptly, and resolved it efficiently. To reach 9/10 in Follow-Up, consider confirming the customer''s email address to prevent future delivery issues: ''Just to make sure it reaches you this time, can I confirm we have the correct email address on file?''',1763116841633);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8tr400sxtd3rihgn3y96','cmhyq8tr200sntd3r146nzk0e','STRONG rapport building throughout - you used the customer''s name, thanked them for holding, and maintained a warm, professional tone. To elevate to 9/10, try adding more personalized acknowledgment of their situation: ''I can see you''re planning to pay on the 12th when you have funds available - we''ll make sure that confirmation is with you well before then so you have everything ready.''',1763116841633);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00tltd3rth2gxkh4','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with firm identification and regulatory status. You must state: ''You''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This is a mandatory FCA requirement under ICOBS 4.5.1R and failure to do so is a regulatory breach.',1763116846299);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00tmtd3rzn0hb009','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','MANDATORY DISCLOSURE: When charging cancellation fees, explain the basis: ''There''s a 20 cancellation charge as outlined in your policy terms and conditions.'' This ensures TCF compliance and transparency. To reach 9/10 in mandatoryDisclosures, also reference where customers can find this in their documentation.',1763116846299);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00tntd3ri5phz69s','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','COMPLAINTS SIGNPOSTING: At the end of every call (especially cancellations), state: ''If you''re unhappy with any aspect of our service, you can make a complaint by calling [number] or emailing [address]. If we can''t resolve it within 8 weeks, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' This is required under DISP 1.2.',1763116846299);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00totd3r61nw30cy','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','Path to Excellence - Data Protection (currently 10/10): Exceptional work on DPA verification and GDPR consent. You''re setting the standard for the team - your approach to obtaining explicit consent for card storage and specifying retention periods is textbook compliance. Consider mentoring other agents on this process.',1763116846299);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00tptd3ri037hcjt','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','Path to Excellence - Rapport (currently 8/10): You maintained a professional, friendly tone throughout. To reach 9/10, add more empathy acknowledgment when customers are cancelling. For example: ''I understand you''ve sold the property - congratulations on completing the sale. Let me make this cancellation as smooth as possible for you.'' This builds stronger connection during transactional calls.',1763116846299);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xtm00u1td3rfkkjb45h','cmhyq8xtj00twtd3rsosgbhn2','COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with full firm identification including regulatory status. Script: ''Hello, this is Rebecca calling from Kidcol Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for training and regulatory purposes.'' This must come BEFORE any other discussion.',1763116846906);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xtm00u2td3rkon1t0b5','cmhyq8xtj00twtd3rsosgbhn2','Path to Excellence (Call Opening 68): You handled the call professionally overall, but the opening lacked regulatory compliance. To reach 8/10, ensure you state firm name, FCA authorization, and call recording disclosure in the first 10 seconds of every call. This protects both the customer and the firm from regulatory risk.',1763116846906);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xtm00u3td3rhu8qc2ww','cmhyq8xtj00twtd3rsosgbhn2','Excellent data protection practice pausing the recording for card details - this demonstrates strong understanding of PCI-DSS and data security. Continue this best practice on all calls involving payment information.',1763116846906);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xtm00u4td3r1xmdc1gc','cmhyq8xtj00twtd3rsosgbhn2','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up 89): You clearly explained the 3-5 day timeline and receipt confirmation. To reach 9/10, consider proactively offering additional support: ''If you don''t receive the refund within 5 working days, please call us back on [number] and we''ll track it immediately for you.'' This shows exceptional customer care.',1763116846906);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq8xtm00u5td3r6v9nibm2','cmhyq8xtj00twtd3rsosgbhn2','Strong rapport building throughout - your warm tone and flexibility with the card choice made the customer feel comfortable. Continue using phrases like ''thank you so much'' and ''have a great day'' to maintain this positive customer experience.',1763116846906);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq99ew00ujtd3rnzdii0qm','cmhyq99eu00uctd3rfkp6z6of','CRITICAL: Always open calls with required compliance elements: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This is a fundamental regulatory requirement.',1763116861929);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq99ew00uktd3rd1727h93','cmhyq99eu00uctd3rfkp6z6of','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up 78): You correctly answered the customer''s query about existing policies. To reach 8/10, proactively offer next steps when a customer appears to need additional coverage. For example: ''I can see you only have the main home and annex with us. Would you like me to arrange for someone from our commercial team to contact you about cover for Summit Camping at Kit Hill? We do offer campsite insurance and I''d be happy to get that process started for you.'' This turns a service call into a value-adding conversation.',1763116861929);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq99ew00ultd3r16lwfp6y','cmhyq99eu00uctd3rfkp6z6of','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport 89): You showed good empathy with ''Oh, bless you'' when the customer mentioned losing their voice. To reach 9/10, maintain that warmth throughout and personalize further. For example: ''I hope you feel better soon, Tracy. Let me make this as quick as possible for you so you can rest your voice.'' This demonstrates exceptional customer care.',1763116861929);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq99ew00umtd3ron8hvby5','cmhyq99eu00uctd3rfkp6z6of','Strong DPA verification process - you correctly gathered date of birth and address before accessing policy details. Continue this excellent practice on every call.',1763116861929);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9ck300v9td3rfjr82ypl','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP - Call Opening: Always begin calls with required regulatory disclosures. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help?'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and protects both customer and firm.',1763116866004);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9ck300vatd3r533ih6pl','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','HIGH PRIORITY - DPA Verification: Complete full DPA verification (name + date of birth minimum) before accessing policy details. Script: ''For data protection, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' This ensures GDPR compliance and prevents unauthorized access to customer data. Currently scored 7/10 - adding DOB verification would bring this to 9/10.',1763116866004);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9ck300vbtd3rulki5c77','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','Path to Excellence - Rapport (currently 8/10): You built good rapport with friendly tone and use of customer''s name. To reach 9/10, add empathy acknowledgment of their situation. Example: ''I can see you''ve been busy at work - thanks so much for taking the time to review your renewal documents. Let me make sure we get someone to talk you through everything properly.''',1763116866004);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9ck300vctd3rbw7kwkf6','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','Path to Excellence - Follow-Up (currently 8/10): Good job arranging specific callback time and confirming contact number. To reach 9/10, provide callback reference and set clearer expectations. Example: ''I''ve booked you for 11am callback - your reference is CB12345. One of our renewal specialists will call to discuss your policy options and answer any questions about the documents you''ve received. The call should take about 10-15 minutes.''',1763116866004);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9irj00w0td3r2vtpowyd','cmhyq9irg00vjtd3r1rzhax4s','Excellent technical support call handling. To reach 9/10 in Rapport, consider adding more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s frustration early in the call. For example: ''I can imagine how frustrating it must be to be locked out when you need to access OGI. Let me get this sorted for you right away.'' This builds even stronger connection.',1763116874047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9irj00w1td3rtefyeiku','cmhyq9irg00vjtd3r1rzhax4s','Strong needs discovery with thorough questioning. To elevate to 9/10, consider summarizing back the issue to confirm understanding before proceeding. For example: ''So just to confirm, you''ve got a new iPhone 17 Pro Max, you''ve factory reset your old phone, and now you can''t approve the sign-in request because the authenticator isn''t on your new device. Is that right?'' This demonstrates active listening.',1763116874047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9irj00w2td3rocyltp5o','cmhyq9irg00vjtd3r1rzhax4s','Great product knowledge demonstrated. To reach 9/10, consider proactively offering preventative guidance. For example: ''For future reference, I''ll send you a quick guide on how to transfer authenticator apps when changing phones, so this doesn''t happen again. Would that be helpful?'' This adds extra value.',1763116874047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9irj00w3td3rx85vzahw','cmhyq9irg00vjtd3r1rzhax4s','Excellent follow-up with clear next steps. To achieve 9/10, consider providing a specific timeframe. For example: ''You''ll get a notification within the next 5 minutes, and our team will call you back within 30 minutes to complete the reset. Does that work for you?'' This sets more precise expectations.',1763116874047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9irj00w4td3rrxpv8cbb','cmhyq9irg00vjtd3r1rzhax4s','Perfect compliance for this call type - all regulatory requirements met for a technical support inquiry with no insurance transaction involved. Continue this standard of professional service delivery.',1763116874047);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9k0a00wmtd3rkf5hcq9i','cmhyq9k0700w8td3rbuhlwfqw','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Must provide call opening compliance elements at start of every call. Required script: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website.'' This is a fundamental regulatory requirement under FCA rules and GDPR Article 13.',1763116875659);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9k0a00wntd3ryqtom8r3','cmhyq9k0700w8td3rbuhlwfqw','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Closing - 7/108/10): You handled the customer''s self-close well by confirming their understanding. To reach 8/10, provide more structured next steps with timeframes. Example: ''That''s absolutely right, Dave. I''d recommend contacting KFH within the next few days to confirm their position on hosting. Once you have that confirmation in writing, give us a call back and we can complete your quote in just a few minutes. Does that work for you?''',1763116875659);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9k0a00wotd3r23v3ustd','cmhyq9k0700w8td3rbuhlwfqw','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up - 7/108/10): You offered ongoing support which is good. To reach 8/10, set clearer expectations and offer proactive follow-up. Example: ''If you haven''t heard back from KFH within a week, feel free to call us back and we can discuss alternative options. Would you like me to send you a summary email of what we discussed today, including the requirements for your building insurer?''',1763116875659);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9k0a00wptd3rsoqqu7fl','cmhyq9k0700w8td3rbuhlwfqw','Consider offering to send supporting documentation or web links when customers are completing online quotes - this would enhance the customer experience and reduce confusion during the self-service process.',1763116875659);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9on200x5td3r7636pvol','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always provide call recording disclosure at the start of every call. Required script: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This is a mandatory FCA requirement and must be completed before proceeding with the call.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9on200x6td3rf2z290hp','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always state regulatory status in call opening. Required script: ''Pickle Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This is required under ICOBS 4.5.2R and ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9on200x7td3rb6sz0wna','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Conduct full DPA verification before accessing customer data. You collected name and quote number, but must also verify date of birth or postcode before accessing policy details. Example: ''For data protection, can I take your date of birth and postcode please?'' This protects customer data under GDPR Article 32.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9on200x8td3rhdstxs8p','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','Path to Excellence (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built good rapport with friendly tone and thanking the customer for holding. To reach 9/10, add more empathy acknowledgment of their situation. Example: ''I can see you were ready to pay online, Mark. Let me get you to the right person who can help you complete that straight away.'' This shows you understand their goal and are actively helping them achieve it.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9on200x9td3rx47r6h7q','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','Path to Excellence (Follow-Up - currently 8/10): You clearly explained the transfer to Will. To reach 9/10, set a time expectation and provide a backup option. Example: ''Will should be able to help you complete the payment in just a few minutes. If for any reason you get disconnected, your quote reference is 00-LUMX087-HQ1, and you can call us back on [number].'' This gives the customer confidence and a safety net.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9p5l00xrtd3rxnf918b3','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','CRITICAL - Data Protection Compliance (0/10): You MUST conduct DPA verification BEFORE accessing any policy data. Always verify customer identity with name AND date of birth before looking up policy details or confirming any information. Script: ''Before I access your policy, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' This is a fundamental GDPR requirement and non-negotiable.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9p5l00xstd3r624k18y3','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance (3/10): Your call opening must include: (1) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (2) FCA regulatory status: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for renewals: ''This is a renewal call, we hold your data in accordance with our privacy policy.'' Practice this opening until it becomes automatic. What you did well: You clearly identified yourself and the company. To reach compliance standard (8/10), add these three required elements to every call opening.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9p5l00xttd3r97f2s106','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','Mandatory Disclosures (5/10): While this was a service call transferred to another colleague, ensure you''re familiar with renewal disclosure requirements. For future renewal discussions, you must explain: price breakdown (premium + IPT + fees), any changes to terms, and right to shop around. What you did well: You acknowledged the customer''s existing policy and offered to review pricing. To reach 8/10, practice stating: ''Let me break down your renewal price for you - that''s X premium, Y insurance premium tax, and Z admin fee, totaling ABC.''',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9p5l00xutd3rgahowh40','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','Needs Discovery (7/10): You identified the customer''s concern about pricing and offered a re-quote, which was good. To reach 8/10, ask one or two probing questions before transferring: ''Has anything changed about your property or circumstances since last year?'' or ''Are you still happy with your current level of cover?'' This ensures the re-quote is based on accurate information and shows thorough customer care.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9p5l00xvtd3r52caal3w','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','Professionalism (8/10): You maintained a warm, friendly tone throughout and used terms of endearment appropriately (''my love''). To reach 9/10, avoid asking customers to repeat themselves multiple times - instead, clarify specific parts: ''I caught that you''re concerned about the renewal price - could you explain what you were expecting?'' This shows active listening and avoids frustrating the customer.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9se400yktd3rcgkd1x4v','cmhyq9se100y3td3re9cg1145','COMPLIANCE - Call Opening Sequence: The call recording disclosure must be made at the very beginning of the call, before any DPA verification or accessing customer records. Current practice delayed this until after security checks. Script: ''Good morning, this is Will from Pikl Insurance. Just to let you know, this call is being recorded for training and monitoring purposes. Now, for security, may I take your date of birth and postcode please?'' This ensures compliance with GDPR transparency requirements from first contact.',1763116886525);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9se400yltd3rbaoshxoo','cmhyq9se100y3td3re9cg1145','Path to Excellence (Call Opening 78): You handled the regulatory disclosures comprehensively later in the call. To reach 8/10, simply move the call recording notice to the very first sentence after introducing yourself. This small change ensures full compliance with GDPR Article 13 transparency requirements from the outset.',1763116886525);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9se400ymtd3rldge1iyj','cmhyq9se100y3td3re9cg1145','Path to Excellence (Rapport 89): You built good rapport with friendly, conversational tone and acknowledged the premium decrease positively (''it''s always nice to see, isn''t it?''). To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''re running your Airbnb business from the barn - that''s great. We''ll make sure your property host cover continues to protect you while you welcome guests.'' This shows deeper engagement with their circumstances.',1763116886525);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9se400yntd3r4nlvsvhy','cmhyq9se100y3td3re9cg1145','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery 89): Excellent work discovering the change in occupancy and verifying property usage. To reach 9/10, probe slightly deeper on the Airbnb activity: ''How many weeks per year do you typically host guests?'' or ''Has your hosting frequency changed since last year?'' This ensures the property host cover remains adequate for their actual usage.',1763116886525);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9se400yotd3r1u3pt6uq','cmhyq9se100y3td3re9cg1145','Excellent compliance practice: Your comprehensive regulatory disclosure at 4:26 covered FCA authorization, cancellation rights, complaints procedure, duty of disclosure, and non-advised status - this is exemplary and should be used as a training example for other agents handling renewals.',1763116886525);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9vbs00zbtd3rwq2sbdw0','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Always open calls with required disclosures: ''Good morning, you''re through to [name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes.'' This is mandatory under FCA rules and protects both customer and firm.',1763116890328);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9vbs00zctd3r77gennxq','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE: Provide complaints procedure at call end: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint by calling us or writing to our complaints team. If we can''t resolve it within 8 weeks, you can contact the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' Required by DISP 1.2.',1763116890328);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9vbs00zdtd3robr26c6o','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','OBJECTION HANDLING (scored 7/10): You handled the customer''s concern about refunds clearly, explaining the pro-rata structure well. To reach 8/10, offer proactive solutions when you can''t provide immediate answers. For example: ''I can''t calculate the exact amount now, but I can email you a written breakdown within 24 hours showing exactly what you''d receive back at 3, 6, and 9 months. Would that help with your decision?'' This shows initiative and customer focus.',1763116890328);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9vbs00zetd3rc2tskfue','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','CLOSING (scored 7/10): You ended professionally but left the renewal decision unclear. To reach 8/10, confirm next steps explicitly: ''So to confirm, you''re not proceeding with the renewal today? That''s fine - your policy expires on [date]. Would you like me to call you back in a week once you have more clarity on your house sale, or would you prefer to call us when you''re ready?'' This creates clarity and maintains the relationship.',1763116890328);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9vbs00zftd3rbeuo57zz','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','FOLLOW-UP (scored 7/10): You invited the customer to call back but didn''t document any action. To reach 8/10, confirm what you''ll do: ''I''ll add a note to your file about your house sale situation. If you''d like, I can also set a reminder to send you a renewal reminder 2 weeks before expiry. Would that be helpful?'' This demonstrates proactive service.',1763116890328);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9xbp0102td3rvsu7hbii','cmhyq9xbm00zmtd3r00m0t63h','CALL OPENING COMPLIANCE (78): Good job providing call recording disclosure and FCA authorization. To reach 8/10, add a brief GDPR acknowledgment at the start for renewals. Example: ''This is a renewal call, so we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This provides a complete opening while being appropriate for renewal context.',1763116892917);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9xbp0103td3rafxl30st','cmhyq9xbm00zmtd3r00m0t63h','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE (89): You explained sum insured requirements clearly and confirmed all policy features. To reach 9/10, proactively highlight any changes from last year or new benefits. Example: ''Your policy remains with Arcoll with the same great features as last year. I notice your buildings sum insured has increased slightly to 425,106 to account for rebuild cost inflation - this protects you better.''',1763116892917);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9xbp0104td3rzngaylw2','cmhyq9xbm00zmtd3r00m0t63h','RAPPORT (89): You maintained professional courtesy throughout and confirmed customer understanding. To reach 9/10, add more personalized engagement based on their specific situation. Example: ''I see you''re still hosting guests in the annex - that''s great! How''s that been going for you this year?'' This builds stronger connection while remaining professional.',1763116892917);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9xbp0105td3rhlaeubn8','cmhyq9xbm00zmtd3r00m0t63h','SALES PROCESS (89): You covered all essential elements including price breakdown, policy features, and credit terms. To reach 9/10, provide a brief summary before closing that reinforces value. Example: ''So just to recap Mark, you''re continuing with comprehensive home insurance including your guest hosting cover, family legal protection, and home emergency - all for 706.72. You''re well protected for another year.''',1763116892917);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9xbp0106td3rl56w1mhp','cmhyq9xbm00zmtd3r00m0t63h','Continue excellent DPA verification practice - you completed this perfectly before accessing any policy data, which is critical for GDPR compliance.',1763116892917);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9yq2010rtd3rgd4s21ht','cmhyq9yq0010btd3r8ghly70q','COMPLIANCE GAP (Medium): At call opening, ensure YOU provide the call recording disclosure and company identification. The transcript shows the customer providing this information, which suggests roles may be reversed. You must state: ''You''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for training and monitoring purposes.'' This is an FCA requirement under PRIN 2A.5.3R.',1763116894731);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9yq2010std3rwqbhblrf','cmhyq9yq0010btd3r8ghly70q','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Call Opening 68): You handled the rest of the call professionally, but the opening needs strengthening. To reach 8/10, ensure you control the call opening by: (1) Identifying yourself and the company first, (2) Providing the call recording notice, (3) Then proceeding to DPA verification. Practice this opening: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Before we discuss your renewal, I need to verify your identity for data protection...''',1763116894731);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9yq2010ttd3rt6czgovy','cmhyq9yq0010btd3r8ghly70q','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery 89): You did well asking about rebuild values and running the calculator, plus checking the average number of adults. To reach 9/10, add more probing questions about changes in circumstances. For example: ''Has anything changed about how you use the property this year - any renovations, changes to guest capacity, or new features added?'' This uncovers hidden needs and demonstrates thorough customer care.',1763116894731);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9yq2010utd3r4oaewksn','cmhyq9yq0010btd3r8ghly70q','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge 89): Excellent explanation of blanket cover and policy features. To reach 9/10, when explaining the rebuild calculator results, add context about why the expected value matters: ''The expected total of 283,000 is based on current rebuild costs in your area using BCIS data. This accounts for inflation in building materials and labor. I''d recommend this level as it gives you adequate protection without over-insuring.''',1763116894731);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyq9yq2010vtd3rs869jbt3','cmhyq9yq0010btd3r8ghly70q','BEST PRACTICE: Excellent DPA verification process - you verified BEFORE accessing any policy data, which is perfect GDPR compliance. Your mandatory disclosures section was comprehensive and clearly delivered. Continue this high standard.',1763116894731);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa6jq011dtd3rlniclnb0','cmhyqa6jn0110td3r2p33dvcd','PROFESSIONALISM (scored 7/10) - Path to 8/10: Dawn handled the call warmly and professionally overall. To reach 8/10, minimize personal interruptions during customer calls (e.g., answering the door at 14:05). When working from home, ensure a distraction-free environment. If interruptions are unavoidable, apologize more formally: ''I do apologize for that brief interruption. Now, where were we with your authenticator setup?''',1763116904871);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa6jq011etd3r22l59qvh','cmhyqa6jn0110td3r2p33dvcd','PROFESSIONALISM - While the friendly conversation built excellent rapport, the extended discussion about Scottish pubs (7:00-8:30) added unnecessary time to a technical support call. Balance rapport-building with efficiency. Keep casual chat to 30-60 seconds, then transition: ''Sounds like a great trip! Now, let me get this sorted for you quickly so you can get back to work.''',1763116904871);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa6jq011ftd3ru7wbnnum','cmhyqa6jn0110td3r2p33dvcd','RAPPORT (scored 9/10) - Path to 10/10: Excellent natural rapport building throughout the call. To reach 10/10 (exemplary standard), maintain this warmth while being slightly more concise. Your conversational style is a strength - just ensure it doesn''t extend call handling time unnecessarily. You''re already doing brilliantly here.',1763116904871);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa6jq011gtd3rxkmky0p6','cmhyqa6jn0110td3r2p33dvcd','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE (scored 8/10) - Path to 9/10: Good technical guidance on MFA reset and authenticator apps. To reach 9/10, proactively explain why Microsoft Authenticator is preferred earlier in the process: ''I''ll send you the reset now. You''ll need Microsoft Authenticator rather than Google - it integrates better with our cloud platform and provides more reliable authentication.'' This prevents customer confusion.',1763116904871);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa6jq011htd3rd7t84g00','cmhyqa6jn0110td3r2p33dvcd','Continue excellent practice of providing ticket references and keeping customers informed during wait times - this demonstrates strong customer service standards',1763116904871);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa7yl0120td3reo34qhy6','cmhyqa7yj011ltd3r2elntsjl','CALL OPENING COMPLIANCE (78): Good job providing call recording disclosure and conducting DPA verification. To reach 8/10, add firm identification earlier in the call. While you mentioned ''Pickle Insurance'' at the start, add regulatory status upfront: ''This is Jess from Pickle Insurance, we''re authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This ensures full compliance from the outset and builds customer confidence immediately.',1763116906702);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa7yl0121td3rkmbp9mx9','cmhyqa7yj011ltd3r2elntsjl','PRODUCT KNOWLEDGE (89): You demonstrated solid understanding of the policy features and explained rebuild costs, contents cover, and hosting cover clearly. To reach 9/10, provide more context about why certain coverages matter for this customer''s specific situation. For example: ''Since you''re doing short-term hosting, the guest-related damage cover is particularly important because standard home insurance typically excludes commercial activity. This gives you peace of mind that both accidental and malicious damage from guests is covered up to 100,000.''',1763116906702);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa7yl0122td3ru4qvhmmh','cmhyqa7yj011ltd3r2elntsjl','NEEDS DISCOVERY (89): Excellent verification of existing policy details and confirmation of occupancy status. To elevate to 9/10, ask one or two forward-looking questions about changes in circumstances: ''Are you planning any renovations or extensions in the coming year?'' or ''Has your hosting activity increased or decreased since last year?'' This demonstrates proactive risk management and may uncover coverage gaps.',1763116906702);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa7yl0123td3rym17zhmk','cmhyqa7yj011ltd3r2elntsjl','RAPPORT (89): You maintained a friendly, professional tone throughout and showed patience when the customer needed clarification. To reach 9/10, acknowledge the customer''s loyalty more explicitly: ''Thank you for renewing with us again this year - we really value your continued trust in Pickle Insurance.'' Also, when the customer mentioned their son studying away, you could have shown more empathy: ''That''s exciting that your son is studying - it''s good to know he''s still covered when he''s home during holidays.''',1763116906702);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqa7yl0124td3rsjxj0njh','cmhyqa7yj011ltd3r2elntsjl','FOLLOW-UP (89): Strong close with clear timelines for document delivery and renewal contact. To reach 9/10, provide the customer with a specific contact method for questions: ''If you have any questions after reviewing your documents, you can call us on [number] or reply directly to the policy email and we''ll get back to you within 24 hours.'' This gives customers confidence they have support after the call ends.',1763116906702);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012mtd3r0dlkrm97','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','CRITICAL - Call Opening Compliance (scored 0/10): You must ALWAYS open calls with: (1) Full firm identification including regulatory status: ''You''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', (2) Call recording disclosure: ''This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes'', (3) GDPR notice appropriate to call type. For existing customer service calls, a brief acknowledgment is acceptable: ''Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This is non-negotiable regulatory requirement. What the law requires: FCA PRIN 2 (skill, care and diligence) and GDPR Article 13 require transparency about firm identity, call recording, and data processing. Why it matters: Customers have a legal right to know who they''re speaking with, that they''re regulated, and how their data is used.',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012ntd3rrvxnydji','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','CRITICAL - Data Protection Compliance (scored 0/10): You MUST verify customer identity BEFORE discussing any policy details. Current practice: You only asked for name. Required practice: Ask for name + date of birth (minimum), or name + postcode + policy number. Script example: ''For data protection, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Then verify: ''Thank you, and can you confirm your postcode?'' Only after verification say: ''Perfect, I can see your policy here.'' What the law requires: GDPR Article 5 (data security) and FCA guidance require verification before accessing personal data. Why it matters: Prevents fraud and unauthorized access to customer information. This is a CRITICAL breach - score of 0 means immediate remediation required.',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012otd3rv1xafm8o','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','HIGH PRIORITY - Mandatory Disclosures (scored 4/10): When directing customers to purchase online, you must still provide key disclosures: (1) Cooling-off rights: ''You''ll have 14 days to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind'', (2) Complaints procedure: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can complain to us and if unresolved, to the Financial Ombudsman Service'', (3) Price breakdown: Confirm whether prices quoted include IPT. Script example: ''The 99.99 annual price includes Insurance Premium Tax. You''ll have 14 days to cancel, and our complaints procedure is on the website.'' What the law requires: ICOBS 6.1.5R and 7.1.4R require these disclosures for all sales. Why it matters: Ensures customers understand their rights and can make informed decisions.',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012ptd3rps9dgaxk','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','Sales Process Compliance (scored 5/10): Path to Excellence - What you did well: You asked good TCF questions about underlying cover and whether the other insurer knows about hosting. To reach 8/10: When directing to online purchase, provide more guidance on needs assessment. Script example: ''When you go online, make sure you accurately describe your hosting activity - how many days per year, number of guests, etc. This ensures you get the right level of cover. If you''re unsure about anything, call us back before purchasing.'' This ensures suitability even for online sales.',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012qtd3r024ltrld','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','Follow-Up (scored 6/10): Path to Excellence - What you did well: You clearly explained the next step (go to website). To reach 8/10: Provide more comprehensive follow-up support. Script example: ''Once you''ve purchased online, you''ll receive a policy document by email within 24 hours. Please read it carefully and call us if you have any questions. Do you have a pen handy for the website address? It''s www.pickle.com. Is there anything else you''d like me to clarify before you go online?'' This ensures customer feels supported and has clear expectations.',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012rtd3r7q0563r0','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','Needs Discovery (scored 7/10): Path to Excellence - What you did well: You asked clarifying questions about the customer''s situation and verified they have underlying cover. To reach 8/10: Probe deeper into their hosting activity to ensure product suitability. Script example: ''Just to make sure the top-up cover is right for you - roughly how many days per year do you host? And is it short-term lets or longer stays?'' This ensures you''re recommending the most suitable product option (annual vs 90-day vs on-demand).',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaccs012std3r0shbxid3','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','Closing (scored 7/10): Path to Excellence - What you did well: You answered the customer''s questions and they seemed satisfied. To reach 8/10: Provide a stronger close with confirmation and support offer. Script example: ''So to confirm, you''ll go to www.pickle.com, select the top-up only option, and choose your preferred term. The annual option at 99.99 is best value if you host regularly. If you have any issues with the online process, just give us a call back and we''ll help you through it. Does that all make sense?'' This ensures clarity and offers ongoing support.',1763116912396);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqajaj013jtd3rxm0zynuf','cmhyqajag0132td3r1e1mwof2','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with full regulatory disclosure. You must state: (1) Company name and FCA authorization status, (2) Call recording notice, (3) Brief GDPR acknowledgment for renewals. Script: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' This is a fundamental FCA requirement under PRIN 7 (communications with clients).',1763116921387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqajaj013ktd3r6e8vn9ks','cmhyqajag0132td3r1e1mwof2','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - 8/10): You built good rapport with friendly language like ''lovely'' and ''bear with me.'' To reach 9/10, add more personalized acknowledgment of the customer''s specific situation. For example, when the customer mentioned their son moving back, you could have said: ''I completely understand - family circumstances change! Let me make sure we''ve got the right number of occupants reflected so your cover is accurate.'' This shows you''re listening and care about their individual needs.',1763116921387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqajaj013ltd3r8h63s3my','cmhyqajag0132td3r1e1mwof2','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Needs Discovery - 8/10): You conducted thorough verification of sums insured and offered the rebuild calculator, which was excellent. To reach 9/10, probe slightly deeper when customers express uncertainty. When the customer said ''I wouldn''t have a clue'' about contents value, try: ''That''s very common! Let me help - think about replacing everything in your home: furniture, electronics, clothing, kitchen items. Would 31,440 cover all of that at today''s prices?'' This helps customers make truly informed decisions.',1763116921387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqajaj013mtd3rbm7fce9b','cmhyqajag0132td3r1e1mwof2','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge - 8/10): You explained the blanket cover and hosting cover clearly. To reach 9/10, provide more context about why features matter to this specific customer. For example: ''Since you''re doing short-term hosting, that 5 million public liability is really important - it protects you if a guest has an accident on your property. And the guest damage cover means you''re protected if they accidentally damage your contents or building.'' This connects features to real-world benefits.',1763116921387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqajaj013ntd3r9c5kc8xz','cmhyqajag0132td3r1e1mwof2','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Follow-Up - 8/10): You clearly explained document delivery and next renewal contact. To reach 9/10, add a proactive service touch: ''I''ve noted that you have four adults currently living there. If your son moves out before next year''s renewal, just give us a call and we can adjust that - it might even reduce your premium slightly. We''re here if anything changes throughout the year.'' This demonstrates ongoing support beyond the transaction.',1763116921387);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaz860149td3r8ixnhrd5','cmhyqaz84013std3rkl6g09ne','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE ISSUE: Agent must provide call opening compliance elements at the START of the call. Required script: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' The customer should not have to provide these disclosures - this is a regulatory breach requiring immediate remediation.',1763116942039);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaz86014atd3rb0e5hb60','cmhyqaz84013std3rkl6g09ne','Path to Excellence (Rapport 910): You built exceptional rapport through patience, empathy, and genuine engagement with the customer''s complex situation. To reach 10/10, incorporate even more personalized acknowledgment of their specific circumstances. For example: ''I can really hear how much thought you''ve put into managing both the farm and the holiday let - it''s clear you''re very hands-on with everything. Let me make sure we get your cover exactly right so you can focus on your guests and teaching without worrying about insurance gaps.''',1763116942039);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaz86014btd3rnvcg0j05','cmhyqaz84013std3rkl6g09ne','Path to Excellence (Needs Discovery 89): You conducted thorough discovery and identified the critical guest hosting coverage gap - excellent work. To reach 9/10, probe slightly deeper on business use patterns earlier in the call. For example: ''You mentioned the annex is let through Sykes - can you tell me about your typical occupancy patterns and whether you''re on-site when guests are staying? This helps me ensure we have the right coverage in place.''',1763116942039);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaz86014ctd3rm60y7g8y','cmhyqaz84013std3rkl6g09ne','Path to Excellence (Product Knowledge 89): You demonstrated strong knowledge of the guest hosting top-up and policy conditions. To reach 9/10, provide more context about why certain conditions exist. For example when discussing unoccupancy: ''The reason insurers have unoccupancy limits is that empty properties have higher risk of issues going unnoticed - burst pipes, break-ins, etc. With your sister able to stay when you''re away, you''re actually reducing that risk, which is why we can keep the better rate.''',1763116942039);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqaz86014dtd3rt1snaug4','cmhyqaz84013std3rkl6g09ne','Path to Excellence (Sales Process Compliance 89): You covered all essential sales process requirements including needs assessment, non-advice disclosure, and product suitability. To reach 9/10, provide a clearer summary of the coverage changes at the point of sale. For example: ''Just to confirm what we''ve added today - you now have the guest hosting top-up which gives you public liability up to 5 million and covers guest-related damage. This closes the gap you had for the last six months and protects you going forward.''',1763116942039);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqb8xb014ytd3rw3rkmsf9','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','CRITICAL COMPLIANCE GAP: Always open calls with required regulatory disclosures. You MUST state: (1) ''This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes'', (2) ''We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'', and (3) GDPR privacy notice: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.'' Practice this opening script until it becomes automatic - this is a non-negotiable regulatory requirement.',1763116954607);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqb8xb014ztd3rzpcrn8ct','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Rapport - currently 8/10): You built good rapport by being friendly and patient with the customer''s questions. To reach 9/10, personalize your responses more by referencing their specific situation. For example: ''I can see you''re building quite a portfolio with 12 properties - that''s impressive! Let me make sure we get this new one protected just as well as your others.'' This shows you''re paying attention to their business growth.',1763116954607);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqb8xb0150td3r8ckz5atc','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Product Knowledge - currently 8/10): You demonstrated strong knowledge of policy features and explained complex concepts clearly. To reach 9/10, proactively anticipate customer questions. For example, when discussing the flat''s leak scenario, you could add: ''It''s a common question with flats - the key thing to remember is: if it''s attached to the building structure, it''s buildings insurance; if you can take it with you when you move, it''s contents.'' This prevents confusion before it arises.',1763116954607);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqb8xb0151td3r2rhikobd','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','PATH TO EXCELLENCE (Mandatory Disclosures - currently 7/10): You covered most required disclosures well, particularly the finance agreement details. To reach 8/10, ensure you explicitly state the 14-day cooling-off period earlier in the call. Script: ''Just so you know, you have 14 days from today to cancel this policy for a full refund if you change your mind - that''s your statutory cooling-off period.'' This should come right after the price is agreed.',1763116954607);
INSERT INTO CoachingRecommendation VALUES('cmhyqb8xb0152td3rhuiojqum','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','Strengthen needs discovery by asking more about the customer''s hosting plans and risk profile. For example: ''You mentioned you''re near the airport - are you expecting mainly short stays or longer bookings? This helps me ensure the unoccupancy terms work for your business model.'' This demonstrates you''re tailoring the policy to their specific needs.',1763116954607);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbj000k3j6gei18ids2','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, firm regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 mandates a privacy notice at first contact with new customers. FCA rules require disclosure of call recording and regulatory status. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand their data rights before sharing sensitive personal and financial information, and confirms they''re dealing with a regulated firm.',1763114604176);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbj000l3j6g1x8cp0i6','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period when customer indicated intention to purchase policy','ICOBS 7.1.4R',1548,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before or on conclusion of the contract. **What to say**: ''Before we finalize this, I need to explain your cancellation rights. You have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period. After 14 days, you can still cancel but may receive a pro-rata refund minus any claims.'' **Why it matters**: This protects consumers by ensuring they know they can cancel without penalty if they''re not satisfied or find a better deal, promoting fair treatment and informed decision-making.',1763114604176);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbk000m3j6gfzxf31qn','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 2.2.2R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have transparent complaints procedures and inform customers of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. **What to say**: ''If you ever need to make a complaint, you can contact us and we''ll aim to resolve it within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, or if we haven''t resolved it within 8 weeks, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know how to seek redress if something goes wrong, providing essential consumer protection and access to independent dispute resolution.',1763114604176);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbk000n3j6gvsymnpjy','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent stated non-advised service but did not clearly explain what this means or the remuneration basis','ICOBS 4.5.2R, IDD Article 19',1026,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.2R requires clear disclosure of whether advice is provided and the basis of remuneration. **What to say**: ''We''re providing this on a non-advised basis, which means we''re not making a personal recommendation based on your individual circumstances. You''ll need to satisfy yourself that this policy meets your needs. We receive commission from the insurer for arranging this policy, but this doesn''t affect the price you pay.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand they''re responsible for assessing suitability and are aware of potential conflicts of interest, enabling informed decision-making.',1763114604176);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbk000o3j6gacdk9ch4','cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide clear breakdown of premium components (premium vs IPT vs fees)','ICOBS 6.1.5R',1095,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires insurers to provide a breakdown of the premium showing Insurance Premium Tax separately. **What to say**: ''The total price of 476.60 breaks down as follows: the insurance premium is 393.39, Insurance Premium Tax at 12% is 47.21, and there are no additional fees. This gives you the total of 476.60.'' **Why it matters**: This transparency allows customers to understand what they''re paying for and ensures they can see the tax component separately, promoting fair treatment and informed purchasing decisions.',1763114604176);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbq001g3j6gtjh5t1yp','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 4.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7',14,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to provide their name and regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. FCA Principle 7 requires clear communication. Agent must state: ''This is Callum from Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. Our full privacy policy is available at [website] or we can send it by post.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and their data protection rights before sharing personal information.',1763114604182);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbq001h3j6guhxgwz6a','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period for the new insurance policy','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before or on conclusion of the contract. Agent must state: ''You''ll have 14 days from your policy start date on 1st December to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period, and there''s no penalty for cancelling during this time.'' This ensures customers understand they can cancel without financial loss if the policy doesn''t meet their needs.',1763114604182);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbq001i3j6g5ds75ji4','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure information or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have procedures for handling complaints and to inform customers of their right to refer to the Financial Ombudsman Service. Agent must state: ''If you ever need to make a complaint, you can contact us directly and we''ll aim to resolve it within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, or if we haven''t resolved it within 8 weeks, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know how to escalate concerns and access independent dispute resolution.',1763114604182);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbq001j3j6g4jt8rbpa','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not conduct needs assessment or confirm product suitability during the sales process','ICOBS 5.2.1R, FCA PRIN 6 (TCF)',NULL,'ICOBS 5.2.1R requires firms to take reasonable steps to ensure a customer only buys a policy that is consistent with their demands and needs. FCA Principle 6 (Treating Customers Fairly) requires ensuring suitability. Agent must ask: ''Before we proceed, can I just confirm this policy still meets your needs? Has anything changed in your circumstances since yesterday - your business activities, the property, or what you need covered?'' This ensures the product remains suitable and demonstrates fair treatment of the customer.',1763114604182);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbq001k3j6g8u9smg8n','cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not confirm that product information documentation was received or offer to resend it','ICOBS 6.1.5R',33,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires firms to provide customers with information about the insurance contract before conclusion. When customer stated ''they never sent me the email'', agent should have said: ''I apologize for that. Let me make sure you have all the policy information before we proceed. I''ll resend the policy documents to your email right now, including the Insurance Product Information Document and your policy terms. Please review these before your payment on the 27th. Can you confirm your email address?'' This ensures the customer has the required pre-contract information to make an informed decision.',1763114604182);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbu00263j6g4xskpjy4','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - no mention of recording, regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice','GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 mandates a privacy notice at first contact when collecting personal data. FCA rules require clear identification of firm status. Call recording must be disclosed before recording begins. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know they''re being recorded, understand who regulates the firm, and are informed of their data rights before sharing sensitive personal and financial information. It''s a fundamental customer protection and legal requirement.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbu00273j6gdbhizd8x','cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Needs discovery could have been more thorough - customer clarified buy-to-let usage late in call (7:28), suggesting this wasn''t fully explored during initial quote or at call start','ICOBS 5.2.1R (Demands and needs), FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',448,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 5.2.1R requires firms to obtain necessary information about customer circumstances and objectives to enable recommendation of suitable products. Even in non-advised sales, understanding property use is essential for correct product selection. **What to say**: After security checks, ask: ''Before we proceed, can you confirm how you''ll be using this property? Will it be your main residence, a second home for personal use, or will you be renting it out to guests or tenants?'' Then verify: ''And I can see the quote includes guest cover - is that correct for your needs?'' **Why it matters**: Holiday homes used for commercial letting have different risk profiles and require specific cover (like guest liability). Confirming this upfront ensures the customer gets appropriate cover and prevents potential claim disputes later.',1763114604187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvbz002y3j6gv3kjtiwm','cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR acknowledgment','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy notice), FCA Handbook SUP 15.3 (Call recording notification)',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at first contact (ICOBS 2.2.2R). Call recording must be disclosed (SUP 15.3). GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information, though abbreviated for renewals. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded (protecting both parties), and that their data is being processed lawfully. These are foundational consumer protections.',1763114604192);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvc4003o3j6g7e5qz4n1','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification, no FCA regulatory status disclosure, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'FCA PRIN 7 and ICOBS 2.2.2R require clear firm identification and regulatory status disclosure. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at [Company Name], we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy available on our website.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data is being used - fundamental consumer protections.',1763114604197);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvc4003p3j6g2sjkfovy','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy data BEFORE completing DPA verification - customer provided property address at 00:25 before identity was verified at 00:42-00:46','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018',25,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data including protection against unauthorized processing. Agent must ALWAYS verify identity BEFORE accessing or discussing any policy information. Correct sequence: ''Before I can access your policy, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verification: ''Thank you, I can now access your policy details.'' This prevents unauthorized individuals from accessing customer data by simply knowing a policy address.',1763114604197);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvc4003q3j6g9dkza3sb','cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide clear breakdown of premium components (insurance premium vs IPT vs fees) when quoting the Level 2 unoccupancy price','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Price disclosure)',415,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires insurers to provide customers with the total price, showing separately the premium, Insurance Premium Tax, and any fees. Agent should state: ''The Level 2 unoccupancy cover would be 259 total, which breaks down as X premium, Y Insurance Premium Tax at 12%, and Z administration fee.'' This transparency allows customers to understand exactly what they''re paying for and compare prices effectively.',1763114604197);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvc8004g3j6grwxes234','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, FCA regulatory status, or GDPR acknowledgment at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to disclose they are recording calls for regulatory purposes. GDPR Article 13 requires data controllers to inform data subjects about data processing at the point of collection. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. **What to say**: Agent must open with: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know their conversation is being recorded (consent/transparency), understand who regulates the firm (consumer protection), and are aware of their data rights before sharing personal information. Failure to disclose call recording may breach GDPR consent requirements and FCA conduct rules.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvc8004h3j6gpc7n6wxd','cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explicitly mention complaints procedure timeline (8 weeks) or Financial Ombudsman Service rights during disclosures','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 2.2.3R',330,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to inform customers about their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service if not resolved within 8 weeks. ICOBS 2.2.3R requires this information to be provided at point of sale or policy change. **What to say**: Agent should add to the disclosure script: ''If you wish to make a complaint, please contact us on this number. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, or we haven''t resolved it within 8 weeks, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand their statutory rights to independent dispute resolution, which is a cornerstone of consumer protection in financial services. It prevents firms from being the sole arbiter of complaints.',1763114604201);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcc00583j6g202kyzuz','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent completely failed to provide call opening compliance requirements: no company identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR acknowledgment','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',2,'FCA and ICOBS rules require firms to identify themselves and disclose regulatory status at the start of every call. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information. Agent must open with: ''Good morning, this is [Name] from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and that their conversation is recorded and data protected.',1763114604205);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcc00593j6gmi9l4jsb','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to provide complaints procedure information or Financial Ombudsman Service rights when processing policy cancellation','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to provide complaints information to customers. Agent must state: ''If you have any concerns about how we''ve handled your cancellation or any other aspect of our service, you can make a formal complaint. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge at financial-ombudsman.org.uk.'' This ensures customers know their rights to redress if they''re unhappy with the service.',1763114604205);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcc005a3j6gt7fp1vqt','cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not clearly explain the 30 cancellation fee at the outset, only mentioning it partway through and then correcting to 20','ICOBS 2.2.2R, FCA PRIN 6 (TCF)',90,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear communication of charges. When customer requests cancellation, agent should immediately state: ''I can help you with that. Please note there is a 20 cancellation fee as outlined in your policy terms. I''ll calculate your refund by taking your remaining premium and offsetting this fee. Let me check what''s due to you.'' This ensures transparency about costs from the beginning and avoids customer confusion.',1763114604205);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvch005x3j6g7uy16hm5','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements - no firm identification, no regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Communications), GDPR Article 13, SM&CR Conduct Rule 2',2,'FCA and ICOBS regulations require firms to identify themselves clearly and disclose call recording. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. Agent must open ALL calls with: ''Good morning/afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality, training and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the call is recorded, and their data rights are protected from the outset.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvch005y3j6gxykl7lrs','cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed and discussed claim information without conducting DPA verification first - discussed policy details and claim status before confirming customer identity','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and Confidentiality), GDPR Article 32 (Security of Processing), Data Protection Act 2018 Section 2',8,'GDPR Article 5 requires that personal data is processed securely and only disclosed to authorized individuals. Before discussing ANY policy or claim information, agent must verify identity by stating: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only after successful verification can policy information be accessed or discussed. This protects customers from unauthorized disclosure of their sensitive insurance and claims data to potentially fraudulent callers.',1763114604209);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvck006l3j6g7001hwm2','cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any mandatory call opening disclosures: no clear firm identification, no FCA regulatory status mentioned, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice acknowledgment','ICOBS 4.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 6',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to disclose their identity and regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. FCA recording rules require disclosure of call recording. **What to say**: ''Good morning/afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and complaints can be escalated to the FOS, that their conversation is recorded, and that their data rights are protected. This is fundamental to transparency and customer protection.',1763114604212);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007q3j6g33nahtrq','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any of the required call opening elements: no firm identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notice, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Information to be provided)',2,'FCA and GDPR require specific disclosures at call opening. Agent must state: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and understand their data rights before proceeding.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007r3j6gka7k0gb3','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent collected personal data (postcode, address, email address) starting at 1:50 without first completing DPA verification. Date of birth was not collected until 18:30, well after sensitive data was gathered','GDPR Article 5(1)(a) (Lawful, fair and transparent processing), Data Protection Act 2018',110,'GDPR Article 5 requires lawful basis for processing personal data and verification of identity before accessing customer information. Agent must verify identity FIRST by stating: ''Before we proceed, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only after verification should agent collect address, email, or discuss any policy details. This protects both customer data and prevents unauthorized access to personal information.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007s3j6g9zooo12v','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to explain 14-day cooling-off period and cancellation rights when providing quote for new business policy','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Cooling-off period), ICOBS 7.1.4R (Cancellation rights)',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R and 7.1.4R require insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights at point of sale. Agent must state: ''You have a 14-day cooling-off period from when your policy starts or when you receive your documents, whichever is later. During this time, you can cancel for a full refund if you change your mind, as long as you haven''t made a claim.'' This ensures customers understand they''re not locked in and can cancel without penalty if the policy doesn''t meet their needs.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007t3j6gwgoi7r8t','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent provided total premium of 750.47 but failed to break down the price into premium, Insurance Premium Tax (IPT), and any fees separately','ICOBS 6.1.9R (Price disclosure), FCA PRIN 7 (Clear, fair and not misleading communications)',1376,'ICOBS 6.1.9R requires clear price disclosure showing the breakdown of charges. Agent must state: ''Your total price is 750.47, which breaks down as: Premium XXX, Insurance Premium Tax at 12% of XXX, and our broker fee of XXX.'' This transparency allows customers to understand exactly what they''re paying for and compare quotes accurately.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007u3j6gxx3nqy20','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to explain complaints procedure or mention Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS) rights at any point during the sales process','DISP 1.2.1R (Complaints handling procedures), ICOBS 6.1.5R (Information about complaints handling)',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to inform customers about complaints procedures. Agent must state: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, we have a formal complaints procedure. You can contact our complaints team, and if you''re not satisfied with our response, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights and how to escalate concerns if needed.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007v3j6gwi24todi','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not confirm that policy documentation would be sent or explain what documents customer would receive','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Pre-contract and contract information)',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires customers to receive policy documentation. Agent should state: ''I''ll email your quote today to the address you provided. If you decide to proceed, you''ll receive your policy documents including your policy schedule, statement of facts, and insurance product information document within 24 hours of your policy starting. Please check these carefully to ensure everything is correct.'' This sets clear expectations about documentation and encourages customers to review their cover.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcq007w3j6g8lv75o3r','cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','medium','tcfCompliance','When customer expressed confusion about legal expenses product (''I don''t understand. Sorry. Do you recommend it or is it''), agent''s explanation remained unclear and customer still seemed uncertain','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications)',1016,'FCA PRIN 6 requires treating customers fairly, which includes clear communication. When customer expresses confusion, agent must simplify: ''Let me explain more clearly. Legal expenses cover is optional - it''s not essential for your holiday let. It would give you 50,000 towards legal costs if you had disputes like a contractor not completing work properly. However, you already have 5m liability cover for guest-related legal issues in your main policy. Many customers choose not to add this. Would you like it, or are you happy without it?'' This respects the customer''s need for clarity without pressure.',1763114604219);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcu008p3j6g38anx7ts','cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening, breaching GDPR transparency requirements','GDPR Article 13, ICO Guidance on Call Recording',1,'GDPR Article 13 requires organizations to inform data subjects when their personal data is being collected, including call recordings. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to Will at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded before they share any personal information, respecting their right to be informed about data processing activities.',1763114604223);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcy009f3j6go5crwsra','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - fundamental FCA requirement for all regulated calls','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13',1,'FCA regulations and GDPR Article 13 require transparency at first contact. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being monitored and stored, protecting their right to informed consent.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcy009g3j6g742gt3p2','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide GDPR privacy notice at call opening for new business sale - required under GDPR Article 13 for first data collection','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',1,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact when collecting personal data. For new business sales, agent must state: ''We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website at [URL] or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers understand how their data will be used before sharing sensitive information.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvcy009h3j6gk1mrszwr','cmhyowvcw008v3j6g8htcaobp','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide explicit IPT breakdown - stated ''inclusive of IPT'' but did not separate the tax amount from base premium','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Price transparency)',183,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear price disclosure including taxes. Agent should state: ''Your total premium is 767.14, which includes Insurance Premium Tax at 12%. The base premium is 685.30 and IPT is 81.84.'' This provides complete transparency on what the customer is paying and ensures they understand the tax component.',1763114604226);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvd900bk3j6gjlx0qupg','cmhyowvd800b33j6g6yqku7vc','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call, which is a fundamental FCA requirement','ICOBS 2.2.3R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.3R and FCA Principle 7 require firms to communicate information clearly and provide transparency about call recording. Every call must begin with disclosure that the call is being recorded. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded and can object if they wish, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring informed consent for data processing.',1763114604238);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdf00cb3j6gof899w4l','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, regulatory status disclosure, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Information to be provided)',1,'FCA regulations require firms to identify themselves with regulatory status, disclose call recording, and provide privacy information. Agent must state: ''Good afternoon, Will speaking from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and their data rights are protected from the outset.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdf00cc3j6g534r01d9','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not disclose remuneration structure (commission-based broker model)','IDD Article 19 / ICOBS 4.5.1R (Disclosure of remuneration)',NULL,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires brokers to disclose the nature of remuneration before conclusion of contract. Agent should state: ''As a broker, we receive commission from the insurer when you purchase a policy. This commission is already included in the premium you pay and doesn''t cost you anything extra. We work with multiple insurers to find you the right cover.'' This transparency ensures customers understand potential conflicts of interest and builds trust in the broker relationship.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdf00cd3j6gm52o2rcg','cmhyowvdd00bs3j6gz1v28m2b','low','followUp','No confirmation of follow-up actions or documentation to be sent to customer','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly) - best practice',288,'TCF best practice requires clear communication of next steps. Agent should state: ''I''ll send you a summary email with the details we discussed, including Home Protect''s contact information and our insurer panel list. If you have any questions or want to proceed with our quote, you can call us back or complete the purchase online. Is there anything else I can help with today?'' This ensures the customer has a clear record of the conversation and knows how to proceed, demonstrating fair treatment and good customer service.',1763114604243);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdi00cv3j6gcymirkxo','cmhyowvdh00cj3j6g2z7msudv','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide firm identification, regulatory status disclosure, call recording notice, or GDPR acknowledgment at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (SM&CR Conduct Rule 2), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA Conduct Rules require clear firm identification. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear communication of regulatory status. Call recording must be disclosed under GDPR lawful processing requirements. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is being recorded, and that their data rights are protected. It''s fundamental to transparency and trust in financial services.',1763114604247);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdm00dn3j6g01hz4e53','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, firm regulatory status, or GDPR notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICO Guidance on call recording',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at data collection. ICO guidance requires disclosure when calls are recorded. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, Pikl Insurance, Rebecca speaking. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is processed in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and how their data is used - fundamental transparency requirements protecting consumer rights.',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdm00do3j6gjy6qw8el','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent mentioned 37% APR for monthly payments but did not provide required Consumer Credit Act disclosures including total amount payable or credit terms','Consumer Credit Act 1974, FCA CONC 4.2.5R',451,'**What the law requires**: CONC 4.2.5R requires clear, fair and not misleading pre-contract credit information including APR, total amount payable, and credit term. **What to say**: ''If you pay monthly, the APR is 37%. Your annual premium of 1,801.75 would become [X] total over 12 monthly payments of [Y]. That''s [Z] more than paying annually. I can email you the full credit agreement with all terms before you decide. Would that be helpful?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand the true cost of credit and can make informed decisions about payment methods, preventing them from unknowingly paying significantly more through instalments.',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdm00dp3j6gx19lpre6','cmhyowvdk00d13j6gf7qyfs88','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not mention complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights during the call','DISP 1.2.1R, FCA Handbook',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective and transparent complaints procedures and inform customers of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. **What to say**: Include in closing: ''If you have any concerns about our service, please let us know. We have a formal complaints procedure, and if you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service. Full details are in the documents I''m sending you.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know their rights to complain and access independent dispute resolution, a key consumer protection in financial services.',1763114604250);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ei3j6gkq7pcs7v','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at start of call - mandatory FCA requirement missing','FCA PRIN 11 (Relations with regulators), SM&CR Conduct Rule 2, GDPR Article 13',0,'FCA regulations and GDPR Article 13 require firms to inform customers that calls are recorded before proceeding. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This protects both the customer (transparency about data processing) and the firm (evidence of advice given). Recording disclosure must occur BEFORE any substantive conversation begins.',1763114604254);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ej3j6gjfy44uw5','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization) during call opening','ICOBS 4.5.1R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',0,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires insurance intermediaries to disclose their regulatory status to customers. Agent must state: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'' during the call opening. This ensures customers know they are dealing with a regulated firm and have access to regulatory protections including FSCS and FOS. This disclosure builds trust and meets legal obligations.',1763114604254);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdp00ek3j6g55gqu19e','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','high','dataProtectionCompliance','GDPR privacy notice incomplete - missing customer rights (access, rectification, erasure) and data retention period','GDPR Article 13 (Information to be provided), UK DPA 2018',178,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact that includes: (1) purposes of processing, (2) customer rights, (3) retention period. Agent stated purposes but must add: ''You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. We retain your information for [X years] in accordance with regulatory requirements. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers understand their data rights before sharing sensitive personal information.',1763114604254);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdp00el3j6gdoy06n53','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No explanation of cooling-off rights (14-day cancellation period) if policy proceeds to sale','ICOBS 7.1.4R (Cancellation rights)',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before or on conclusion of contract. When policy is sold, agent must state: ''You have 14 days from your policy start date or receipt of documents, whichever is later, to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period.'' This protects customers by ensuring they know they can cancel without penalty if the policy doesn''t meet their needs.',1763114604254);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdp00em3j6gl9it4606','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No explanation of complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS) rights','DISP 1.2.1R (Complaints handling procedures)',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective complaints handling procedures and inform customers of their rights. Agent must state: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, please contact our complaints team. If we can''t resolve your complaint within 8 weeks, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know how to escalate concerns and access independent dispute resolution.',1763114604254);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdp00en3j6g0srw4n8e','cmhyowvdn00dv3j6g40irtjvr','medium','salesProcessCompliance','No confirmation that product information document will be provided or has been sent','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Product information)',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires provision of Insurance Product Information Document (IPID) before contract conclusion. Agent should state: ''I''ll email you the Insurance Product Information Document which summarizes the key features, benefits, and exclusions of this policy. Please review it before your policy starts.'' This ensures customers have clear, standardized information to make informed decisions about their insurance purchase.',1763114604254);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdx00fb3j6g461obqjw','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - fundamental FCA requirement','FCA PRIN 11 (Relations with regulators), GDPR Article 13',1,'FCA regulations and GDPR Article 13 require call recording disclosure and privacy notice at first contact. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This ensures customers are aware of recording and understand their data rights before sharing personal information.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdx00fc3j6g51icj1n7','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state regulatory status (FCA authorization) at call opening','ICOBS 4.5.1R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status. Agent must state: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'' during call opening. This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and have access to regulatory protections including FSCS and Financial Ombudsman Service.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdx00fd3j6gip3sez4t','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period when providing quote for new business','ICOBS 7.1.4R (Cancellation rights)',2664,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of cancellation rights before contract conclusion. Agent must state: ''If you decide to proceed with this policy, you''ll have a 14-day cooling-off period from your policy start date. This means you can cancel for a full refund if you change your mind, with no questions asked.'' This protects customers by ensuring they understand they can cancel without penalty if the policy doesn''t meet their needs.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdx00fe3j6gwcj53vem','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 4.5.3R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R and ICOBS 4.5.3R require firms to provide complaints handling information. Agent must state: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a formal complaint. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. You also have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service, which is a free, independent service. Full details are in your policy documents.'' This ensures customers know how to escalate concerns and access independent dispute resolution.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdx00ff3j6g7zzyonjz','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain remuneration structure (commission vs fee basis)','IDD Article 19, ICOBS 4.5.2R',1163,'IDD Article 19 and ICOBS 4.5.2R require disclosure of remuneration basis. Agent stated non-advised service but must also state: ''We receive commission from insurers when you purchase a policy. This doesn''t affect the price you pay - the premium is the same whether you buy direct or through us. We can provide details of our commission on request.'' This transparency ensures customers understand potential conflicts of interest.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvdx00fg3j6g3umz92aj','cmhyowvdv00et3j6gzq4qiwdg','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not explicitly confirm Insurance Product Information Document (IPID) would be provided','ICOBS 6.1.5R (IDD implementation)',2664,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires provision of IPID before contract conclusion. Agent should state: ''I''m sending you the Insurance Product Information Document along with your quote. This is a standardized summary that shows what''s covered, what''s not covered, and any restrictions. Please read this before deciding to proceed.'' This ensures customers receive key information in a clear, comparable format as required by IDD.',1763114604261);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve500gw3j6gmy1u2vjo','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed and discussed policy pricing and details without conducting DPA verification first','GDPR Article 5, DPA 2018, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',30,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5 and the Data Protection Act 2018 require that personal data is processed lawfully and securely. Before accessing any customer policy information, the agent must verify the caller''s identity. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? Thank you. And can you confirm the postcode on the policy?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized individuals from accessing sensitive customer information including policy details, pricing, and personal data. Failure to verify identity is a serious data breach that could result in FCA enforcement action and ICO penalties.',1763114604270);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve500gx3j6ghb6hp5kz','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, regulatory status (FCA authorization), or any GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 2.2.2R, FCA PRIN 7, GDPR Article 13',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice. Call recording must be disclosed for consent. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Pickle Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. As this is regarding your renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: These disclosures ensure customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data is being used. This is fundamental to consumer protection and informed consent.',1763114604270);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve500gy3j6gy0wd9qwo','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','high','tcfCompliance','Agent made minimal effort to retain customer or explore alternatives when faced with price objection, potentially failing to deliver fair customer outcomes','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',58,'**What the law requires**: FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly and deliver good outcomes. When a customer objects to pricing, agents must explore alternatives and demonstrate value. **What to say**: ''I completely understand your concern about the increase. Before you decide, let me review your policy details to ensure everything is accurate - sometimes we can adjust cover levels or excesses to reduce the premium. I''d also like to check if there are any discounts you qualify for. Can I take a few minutes to do that for you? I want to make sure we''re giving you the best possible price.'' **Why it matters**: TCF requires firms to actively work in customers'' interests, not passively accept their departure. This demonstrates the firm is trying to achieve fair outcomes and retain customers through value, not just price.',1763114604270);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve500gz3j6gjizkxxhm','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to mention complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights when customer expressed dissatisfaction','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 2.2.2R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective complaints handling procedures and inform customers of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. When a customer expresses dissatisfaction, this information should be provided. **What to say**: ''I''m sorry we haven''t been able to help with the pricing today. If you''d like to make a formal complaint about this, please let me know and I can log it for you. You also have the right to refer any complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service. Would you like me to send you information about our complaints procedure?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know their rights and how to escalate concerns, which is a fundamental consumer protection under UK regulation.',1763114604270);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve500h03j6go759q6xc','cmhyowve400ge3j6gg45rs7ir','medium','needsDiscovery','Agent mentioned checking policy details but never actually verified sums insured, coverage levels, or explored customer needs','ICOBS 5.1.1R (Demands and needs)',50,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 5.1.1R requires brokers to obtain information about customer demands and needs before making recommendations. Even for renewals, agents should verify that cover remains appropriate. **What to say**: ''Let me pull up your policy details now. I can see you have buildings cover of X and contents of Y. Have there been any changes to your property in the last year - extensions, renovations, or valuable items added? Also, when did you last check your rebuild cost? Property values have increased significantly, and you might be over-insured, which could reduce your premium.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures the customer has appropriate cover and may identify opportunities to adjust the policy to reduce cost while maintaining suitable protection. It demonstrates the broker is acting in the customer''s best interests.',1763114604270);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve800hr3j6gm2nxvg3q','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements for new business sale: no firm identification, no FCA regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Identification), GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'FCA and GDPR regulations require full call opening compliance for new business. Agent must state: ''Good morning, this is [Name] calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Before we proceed, I need to let you know that we collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data at any time. For our full privacy policy, please visit our website or I can arrange to send it to you.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and their data protection rights from the outset.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve800hs3j6g1n6he744','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period for new business policy sale','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights at point of sale. Agent must state: ''You have 14 days from your policy start date or from receiving your policy documents, whichever is later, to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period, and you''ll find full details in your policy documents we''re sending.'' This ensures customers understand they can cancel without penalty during the cooling-off period, which is a fundamental consumer protection.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve800ht3j6ga14zlymx','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to provide complaints procedure information or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 2.2.3R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to provide complaints handling information. Agent must state: ''If you ever need to make a complaint about our service, please contact us and we''ll send you our complaints procedure. We''ll aim to resolve it within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, or if we haven''t resolved it within 8 weeks, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge. You''ll find full details in your policy documents.'' This ensures customers know their rights to escalate complaints to an independent body.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowve800hu3j6gpzal2uz2','cmhyowve700h63j6g8hzfhivw','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Limited needs assessment conducted - agent proceeded directly to payment without confirming suitability or exploring customer''s specific cover requirements','ICOBS 5.1.1R (Demands and Needs), FCA PRIN 6 (TCF)',14,'ICOBS 5.1.1R requires firms to specify demands and needs before concluding a contract. Even on continuation calls, agent should state: ''Before we finalize this, can I just confirm - has anything changed about your circumstances since we last spoke that might affect your cover needs? For example, any home improvements, changes to security, or valuable items you''ve acquired?'' This ensures the policy remains suitable and demonstrates compliance with Treating Customers Fairly principles.',1763114604273);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvee00ih3j6goqmu4hk4','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening','FCA PRIN 2 (Due Skill, Care and Diligence) and GDPR Article 13',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA and GDPR require customers to be informed when calls are recorded. This must be stated at the beginning of every call before any business is conducted. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers give informed consent to recording and protects their privacy rights. Without this disclosure, the recording may be inadmissible as evidence and violates data protection principles.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvee00ii3j6g6tklg2o8','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent collected policy reference number BEFORE conducting proper DPA verification (name and date of birth)','GDPR Article 5 (Data Security) and Data Protection Act 2018',13,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5 requires appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorized data access. DPA verification MUST be completed BEFORE accessing any policy information. Minimum verification is full name AND date of birth. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' [Wait for both pieces of information] ''Thank you, and now can I take your policy reference number?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents fraudsters from accessing customer policy data by simply knowing a policy reference. Verifying identity first protects customers from data breaches and identity theft.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvee00ij3j6ga8mn0zz3','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state FCA regulatory status in call opening','ICOBS 4.5.1R',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires insurance intermediaries to disclose their regulatory status to customers. This must include that the firm is authorized and regulated by the FCA. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance - we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Rebecca speaking, how can I help?'' **Why it matters**: This disclosure ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and have access to FCA protections including the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvee00ik3j6gyy073jnr','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','high','dataProtectionCompliance','Incomplete DPA verification - only name collected, no date of birth verification conducted','GDPR Article 5 and Data Protection Act 2018',22,'**What the law requires**: Adequate DPA verification requires at least TWO pieces of identifying information - typically full name AND date of birth. Name alone is insufficient security. **What to say**: ''Can I take your full name please?'' [Customer responds] ''Thank you, and can I also take your date of birth for verification?'' [Customer responds] ''Perfect, thank you Mr/Mrs [Name]. Now I can securely access your policy.'' **Why it matters**: Single-factor verification (name only) provides inadequate security. Many people share the same name, so date of birth is essential to confirm you''re speaking to the correct policyholder and prevent unauthorized access.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvee00il3j6g2y3og8rw','cmhyowvec00i03j6g6d4rn7nt','medium','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided (even abbreviated version appropriate for renewals)','GDPR Article 13',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice, though for renewals an abbreviated version is acceptable since the customer relationship already exists. **What to say**: For renewal calls, after verification state: ''As this is a renewal, we already hold your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy. If you''d like a copy of our privacy notice, I can email that to you.'' **Why it matters**: This acknowledges the existing data relationship and reminds customers of their ongoing data rights, while being proportionate for a renewal context rather than requiring the full notice needed for new business.',1763114604278);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvei00jb3j6g3zcr00wi','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to identify firm name, regulatory status, and call recording disclosure at call opening','ICOBS 4.5.1R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to provide their name and regulatory status in communications with customers. FCA guidance requires call recording disclosure. **What to say**: ''Good morning, this is Rebecca calling from [Company Name], authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and that their conversation is recorded for their protection and dispute resolution.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvei00jc3j6ga66a80wz','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective and transparent complaints procedures and inform customers of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. **What to say**: ''If you have any concerns about our service, please contact our complaints team on [number] or email [address]. If we can''t resolve your complaint within 8 weeks, you have the right to refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know how to raise concerns and access independent dispute resolution, which is a fundamental consumer protection right.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvei00jd3j6g7sgarjnv','cmhyowveg00ir3j6g22xx0obw','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide clear breakdown of cancellation charges and refund calculation','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Transparency of charges)',120,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear information about charges. When explaining cancellations, itemize all components. **What to say**: ''Let me break down your refund: Your total premium was X, you''ve had cover for Y days, so the pro-rata refund is Z. We deduct a 20 cancellation charge as per your policy terms, giving you a final refund of approximately 70.'' **Why it matters**: Transparent pricing builds trust and ensures customers understand what they''re paying for, reducing disputes and complaints.',1763114604282);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvem00k33j6gn4zqt45j','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Information to be provided), SM&CR Conduct Rule 2',1,'FCA PRIN 7 and ICOBS 2.2.2R require clear firm identification and regulatory status disclosure. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. Agent must open with: ''Good morning, you''re through to Callum at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality, training, and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy available on our website.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded, and how their data is used - fundamental transparency requirements.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvem00k43j6gtrbsbn6s','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide price breakdown showing premium components and Insurance Premium Tax separately','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Premium disclosure), FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',672,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires insurers to disclose the total premium and separately identify Insurance Premium Tax. Agent must state: ''The additional cost is 59.70, which breaks down as X for the insurance premium and X Insurance Premium Tax at 12%.'' This ensures customers understand what they''re paying for and can distinguish between the insurer''s charge and government tax - essential price transparency.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvem00k53j6gt19krutf','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain cooling-off rights for the mid-term adjustment adding new buildings cover','ICOBS 7.1.4R (Cancellation rights), Consumer Insurance (Disclosure and Representations) Act 2012',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of cancellation rights when material changes are made to policies. Agent must state: ''If you add this buildings cover, you have 14 days to cancel the change if you''re not satisfied. You''ll receive a pro-rata refund for the unused portion of the additional premium.'' This protects customers by ensuring they know they can reverse the decision without penalty if they change their mind or find better cover elsewhere.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvem00k63j6gfjbxc5c7','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure information or mention Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R (Complaints handling procedures), FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective complaints handling procedures and inform customers of their rights. Agent must state: ''If you have any concerns about this policy, please contact us first and we''ll do our best to resolve them. If we can''t resolve your complaint within 8 weeks, or you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer the matter to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights to independent dispute resolution and aren''t deterred from complaining.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvem00k73j6gd1o1nffm','cmhyowvek00jj3j6gvfwax7yw','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not explicitly confirm suitability of the buildings insurance for the customer''s specific needs regarding freeholder excess avoidance','ICOBS 5.2.1R (Demands and needs), IDD Article 20 (Demands and needs test)',NULL,'ICOBS 5.2.1R and IDD Article 20 require firms to specify customer demands and needs and explain why a product is suitable. Agent should state: ''Based on what you''ve told me about the 500 freeholder excess being too high, this buildings insurance for fixtures and fittings is suitable because it gives you cover with only a 100 excess, making claims much more affordable for issues like leaks or damage to your flat''s interior structure.'' This demonstrates the product meets the customer''s identified need and provides clear rationale for the recommendation.',1763114604286);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvet00ll3j6g623h083w','cmhyowver00l33j6g4nw0o2rl','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide ANY required call opening compliance elements: no firm identification, no FCA regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R, ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R and ICOBS 2.2.2R require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Agent must open ALL calls with: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Jessup Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy - you can find full details on our website or I can send you a copy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and how their data is protected - fundamental consumer protections required by UK law.',1763114604293);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvew00m33j6ggw7058w4','cmhyowveu00lr3j6gq3xp4jlq','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No call opening compliance elements present - however, this is because the call went to voicemail and no actual customer conversation occurred. This is not a compliance breach but rather a missed contact attempt.','ICOBS 4.2.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 6',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.2.1R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: When live contact is made, agent must state: ''Good morning, this is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, how their data will be used, and their rights - fundamental consumer protections under UK law.',1763114604296);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvf000mm3j6gnwdbi1qr','cmhyowvez00m93j6g839950w9','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No call opening compliance elements delivered - however, this is because the call went to voicemail with no live customer interaction. This is NOT a compliance breach as regulations apply to customer conversations, not voicemail messages.','ICOBS 4.2.1R / GDPR Article 13',0,'NOT APPLICABLE - This was a voicemail message, not a customer conversation. When the customer returns the call, the agent MUST deliver full call opening compliance: **What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.2.1R requires firm identification and regulatory status disclosure. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy notice at first contact. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Rebecca at Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. For this quote discussion, we''ll be using the information you''ve already provided. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data is being used, providing transparency and trust.',1763114604301);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvf600ny3j6g3zxsnx1l','cmhyowvf500nb3j6g979vzfd7','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call','FCA COBS 11.8 and GDPR Article 13',1,'FCA COBS 11.8 requires firms to inform customers when calls are being recorded. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being monitored and stored, protecting their right to informed consent under GDPR Article 13.',1763114604307);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfa00oq3j6gfdrr2itb','cmhyowvf800o43j6g0rh86aak','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call','GDPR Article 13 and ICO guidance on call recording',1,'GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing at the point of collection. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes.'' This can be brief but must occur before substantive conversation begins. This ensures customers are aware their voice data is being captured and can object if they wish, fulfilling the transparency principle of GDPR.',1763114604310);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfe00pg3j6gr4i2dlc2','cmhyowvfc00ow3j6ga6svk69k','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any of the required call opening elements: no firm identification, no FCA authorization statement, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice (even abbreviated for renewals)','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at first contact. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear communication. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection (abbreviated acceptable for renewals). Call recording must be disclosed under ICO guidance. **What to say**: ''Good morning, this is [Agent Name] from [Company Name]. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy. Am I speaking to Mrs. Abdul?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded (consent/transparency), and that their data is being processed lawfully. It''s foundational to consumer protection and regulatory compliance.',1763114604314);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfi00px3j6gakexk471','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any mandatory call opening disclosures - no firm identification with FCA status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at the start of calls. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with data subjects. The Consumer Duty requires clear, timely communications. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: These disclosures ensure customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and what happens to their personal data. This transparency is fundamental to consumer protection and informed consent.',1763114604319);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfi00py3j6gw5m2o55n','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer quote data without conducting proper DPA verification - only obtained customer name, no date of birth, postcode, or other verification before looking up quote on system','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (integrity and confidentiality), DPA 2018 Section 2, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',30,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data against unauthorized access. Firms must verify identity before accessing customer records. Minimum verification is name + date of birth + postcode (or policy number). **What to say**: ''Before I can access your quote details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' [After verification] ''Thank you, Mr Jones. Let me bring up your quote now.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to personal data if someone impersonates a customer. Insurance quotes contain sensitive information (property details, personal circumstances, financial data) that must be protected. Accessing data without verification is a data breach under GDPR.',1763114604319);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfi00pz3j6g5v5mj1gc','cmhyowvfh00pm3j6g58beb3db','medium','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent discussed quote details with husband when quote was in wife''s name without establishing lawful basis or consent for third-party access','GDPR Article 6 (lawful basis for processing), FCA guidance on third-party access',45,'**What the law requires**: GDPR requires a lawful basis to share personal data with third parties. When a spouse calls about a partner''s quote, the agent must establish joint interest or obtain consent. **What to say**: ''I can see this quote is in your wife Lean''s name. To discuss her quote with you, I need to confirm you''re both named on the property and this is a joint insurance inquiry. Are you both applying for this policy together?'' [If yes] ''Perfect, that gives me the lawful basis to discuss this with you.'' [If no] ''I''d need to speak with Lean directly or get her verbal consent to discuss her quote with you.'' **Why it matters**: This protects individuals'' data privacy rights - even from family members. It ensures data is only shared with authorized parties and prevents potential domestic abuse scenarios where one partner controls another''s affairs without consent.',1763114604319);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfm00qn3j6go2qunqnb','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - mandatory FCA requirement missing','FCA PRIN 11 (Relations with regulators) and SYSC 9.1.1R (Telephone recording)',1,'FCA regulations require firms to inform customers that calls are being recorded before proceeding with the conversation. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Jasmine speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being monitored and can object if they wish, protecting both customer rights and the firm''s evidential record.',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfm00qo3j6gu9tae2f3','cmhyowvfk00q53j6g7hu8gecz','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain refund calculation method or potential cancellation fees when processing policy cancellation','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Cancellation rights) and FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear communication of cancellation terms including refund calculations. Agent must state: ''You''ll receive a pro-rata refund for the unused portion of your policy from today''s date. There may be an administration fee of [amount], which will be deducted from your refund. The cancellations team will confirm the exact refund amount when they call you back, typically within [X] working days.'' This ensures customers understand the financial implications of cancellation before proceeding, preventing disputes and ensuring transparency.',1763114604322);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfq00re3j6gm6kof4l6','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any mandatory call opening elements: no firm identification with FCA authorization status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'FCA and ICOBS regulations require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at the start of calls. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to Jess at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data will be used - fundamental consumer protections.',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfq00rf3j6gth7mvjkg','cmhyowvfp00qu3j6g13wdtyd8','high','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent attempted to search for and access policy information using only email address before conducting proper DPA verification with name and additional security details','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and Confidentiality), DPA 2018 Section 2',19,'GDPR Article 5 requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data against unauthorized access. Agent must complete full DPA verification BEFORE accessing any policy data. Correct process: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verification should the agent search for and discuss policy information. This prevents unauthorized access to sensitive customer data and protects against potential data breaches.',1763114604327);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfz00rz3j6gg3giase0','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any of the mandatory call opening disclosures: no call recording notification, no FCA regulatory status, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA PRIN 7 requires clear, fair communication. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded (consent), and how their data is being used - fundamental transparency and data protection rights.',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfz00s03j6g6o6ut3g1','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy data after verifying name only, without completing proper DPA verification (no DOB, postcode, or second identifier obtained)','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018',30,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data, including protection against unauthorized processing. DPA verification must use at least TWO identifiers before accessing policy information. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? And can you confirm your postcode?'' Only after receiving correct answers: ''Thank you, that''s verified. Let me bring up your policy now.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to sensitive personal and financial data, protecting customers from fraud and identity theft, and ensuring the firm complies with data security obligations.',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvfz00s13j6g47hdmuih','cmhyowvfy00rp3j6g4nxwpfeq','low','professionalism','Agent used overly familiar language (''my love'') multiple times, which may not be appropriate for all customers and could be perceived as unprofessional','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), SM&CR Conduct Rule 1 (Act with integrity)',45,'**What the law requires**: FCA PRIN 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly, which includes maintaining professional boundaries. SM&CR Conduct Rule 1 requires staff to act with integrity. **What to say**: Use professional but warm language: ''That''s perfect, Leigh. Let me get that sorted for you'' or ''No problem at all, I''ll look into that for you right away.'' Avoid terms of endearment like ''my love'', ''darling'', ''sweetheart''. **Why it matters**: While building rapport is important, overly familiar language can make some customers uncomfortable, may be perceived as patronizing, and doesn''t maintain professional standards expected in regulated financial services.',1763114604336);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvg300sq3j6gyfa3x8z3','cmhyowvg100s73j6g4z9hvvku','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide mandatory call opening disclosures: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice acknowledgment','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy information), SM&CR conduct rules',1,'FCA and ICOBS regulations require clear firm identification and call recording disclosure at every call opening. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information. For existing customer service calls, agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the call is recorded, and their data rights are acknowledged - fundamental transparency requirements under UK regulation.',1763114604339);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvg600tg3j6gisen6jj5','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy information)',2,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves clearly. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at point of data collection. FCA rules require disclosure of call recording. **What to say**: ''Good morning, this is Will calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, the firm''s regulatory status for their protection, that the call is recorded (consent/transparency), and their data rights are acknowledged. Without this, customers cannot make informed decisions about sharing information.',1763114604343);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvg600th3j6gjpndf2p4','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent did not complete proper DPA verification before accessing policy details. Only verified address and email, not the minimum required name + date of birth verification','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Security of processing), Data Protection Act 2018, FCA guidance on data security',14,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Firms must verify identity before disclosing policy information. Minimum verification is full name + date of birth + one other identifier (address/postcode). **What to say**: ''For security purposes before I access your policy, can I take your full name and date of birth please? And can you confirm the postcode on the policy?'' Only after successful verification: ''Thank you, that''s all verified. I can now access your policy details.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to personal insurance data and protects customers from fraud. Without proper verification, the firm could disclose sensitive information to an impersonator, breaching data protection laws and exposing customers to identity theft.',1763114604343);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvg600ti3j6gy7whn7t6','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure information or Financial Ombudsman Service rights during the cancellation process','DISP 1.2 (Complaints handling procedures), ICOBS 2.3.1R (Information about the firm and its services)',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2 requires firms to provide information about their complaints handling procedures. Customers must be informed of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. This should be provided during significant policy changes including cancellations. **What to say**: ''Just to let you know, if you have any concerns about how we''ve handled this cancellation, you can make a complaint by contacting our complaints team at [contact details]. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know their rights and how to seek redress if dissatisfied. It''s a fundamental consumer protection that empowers customers to challenge poor service and holds firms accountable.',1763114604343);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvg600tj3j6g15gbg6h6','cmhyowvg500sw3j6geyu94pzd','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide a breakdown of the refund calculation or explain how the prorated refund was calculated','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Premium refunds), FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',85,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R and TCF principles require transparency in financial transactions. When processing cancellations with refunds, customers should understand how their refund is calculated. **What to say**: ''Your policy was active for [X] days out of [Y] days annual term. Your refund will be calculated on a pro-rata basis for the unused period, which is approximately [amount]. We''ll deduct the 30 cancellation charge, so your net refund will be around [amount]. Our accounts team will confirm the exact amount within 3-5 days.'' **Why it matters**: This transparency helps customers understand what they''re receiving and why, preventing confusion or disputes. It demonstrates fair treatment and builds trust by showing the firm has nothing to hide in its calculations.',1763114604343);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgb00u13j6getgdbhmx','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - mandatory FCA requirement','FCA PRIN 2.1.1R (Integrity), GDPR Article 13',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules and GDPR Article 13 require firms to inform customers that calls are being recorded and explain why. This must happen at the START of every call before any business is conducted. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. Just to let you know, this call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: Customers have a legal right to know they''re being recorded and can object. Recording without disclosure breaches GDPR consent requirements and FCA transparency principles.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgb00u23j6g962z4mmp','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization) at call opening','ICOBS 2.2.2R, IDD Article 3',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires insurance intermediaries to disclose their regulatory status to customers before conducting business. This includes stating the firm is ''authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. How can I help?'' **Why it matters**: Customers need to know they''re dealing with a regulated firm so they understand their protections under the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgb00u33j6gmi6gkbof','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','high','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided - even service calls require brief acknowledgment of data processing','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice when processing personal data. For existing customer service calls, an abbreviated notice is acceptable: acknowledging data is held and processed in accordance with privacy policy. **What to say**: After regulatory disclosure, add: ''Your personal data is held and processed in accordance with our privacy policy. You can find full details on our website or I can send you a copy.'' **Why it matters**: Even existing customers must be reminded of their data rights (access, rectification, erasure) and how their information is being used, ensuring ongoing transparency and trust.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgb00u43j6g1eb3cfh1','cmhyowvg900tp3j6gp8viyn8a','high','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy system before completing DPA verification - data accessed before identity confirmed','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018',35,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires personal data to be processed securely, preventing unauthorized access. Identity must be verified BEFORE accessing any customer data to ensure you''re speaking to the data subject or authorized representative. **What to say**: Immediately after taking policy reference, state: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verification: ''Thank you, I''ll now access your policy.'' **Why it matters**: Accessing data before verification risks disclosing personal information to unauthorized individuals (fraud, identity theft). This protects both customer and firm from data breaches.',1763114604347);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgg00uj3j6g0wa8frsa','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy data using partial policy number without conducting any DPA verification of caller identity or authority to access the data','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and Confidentiality, GDPR Article 32 - Security of Processing, DPA 2018',100,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data against unauthorized access. Article 32 mandates technical and organizational measures to ensure data security. Before accessing any customer policy data, the agent must verify the caller''s identity and authority. **What to say**: ''Before I access that policy, can I take your full name, your broker firm name, and your FCA reference number please? Thank you. And can you confirm the customer''s name on the policy?'' Only after verification should the agent proceed. **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to customer personal data, protects against fraud and data breaches, and ensures compliance with data security obligations. Failure to verify could result in ICO enforcement action, fines up to 17.5m or 4% of turnover, and mandatory data breach reporting.',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgg00uk3j6gwx56km67','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided - missing required information about data processing purposes, customer rights (access, rectification, erasure), and retention periods','GDPR Article 13 - Information to be provided where personal data are collected, UK GDPR',3,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires that when personal data is collected, the data controller must provide information about processing purposes, legal basis, retention periods, and data subject rights. This must be provided at the time of first contact or data collection. **What to say**: Add to IVR or agent greeting: ''This call is being recorded for training, quality, and regulatory purposes. We process your personal data to provide insurance services in accordance with GDPR. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit [website] or request a copy.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures transparency about data processing and informs customers of their legal rights before they share personal information. It''s a fundamental GDPR requirement that protects customer autonomy and enables informed consent.',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgg00ul3j6gh9yb9w4v','cmhyowvgf00ua3j6ggencneui','high','dataProtectionCompliance','No verification of caller''s lawful basis or authority to request changes to customer policy data on behalf of the customer','GDPR Article 6 - Lawfulness of Processing, FCA SM&CR - Conduct Rules',95,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 6 requires a lawful basis for processing personal data. When a third party (broker) requests access to or changes to customer data, the firm must verify the broker''s authority and the customer''s consent. **What to say**: ''Before I make that change, can you confirm you have the customer''s authorization to backdate this policy? And can I take the customer''s name and date of birth to verify the policy details?'' Document the authorization in the system notes. **Why it matters**: This ensures the customer has consented to the broker acting on their behalf and prevents unauthorized changes to policies. It protects both the customer and the firm from disputes and demonstrates proper data governance.',1763114604352);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgk00ve3j6gnou1tyj5','cmhyowvgi00ur3j6g97t43ame','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any of the three mandatory call opening elements: (1) call recording disclosure, (2) FCA regulatory status, (3) GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with data subjects. FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or I can send it to you. How can I help today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know (1) who is handling their data, (2) that the firm is regulated and accountable, (3) their data protection rights, and (4) that the call is recorded. These are fundamental transparency requirements protecting consumers.',1763114604357);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgp00w13j6gqqtqupyl','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy data using policy reference number without conducting DPA verification (name, DOB, address). This is a GDPR breach as sensitive personal data was accessed without proper identity verification.','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and confidentiality principle; Data Protection Act 2018',35,'GDPR Article 5 requires appropriate security measures for personal data processing. Agent must state: ''Thank you for the policy reference. Before I access your account, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can you please confirm your full name, date of birth, and postcode?'' This ensures only the legitimate policyholder can access sensitive policy and personal information, preventing fraud and unauthorized disclosure.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgp00w23j6gnszxqfkf','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening. No mention of ''this call is being recorded'' or similar statement.','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (SM&CR Conduct Rules); GDPR Article 13 (transparency)',0,'FCA Conduct Rules and GDPR require transparency about call recording. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This informs customers their conversation is being monitored and stored, allowing them to consent or object before proceeding.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgp00w33j6g9pp6vron','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization) during call opening, as required for all customer-facing communications.','ICOBS 2.2.2R - Clear, fair and not misleading communications',0,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to communicate their regulatory status. Agent must state: ''You''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This assures customers they''re dealing with a regulated firm with proper consumer protections and oversight.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgp00w43j6g4fxdicmc','cmhyowvgn00vk3j6go5x9y2od','medium','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided, though for renewal calls an abbreviated notice is acceptable (e.g., ''your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy'').','GDPR Article 13 - Information to be provided where personal data are collected',0,'GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. For renewal calls, agent should state: ''As this is a renewal, your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. If you''d like a copy or have questions about your data rights, please let me know.'' This acknowledges the existing data relationship while ensuring customers know their rights.',1763114604361);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wn3j6gay0n9dhl','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure and GDPR privacy notice at call opening','GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires notification of data processing at point of collection. FCA regulations require call recording disclosure. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Jasmine speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is recorded and their data rights are protected, providing transparency and informed consent before any discussion begins.',1763114604365);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgs00wo3j6gmb32slcx','cmhyowvgr00wa3j6gn1k0fegb','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain cancellation process, potential fees, or refund entitlement before transferring customer','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), FCA PRIN 6 (TCF)',90,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear communication about financial implications of customer decisions. Before transfer, agent should state: ''My colleague in our cancellations team will calculate any refund due to you. Depending on your policy terms, there may be a cancellation fee, and they''ll explain the exact amount you''ll receive back. They''ll also confirm your cancellation date and send written confirmation.'' **Why it matters**: This manages customer expectations about potential costs and ensures transparency about the cancellation process, preventing surprises and demonstrating fair treatment.',1763114604365);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xg3j6g97g36lla','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any required call opening compliance elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'FCA rules and GDPR Article 13 require specific disclosures at call opening. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and understand their data rights before sharing personal information.',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvgx00xh3j6gc6m290dz','cmhyowvgv00wy3j6gvsbqtm2s','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent only collected customer name and attempted to access quote/policy data without conducting proper DPA verification (no DOB, address, or security questions)','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (integrity and confidentiality), DPA 2018 Section 2',16,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Agent must conduct full DPA verification BEFORE accessing any customer data. Required script: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verifying at least two data points should the agent access systems containing customer information. This prevents unauthorized access to sensitive personal and financial data and protects customers from potential fraud or data breaches.',1763114604369);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvh000y03j6gru916af9','cmhyowvgz00xn3j6gzp87efrf','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent provided NO regulatory call opening whatsoever - missing firm identification, FCA authorization statement, call recording disclosure, and GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy information)',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. FCA rules require call recording disclosure. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded for their protection, and how their personal data is being used - fundamental transparency requirements.',1763114604372);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvh000y13j6g9t0gvvi8','cmhyowvgz00xn3j6gzp87efrf','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy data (accepted policy reference and looked up account) without conducting any DPA verification - no date of birth, address, or security questions asked','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Security of processing), Data Protection Act 2018 Section 2, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R (Data security)',5,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Firms must verify identity BEFORE accessing customer records. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after successful verification: ''Thank you, that''s verified. Now, what''s your policy reference?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized individuals from accessing someone else''s policy information by simply knowing a policy number. It protects customers from identity fraud and data breaches, and ensures the firm meets its legal duty to secure personal data.',1763114604372);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvh300yr3j6gyc5delk9','cmhyowvh200y73j6gaakdd6an','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any of the three mandatory call opening elements: (1) FCA authorization status, (2) call recording disclosure, (3) GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Senior Managers Regime), GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Call recording must be disclosed before recording begins (ICO guidance). **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Willett Pickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: These disclosures ensure customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is being recorded, and how their personal data will be used - fundamental transparency requirements for customer protection.',1763114604376);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhb00zi3j6gtp1zy2nr','cmhyowvh900z13j6grk4omltt','high','callOpeningCompliance','Incomplete call opening - agent only mentioned call recording but failed to provide firm identification, regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), GDPR Article 13',40,'FCA rules require clear firm identification and regulatory status disclosure. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Agent must state: ''This is Keith calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and understand their data rights before sharing any personal information.',1763114604383);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhb00zj3j6gpp38ywbn','cmhyowvh900z13j6grk4omltt','medium','followUp','Agent did not offer alternative solutions, referrals, or signposting when unable to provide cover','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',105,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly throughout the customer journey, including when unable to provide services. Agent should state: ''I''m sorry we can''t help with company-owned properties, but I''d be happy to recommend a specialist commercial insurance broker who deals with corporate holiday lets. Would you like me to provide some contact details or send you information by email?'' This demonstrates TCF by ensuring the customer isn''t left without options and maintains trust in the firm even when a sale cannot be completed.',1763114604383);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhf01043j6g8fwyvumn','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer personal data (email address and renewal information) without conducting DPA verification','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and Confidentiality, Data Protection Act 2018',14,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires that personal data is processed securely with integrity and confidentiality. Before accessing any customer policy data, the agent must verify the caller''s identity to prevent unauthorized disclosure. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? Thank you. And can you confirm the postcode on the policy?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents fraudsters from obtaining customer information by impersonating policyholders and protects customers from identity theft and data breaches.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhf01053j6grt33wqy4','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Complete absence of call opening compliance - no firm identification, regulatory status, call recording disclosure, or GDPR notice provided','ICOBS 4.5.1R (Firm Identification), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy Notice), FCA PRIN 2.1.1R (Skill, Care and Diligence)',2,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''Good morning, this is [name] from Pikl Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: Customers have the right to know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data is being used. This builds trust and ensures transparency.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhf01063j6gjurjp1m7','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','critical','professionalism','Agent used profanity multiple times while customer was on the line (''Jesus Christ'', ''fucking freezing'') - severe breach of professional standards','FCA PRIN 2.1.1R (Skill, Care and Diligence), SM&CR Conduct Rule 1 (Act with Integrity)',2,'**What the law requires**: FCA Principle 2 requires firms to conduct business with due skill, care and diligence. SM&CR Conduct Rule 1 requires staff to act with integrity. This includes maintaining professional communication standards at all times. **What to say**: When experiencing technical difficulties: ''I apologize, I''m experiencing a brief technical issue. Please bear with me for just a moment while I resolve this.'' Never use profanity or express frustration audibly. **Why it matters**: Unprofessional language damages customer trust, creates poor customer outcomes, and exposes the firm to complaints and regulatory action. It demonstrates lack of care and diligence in customer interactions.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhf01073j6gxkzam3r3','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No mandatory disclosures provided - no service type, remuneration basis, complaints procedure, or FOS rights mentioned','ICOBS 4.5.2R (Service and Remuneration), ICOBS 6.1.5R (Complaints Information), DISP 1.2',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.2R requires disclosure of service type (advised/non-advised) and remuneration basis. ICOBS 6.1.5R requires information about complaints procedures and FOS rights. **What to say**: ''We''re providing you with a non-advised service today, which means we''re not making a personal recommendation. We''re paid by commission from insurers. If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint - I can provide details of our complaints procedure. You also have the right to refer matters to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' **Why it matters**: These disclosures ensure customers understand the nature of the service, potential conflicts of interest, and their rights if things go wrong. This is fundamental to treating customers fairly.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhf01083j6gd3jmzz61','cmhyowvhe00zp3j6gkp98ymii','medium','tcfCompliance','Customer experience significantly compromised by technical difficulties and unprofessional handling - poor customer outcome','FCA PRIN 2.1.1R Principle 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',8,'**What the law requires**: FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly and deliver appropriate customer outcomes. This includes managing technical difficulties professionally. **What to say**: ''I sincerely apologize for the delay. I''m having a technical issue accessing our system, but I''m working to resolve it now. I really appreciate your patience. To make sure I don''t waste any more of your time, would you prefer I call you back in 5 minutes once this is resolved?'' **Why it matters**: How firms handle service difficulties is a key TCF indicator. Professional management of problems maintains customer trust and demonstrates commitment to fair treatment even when systems fail.',1763114604387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvho011l3j6gbnlbuopq','cmhyowvhm01123j6gqin9qy9q','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not identify the firm name or FCA regulatory status at the call opening. This information was only provided later at timestamp 353 during the pre-sale disclosure script.','ICOBS 2.2.2R - Initial disclosure requirements',37,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to disclose their identity and regulatory status before conducting insurance business. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good afternoon, this is Keith calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority, FCA number [XXX]. This call is being recorded for quality and monitoring purposes.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with and that the firm is properly regulated before any business discussion begins, providing essential consumer protection.',1763114604396);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhs012a3j6g6pruib7s','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, FCA regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Call recording must be disclosed for consent and transparency. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data and conversation will be used - fundamental transparency requirements.',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhs012b3j6gwvdueyrh','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy details using policy number without conducting DPA verification (name + date of birth) first - serious GDPR breach','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and Confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',107,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data including protection against unauthorized processing. Firms must verify identity BEFORE accessing customer records to prevent data breaches. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? Thank you. And can you confirm your postcode?'' Only after verification: ''Thank you, I can now access your policy.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized individuals from accessing someone else''s policy data by simply knowing a policy number. It''s a fundamental data security control that protects customers from identity fraud and data breaches.',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhs012c3j6gkqfe2nbp','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain refund calculation methodology or cancellation fees (if applicable) - customer only told there would be ''no refund'' after 14 days without explanation of pro-rata calculation','ICOBS 7.1.6R, FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',297,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 7.1.6R requires clear information about cancellation terms including how refunds are calculated. Customers must understand what they''ll receive back. **What to say**: ''As your policy started on 14th October and we''re now past the 14-day cooling-off period, any refund would be calculated on a pro-rata basis for the unused time, minus our X administration fee. Let me calculate exactly what you''d receive back... [calculate]. Does that make sense?'' **Why it matters**: Customers need to understand the financial impact of cancellation to make informed decisions. Simply saying ''no refund'' without explanation can be misleading if a pro-rata refund is actually due.',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhs012d3j6gr4303udv','cmhyowvhq011r3j6g45v9sulr','medium','productKnowledge','Agent initially provided incorrect information about cooling-off period (stated 30 days instead of 14 days), though later corrected after checking with management','ICOBS 7.1.4R, FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',297,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 7.1.4R specifies a 14-day cooling-off period for insurance contracts. Agents must provide accurate information to avoid customer detriment. **What to say**: Before taking calls, ensure you know: ''The cooling-off period is 14 days from policy start date or receipt of documents, whichever is later. During this time, customers can cancel for a full refund if no claims have been made.'' **Why it matters**: Incorrect information about cancellation rights could lead customers to miss their cooling-off period or make wrong assumptions about refunds. While the agent corrected the error, initial misinformation creates confusion and undermines trust.',1763114604400);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhv01313j6grrvozmz7','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide firm identification with regulatory status, call recording disclosure, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13',3,'FCA and ICOBS require clear firm identification and call recording disclosure. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. Agent must open with: ''Good morning, this is Callum calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. This is regarding your renewal - we hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and their data rights are protected.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhv01323j6gwuwwlfdk','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy information and assisted with purchase without conducting DPA verification first','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018',3,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data including protection against unauthorized processing. Agent must verify identity BEFORE accessing any policy data. Script: ''Before I can access your policy details and assist you, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? Thank you. And can you confirm the postcode on the policy?'' This protects customer data from unauthorized access and ensures compliance with data protection law.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhv01333j6gz825psjm','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period for the renewal purchase','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights. Agent must state: ''Just to let you know, you have a 14-day cooling-off period from today. If you change your mind for any reason, you can cancel within 14 days for a full refund of any premium paid.'' This ensures customers understand their statutory right to cancel without penalty.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhv01343j6g3c2l95tq','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide information about complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 2.3.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R and ICOBS 2.3.1R require firms to provide complaints handling information. Agent should state: ''If you have any concerns or complaints, please contact us and we''ll work to resolve them. If we can''t resolve your complaint within 8 weeks, or you''re unhappy with our response, you can refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge. Full details are in your policy documents.'' This ensures customers know their rights to complain and access independent dispute resolution.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhv01353j6gw060tmir','cmhyowvhu012j3j6gv11djxrs','medium','salesProcessCompliance','No price breakdown or confirmation provided during the sales process','ICOBS 6.1.5R (Product information)',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear information about the insurance product including price. Agent should confirm: ''Just to confirm, your hosting top-up renewal is 99 including Insurance Premium Tax. You''ll see the full breakdown in your confirmation email.'' This ensures price transparency and helps customers make informed decisions.',1763114604403);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhz013x3j6g9hit32hm','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call opening disclosures: no company identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice (even abbreviated for renewal)','FCA PRIN 2A.2.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'FCA and GDPR require specific disclosures at call commencement. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority, FCA number [XXX]. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that recording is taking place, and that their data is being processed lawfully. For renewals, an abbreviated GDPR notice is acceptable as the relationship is established.',1763114604408);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvhz013y3j6g1qvvpyrx','cmhyowvhy013b3j6g9kuybcwk','low','professionalism','Agent''s comment ''First world problem'' at 02:53 could be perceived as dismissive of customer''s genuine financial concerns about council costs','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',173,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly and with respect. When customers express financial concerns, agents should acknowledge them seriously. Agent should say: ''I understand those additional costs can be challenging. Let me make sure we get you the best value on your insurance today.'' This validates customer concerns while maintaining professionalism and demonstrates TCF in practice by showing empathy for their financial situation.',1763114604408);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvi2014o3j6gjpo97ckp','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - mandatory requirement missing','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty - Act in good faith), GDPR Article 13',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing, including call recording. FCA Consumer Duty requires firms to act in good faith, which includes informing customers their calls are recorded. **What to say**: Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: Customers have a right to know when they''re being recorded so they can make an informed choice about continuing the call. This protects their privacy rights and ensures transparent data processing.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvi2014p3j6gap64537b','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to identify firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization) at call opening','ICOBS 2.2.2R (Communication to customers)',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to communicate their name and regulatory status to customers. This must be done at first contact. **What to say**: Agent must state: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Keith speaking, how can I help?'' **Why it matters**: Customers need to know they''re dealing with a regulated firm to have confidence in the service and understand their protections under the FCA regulatory framework and Financial Ombudsman Service access.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvi2014q3j6gfyadxr2m','cmhyowvi101443j6g7oea3sej','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide GDPR privacy notice appropriate for service call with existing quote','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at data collection. For service calls with existing customers/quotes, an abbreviated notice is acceptable. **What to say**: Agent should state: ''Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. You can find full details on our website or I can send you a copy if you''d like.'' **Why it matters**: Even for existing quotes, customers should be reminded of their data rights and how their information is being used, ensuring ongoing transparency about data processing.',1763114604411);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvi7015f3j6g2lqez2nb','cmhyowvi4014w3j6g0ru4kwzu','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide mandatory call opening disclosures: no clear firm identification, no FCA authorization statement, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice (even abbreviated for renewal)','ICOBS 4.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'ICOBS 4.5.1R and FCA PRIN 7 require clear firm identification and regulatory status disclosure at first contact. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information. Agent must open ALL calls with: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We are authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. [For renewals add:] This is regarding your policy renewal and we already hold your details on file in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded, and how their data is being used - fundamental transparency requirements.',1763114604415);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvib01673j6gg03aqs0i','cmhyowvia015l3j6g36rm5bdi','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call','GDPR Article 13 - Information to be provided where personal data are collected from the data subject',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires that when personal data is collected, the data subject must be informed that the call is being recorded and the purpose of the recording. **What to say**: Agent must state at call opening: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded before they share any personal information, giving them the opportunity to object or disconnect if they''re not comfortable. It''s a fundamental transparency requirement under GDPR.',1763114604420);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvig016y3j6g99mj17se','cmhyowvif016d3j6g8c6g2fej','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call','GDPR Article 13 and ICO guidance on call recording',0,'GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing, including call recording. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded before they share any information, respecting their right to be informed about data processing activities.',1763114604425);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvil017k3j6gye8b8zgc','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed and discussed customer policy data including name, address, postcode, property details, and sums insured without conducting any DPA verification. This is a fundamental GDPR breach.','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and Confidentiality, GDPR Article 32 - Security of Processing, DPA 2018',122,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) and Article 32 require appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Even for broker-to-underwriter calls, the agent must verify the caller''s identity and authority before accessing customer data. Agent must state: ''Before I access the policy, can I take your full name and date of birth to verify your identity? And can you confirm you''re authorized to discuss this customer''s details on behalf of [broker firm name]?'' This ensures only authorized individuals access sensitive customer information and protects against data breaches, social engineering, and unauthorized disclosure.',1763114604430);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvil017l3j6gc62h44uz','cmhyowvij01743j6gtpxcylds','medium','professionalism','Extended personal conversation about system shortcuts (OGI F10/F11 discussion) was excessive and extended call time unnecessarily, reducing efficiency','FCA PRIN 6 - Treating Customers Fairly (TCF Outcome 3: Efficient Service)',380,'FCA Principle 6 (Treating Customers Fairly) requires firms to provide efficient service. While building rapport is important, extended non-business conversations can delay service to other customers and increase operational costs. Agent should keep friendly banter brief: ''That''s a great tip - I''ll try it later. Now let me get this quote processed for you quickly.'' This maintains warmth while respecting everyone''s time and ensuring efficient service delivery.',1763114604430);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvip018d3j6gvuxy74zz','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification, no FCA regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy notice at data collection)',1,'FCA and ICOBS regulations require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Agent must open EVERY call with: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data is being used - fundamental consumer protections.',1763114604434);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvip018e3j6gjgr8t2tg','cmhyowvio017r3j6go2evih8z','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy data without conducting any DPA verification - no date of birth, postcode, security questions, or any identity verification before viewing account information','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018 Section 2, FCA SYSC 3.2.6R (Systems and controls for data security)',40,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) and DPA 2018 require appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Agent must NEVER access customer data before verification. Required process: ''Before I access your account, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after receiving and confirming at least TWO data points should the agent access the system. This prevents unauthorized access to sensitive customer information and protects against fraud and data breaches.',1763114604434);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviu01943j6gw5a5vmca','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with new customers. FCA rules require call recording disclosure and firm identification. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Before we start, I need to let you know we collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or I can send it to you.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand how their data will be used before sharing sensitive information and confirms they''re dealing with a regulated firm.',1763114604439);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviu01953j6gk5osl1dp','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent collected extensive personal data (name, address, email, property details) before completing DPA verification with date of birth, which wasn''t obtained until 24:17 into the call','GDPR Article 5(1)(a) (lawful processing), Data Protection Act 2018',196,'**What the law requires**: GDPR requires lawful basis for processing personal data and verification of identity before accessing or recording personal information. **What to say**: Immediately after call opening: ''Before I can help you today, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verification: ''Thank you, I can now access your details and help with your quote.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to personal data and ensures the person providing information has the right to do so, protecting both customer and firm from data breaches.',1763114604439);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviu01963j6gp7i40lej','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period for new policy purchase','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before or on conclusion of the contract. **What to say**: When presenting the quote or before taking payment: ''I should mention that you have a 14-day cooling-off period from when your policy starts. If you change your mind during this time, you can cancel for a full refund, or a pro-rata refund if cover has already started.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know they can cancel without penalty if they''re not satisfied, supporting informed decision-making and Treating Customers Fairly principles.',1763114604439);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviu01973j6gv581zaet','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No mention of complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have procedures for handling complaints and to inform customers of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. **What to say**: During the call or in follow-up documentation: ''If you''re ever unhappy with our service, we have a complaints procedure. You can contact our complaints team, and if you''re not satisfied with our response, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know how to escalate concerns and access independent dispute resolution, which is a fundamental consumer protection.',1763114604439);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviu01983j6g1r51yooy','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','No disclosure of remuneration basis (commission vs fee)','ICOBS 4.3.1R (IDD Article 19)',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.3.1R requires disclosure of whether remuneration is received by commission or fee. **What to say**: During needs assessment or before quote: ''I should let you know that we receive commission from insurers when you purchase a policy. This doesn''t affect the price you pay, which is set by the insurer.'' **Why it matters**: This transparency allows customers to understand potential conflicts of interest and make informed decisions about whether the broker''s recommendations are in their best interest.',1763114604439);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviu01993j6g52bm9mth','cmhyowvit018k3j6g901ops5y','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Call ended without providing price breakdown or completing the sales process, though this was due to technical/underwriting referral rather than agent error','ICOBS 6.1.5R',2137,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear information about the price, including premium, taxes, and charges. **What to say**: When callback occurs with quote: ''Let me break down the price for you: the annual premium is X, Insurance Premium Tax is Y, and our broker fee is Z, making a total of [total]. You can pay annually or in monthly instalments.'' **Why it matters**: Clear price breakdown ensures customers understand exactly what they''re paying for and can compare products effectively, supporting informed decision-making.',1763114604439);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviy019z3j6gx2cz99sc','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening','GDPR Article 13, FCA SYSC 9.1',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires controllers to inform data subjects when their personal data is being collected, including through call recordings. FCA SYSC 9.1 requires firms to record telephone conversations for MiFID business and maintain audit trails. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Trickle Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded and can object if they wish, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring informed consent.',1763114604443);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviy01a03j6gztpc3ut5','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide GDPR privacy notice at call opening','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires that when personal data is collected directly from the data subject, the controller must provide information about data processing purposes, legal basis, retention periods, and data subject rights at the time of collection. **What to say**: ''We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or I can send it to you.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand how their data will be used and their rights before sharing sensitive personal and financial information, enabling informed consent and transparency.',1763114604443);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowviy01a13j6ggxe0f96n','cmhyowvix019f3j6gvqbnrt44','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer data without conducting proper DPA verification (only collected name, no date of birth or address verification)','GDPR Article 5(1)(f), Data Protection Act 2018 Section 2',48,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires personal data to be processed securely using appropriate technical and organizational measures. The Data Protection Act 2018 requires controllers to verify identity before disclosing personal data to prevent unauthorized access. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your father''s details, I need to verify his identity for data protection. Can I take his full name, date of birth, and postcode please? And can I also confirm your relationship to the policyholder and whether you''re authorized to discuss his policy?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to personal data and ensures only legitimate parties can access sensitive insurance information, protecting customers from fraud and data breaches.',1763114604443);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01ba3j6g4s7b4j9a','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - fundamental FCA requirement missing','FCA PRIN 11 (Relations with regulators), GDPR Article 13',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA expects firms to inform customers that calls are recorded for regulatory and quality purposes. GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing at point of collection. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: Customers have a right to know their conversation is being recorded and stored. This protects both customer privacy rights and provides evidence for regulatory compliance and dispute resolution.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01bb3j6g9qjkfkun','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided - even abbreviated notice required for renewal calls','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing. For renewal calls, an abbreviated notice is acceptable acknowledging data already held. **What to say**: ''As this is a renewal, we already have your details on file and they''re held in accordance with our privacy policy. If you''d like a copy of our privacy notice, I can email that to you.'' **Why it matters**: Even existing customers must be reminded their data is being processed lawfully. This maintains transparency and reminds customers of their ongoing data rights.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01bc3j6g9vgalhsy','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization)','ICOBS 2.2.2R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status in communications with customers. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Pickle Insurance, Keith speaking. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded. How can I help?'' **Why it matters**: Customers have a right to know they''re dealing with a regulated firm, which provides them with regulatory protections including access to the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01bd3j6ggqzo4y9u','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Cooling-off rights not proactively disclosed during sales process - only mentioned reactively when customer asked about cancellation','ICOBS 6.1.5R, Distance Marketing Directive',1774,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before contract conclusion. For renewals, customers must be told about their 14-day cooling-off period. **What to say**: ''Before we proceed, I should mention you have 14 days from your renewal date to cancel for a pro-rata refund if you change your mind. After 14 days, there''s a 30 cancellation charge. Are you happy to proceed?'' **Why it matters**: Customers must know they can cancel without significant penalty if they find better cover elsewhere or change their mind. This prevents customers feeling locked into unsuitable policies.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01be3j6gqaz0iv7e','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights disclosed','DISP 1.2, ICOBS 2.2.2R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2 requires firms to provide information about their complaints procedure. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires disclosure of FOS rights. **What to say**: ''If you''re ever unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint by calling our complaints team on [number] or writing to [address]. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' **Why it matters**: Customers must know how to escalate concerns and access independent dispute resolution. This is a fundamental consumer protection ensuring firms remain accountable.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01bf3j6ggljklbqe','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Price breakdown not clearly itemized - IPT and fees mentioned but not separated from base premium','ICOBS 6.1.9R, FCA PRIN 7',127,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.9R requires clear disclosure of the total price and its component parts including taxes. **What to say**: ''Your total renewal price is 399.18, which breaks down as: base premium 330.48, Insurance Premium Tax 38.70, and guest top-up 30. The monthly option includes a credit charge of 33.53.'' **Why it matters**: Customers need to understand what they''re paying for and identify the true cost of credit. Transparent pricing enables informed decisions and comparison shopping.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyowvja01bg3j6g1iubf620','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Needs assessment could be more thorough - agent accepted customer''s previous assessment without re-validating circumstances','ICOBS 5.1.1R (Demands and needs), FCA PRIN 6 (TCF)',201,'**What the law requires**: Even for non-advised sales, ICOBS 5.1.1R requires firms to obtain information about customer''s demands and needs. For renewals, circumstances should be re-validated. **What to say**: ''I can see we discussed your cover in detail previously. Before we proceed with renewal, let me just confirm - have there been any changes to your circumstances? Any home improvements, new valuable items, or changes to how you use the property? Any changes to who lives there?'' **Why it matters**: Customer circumstances change over time. Re-validating needs ensures the policy remains suitable and prevents under-insurance or coverage gaps that could leave customers unprotected.',1763114604455);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp7u17001otd3rxjqarcie','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Complete absence of mandatory call opening elements - no firm identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notice','ICOBS 4.5.1R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status in all customer communications. Agent must state: ''Good morning/afternoon, you''ve reached [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and their interaction is protected.',1763115115723);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp7u17001ptd3rc5b7v8xx','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided - complete failure to inform customers about data processing','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',1,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with customers. Agent must state: ''We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website at [URL] or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers understand their data rights before sharing any personal information.',1763115115723);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp7u17001qtd3raajiixmq','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','critical','tcfCompliance','Customer directed away from phone contact without explanation or alternative support - potential breach of fair treatment and accessibility obligations','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), Equality Act 2010',1,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly and provide appropriate service channels. If voicemail is necessary, agent must provide: ''Please leave a message with your name, policy number, and contact details, and I''ll return your call within 24 hours. Alternatively, call our main office on [number] for immediate assistance, or email [address].'' This ensures all customers can access service through their preferred method and vulnerable customers aren''t excluded.',1763115115723);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp7u17001rtd3rzr26aag1','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','critical','professionalism','Unprofessional communication - appears to be personal voicemail greeting used for business insurance calls','FCA PRIN 7, SM&CR Conduct Rule 2 (Act with due care, skill and diligence)',1,'SM&CR Conduct Rule 2 requires staff to act with due care, skill and diligence. All customer-facing communications must be professional and business-appropriate. Use company-approved voicemail scripts that include: firm name, regulatory status, alternative contact methods, and expected response time. Personal-style greetings undermine customer confidence and regulatory compliance.',1763115115723);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp7u17001std3rleyh6ka2','cmhyp7u0z001btd3r34sz1ng3','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No information provided about complaints procedures, FOS rights, or how to escalate concerns','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have accessible complaints procedures. Voicemail greeting should include: ''If you wish to make a complaint, please contact our complaints team on [number] or email [address]. You can find full details of our complaints procedure on our website.'' This ensures customers know how to raise concerns even when unable to speak to an agent directly.',1763115115723);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp7ytu002std3rzdgbs6es','cmhyp7ytr002itd3rljqj4o2c','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent''s voicemail greeting identifies incorrect company name (''Help Bank'' instead of Pikl Insurance), failing firm identification requirements','ICOBS 2.2.2R - Clear, fair and not misleading communications',0,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires all communications to be clear, fair and not misleading. Firm identification is mandatory. Agent must update voicemail to state: ''You''ve reached [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Please leave a message and I''ll return your call as soon as possible.'' This ensures customers can clearly identify who they''re dealing with and the regulatory status of the firm, even when the agent is unavailable.',1763115121939);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp80bd003ctd3r1v90o9h4','cmhyp80b8002wtd3r6qwy7ngq','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No opening compliance elements delivered - firm regulatory status, call recording disclosure, and GDPR notice all missing. However, this is because the call went to voicemail with no live customer interaction.','ICOBS 4.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to disclose their identity and regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. FCA PRIN 7 requires clear communication with customers. **What to say**: When customer returns the call, agent MUST open with: ''Good morning, you''re through to Rebecca at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is processed in accordance with our privacy policy - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data at any time.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded, and that their data rights are protected. This is foundational to treating customers fairly and maintaining regulatory compliance. NOTE: In this specific case, compliance was impossible as no live conversation occurred - this must be rectified on the return call.',1763115123865);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp84jy003wtd3ryi63pbj9','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No call opening compliance elements provided - no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, no GDPR notice. However, this is a voicemail message where live compliance disclosures are impossible.','ICOBS 4.2.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7',0,'ICOBS 4.2.1R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. In voicemail context, agent should state: ''This is Keith from Pickett Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. Regarding your quote request, please call me back on 0800-254-5171. When we speak, I''ll need to verify your identity and explain how we handle your data in line with GDPR requirements.'' This acknowledges compliance obligations while recognizing voicemail limitations. OPERATIONAL RECOMMENDATION: Consider whether voicemail is appropriate for initial insurance quote discussions that require mandatory disclosures.',1763115129358);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp84jy003xtd3r2auoduds','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','No DPA verification conducted before discussing customer''s quote request. However, this is inherent to voicemail format where two-way verification is impossible.','GDPR Article 5, Data Protection Act 2018',16,'GDPR Article 5 requires lawful processing and security of personal data. Before discussing any policy details, agent must verify identity with minimum of name and date of birth. In voicemail context, agent should avoid referencing specific policy details and state: ''I have your quote ready to discuss. When you call back, I''ll need to verify your identity with your date of birth before we go through the details. This protects your personal information.'' This demonstrates data protection awareness even in voicemail format.',1763115129358);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp84jy003ytd3rhisv0vx3','cmhyp84jq003gtd3rghgvxhao','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No mandatory disclosures provided regarding service type, remuneration, complaints procedure, or customer rights. Voicemail format prevents these required communications.','ICOBS 4.5.1R, ICOBS 6.1.5R',NULL,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires disclosure of service type (advised/non-advised) and remuneration basis. ICOBS 6.1.5R requires information about complaints procedures. In voicemail, agent should acknowledge these requirements: ''When we speak, I''ll explain how our service works, your cancellation rights, and how to contact us if you have any concerns. I want to make sure you have all the information you need to make the right decision.'' This sets expectation for compliant conversation while recognizing voicemail limitations. CRITICAL: Do not provide quotes or discuss policy details via voicemail where mandatory disclosures cannot be delivered.',1763115129358);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp8ent004wtd3rs71udlwo','cmhyp8eno004ctd3rupyyr7in','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide ANY of the required call opening compliance elements: (1) No firm identification with regulatory status, (2) No call recording disclosure, (3) No GDPR privacy notice. Agent only said ''Hi, good morning, this is a Jess at Pickle, how can I help?'' This is a fundamental FCA compliance breach.','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy Information)',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves with regulatory status at call opening. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with data subjects. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''Good morning, this is Jess calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded, and that they understand their data rights before sharing any personal information. This is fundamental to consumer protection and regulatory accountability.',1763115142457);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp8i2j005jtd3r02or8o0e','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with new customers, including purpose of processing, legal basis, and data subject rights. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to Jess at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and what happens to their personal information before they share sensitive data.',1763115146876);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp8i2j005ktd3rq9bqby83','cmhyp8i2f0052td3ril2rzlin','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent attempted to collect customer''s name without establishing lawful basis for processing or completing any verification','GDPR Article 6 (Lawfulness of processing), GDPR Article 13',54,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 6 requires a lawful basis for processing personal data. For new customers, this requires informed consent or legitimate interest with transparency. Article 13 requires information about processing before data collection. **What to say**: Before collecting any data, state: ''To provide you with a quote for your Airbnb property insurance, I''ll need to collect some personal information including your name, address, and property details. We''ll use this information solely to assess your insurance needs and provide a quote. Are you happy to proceed?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand why their data is being collected and consent to processing before sharing personal information, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring lawful data processing.',1763115146876);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp8khe0065td3rmz6bqpmw','cmhyp8kh9005otd3ryqqyk0jy','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Communications to customers), GDPR Article 13 (Information to be provided)',1,'FCA and GDPR regulations require specific disclosures at call opening. Agent must state: ''Good morning, this is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the firm is regulated, and that their data and conversation are being processed lawfully.',1763115150003);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp8khe0066td3ri6l6i3o3','cmhyp8kh9005otd3ryqqyk0jy','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed and discussed policy details (credit agreement amounts, payment schedules, policy numbers) without conducting DPA verification. No security questions, date of birth, or address verification performed before accessing customer data','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), GDPR Article 32 (Security of processing), DPA 2018 Section 2',3,'GDPR Article 5 requires that personal data is processed securely and confidentially. Agent must verify identity BEFORE accessing any policy information. Agent must state: ''Before I can discuss your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can you please confirm your full name, date of birth, and postcode?'' This protects customers from unauthorized access to their sensitive financial and personal information, even on callback situations where the customer may be expecting the call.',1763115150003);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp8rhb007ltd3rvgn2is2q','cmhyp8rh5006ytd3r06rdl17n','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure and GDPR privacy notice at call opening','GDPR Article 13, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R, Data Protection Act 2018',1,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with new customers, including purpose of data processing and customer rights. FCA rules require call recording disclosure. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, Picker Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or we can send it to you. How can I help?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are informed about data collection before sharing sensitive personal information, and are aware the call is recorded. It''s a fundamental data protection requirement for all new business contacts.',1763115159072);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp989d008etd3rf9vgsldw','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent completely failed to provide mandatory call opening compliance elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 4.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 6',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at [Company Name], we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and complaints can be escalated to the FOS, that their conversation is recorded, and how their data will be used - fundamental consumer protections.',1763115180818);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp989d008ftd3rebfk1koj','cmhyp9899007xtd3re7k5lhhp','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent failed to conduct proper DPA verification before accessing customer quote data. Only requested name and email, did not verify date of birth or other security information before looking up the quote','GDPR Article 5(1)(f), Data Protection Act 2018',14,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Firms must verify identity before accessing customer records. **What to say**: After taking the name, immediately state: ''For data protection purposes, can I please take your date of birth and postcode to verify your identity?'' Only after successful verification: ''Thank you, I can now access your quote details.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to personal data and ensures you''re speaking to the genuine customer, not a fraudster attempting to access their information. It''s a fundamental data security control.',1763115180818);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9c15009rtd3r2kerslvs','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy information using reference number without conducting DPA verification (name, date of birth, address)','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and Confidentiality, DPA 2018',37,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data including protection against unauthorised processing. Before accessing ANY policy data, agent must verify customer identity by asking: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' This prevents unauthorised access to sensitive personal and financial information and protects customers from potential fraud or data breaches.',1763115185705);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9c15009std3rb8wkjhm1','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.2.1R (Transparency), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'FCA transparency rules and GDPR Article 13 require disclosure at first contact. Agent must state: ''Good morning, Pikl Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Pikl Insurance is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' This ensures customers know they''re being recorded, can verify the firm''s legitimacy, and understand their data is being processed lawfully.',1763115185705);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9c15009ttd3r8u3hq0gc','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off rights for the renewal policy','ICOBS 6.1.5R - Cancellation Rights',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires insurers to inform customers of cancellation rights. Agent must state: ''When you complete your renewal online, you''ll have 14 days from when your policy starts to cancel for a refund if you change your mind. This is your cooling-off period and you''ll see full details in your policy documents.'' This ensures customers understand they can cancel without penalty during the cooling-off period, which is a key consumer protection.',1763115185705);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9c15009utd3rgdg8zrr9','cmhyp9c0z0099td3rpctxgpmk','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide information about complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R - Complaint Handling Procedures',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective complaints handling procedures and inform customers of their rights. Agent must state: ''If you have any concerns about your policy or our service, you can make a complaint to us and we''ll respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know how to escalate concerns and access independent dispute resolution.',1763115185705);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9e1x00agtd3rke4bp37o','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any regulatory opening - no FCA authorization statement, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (SM&CR), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at first contact. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice when collecting personal data. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data - for our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded, and how their personal data will be used and protected.',1763115188325);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9e1x00ahtd3rnfqw7ngb','cmhyp9e1s00a0td3r5kshckd7','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent collected customer''s full name and discussed policy details without conducting any DPA verification (no DOB, address, or policy number requested)','GDPR Article 5(1)(f), DPA 2018 Section 2, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',100,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data including protection against unauthorized processing. Firms must verify identity before accessing or recording customer information. **What to say**: ''Before I can help you today, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name, date of birth, and postcode please?'' Only after verification: ''Thank you, I can now access your details securely.'' **Why it matters**: DPA verification prevents unauthorized access to customer data, protects against fraud and identity theft, and ensures compliance with data security principles. Without verification, the firm cannot confirm they''re speaking to the genuine customer or data subject.',1763115188325);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9f0o00b2td3r5fevop13','cmhyp9f0k00altd3r62l1yhfc','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide firm identification or regulatory status at call opening. Call recording disclosure was provided but came after DPA verification rather than at the start of the call.','ICOBS 4.5.1R and FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to provide their name and regulatory status in communications with customers. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, this is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for training and regulatory purposes.'' This must be the FIRST thing said, before DPA verification or any discussion. This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with and that the firm is properly regulated, building trust and meeting transparency requirements.',1763115189577);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bqtd3rvyty8wxe','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13',1,'FCA PRIN 7 and ICOBS 2.2.2R require clear firm identification and regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. Agent must state: ''Good afternoon, this is Jess calling from Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and how their data is being used.',1763115190315);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9fl600brtd3rgu6nyz0n','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','high','dataProtectionCompliance','Inadequate DPA verification - agent only collected customer name without secondary identifier (date of birth or postcode) before accessing policy details','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018',34,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Agent must collect TWO identifiers before accessing policy information. Script: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' This prevents unauthorized access to customer data and protects against social engineering fraud.',1763115190315);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bstd3rxt18nj81','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to provide complaints procedure information or Financial Ombudsman Service rights at any point during the call','DISP 1.2 (Obligation to have complaints handling procedures), FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',NULL,'DISP 1.2 requires firms to make customers aware of their right to complain and refer matters to the Financial Ombudsman Service. Agent should state at call close: ''If you ever need to make a complaint about our service, please contact us and we''ll provide our complaints procedure. If you''re not satisfied with our response within 8 weeks, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights and how to escalate concerns if needed.',1763115190315);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9fl600bttd3rn8kxcira','cmhyp9fl200b6td3r0lral0cg','medium','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy notes and details immediately after only collecting name, without completing proper two-factor verification','GDPR Article 32 (Security of processing)',52,'GDPR Article 32 requires appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure data security. Agent must complete full DPA verification (name + DOB/postcode) BEFORE stating ''Just having a little read through the notes.'' This prevents potential data breaches where an unauthorized person could access policy information by only knowing the customer''s name.',1763115190315);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9gsy00cftd3ru4ltmum5','cmhyp9gsu00bxtd3re51zdp4k','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no firm identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR acknowledgment','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',0,'FCA and ICOBS rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at the start of calls. GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning/afternoon, this is [Agent Name] calling from [Company Name]. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the firm is regulated, and that their conversation is being recorded and data protected.',1763115191891);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9gsy00cgtd3r4cp340th','cmhyp9gsu00bxtd3re51zdp4k','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not mention complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights when discussing policy corrections and potential refund issues','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 2.3.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have effective complaints handling procedures and inform customers of their rights. When discussing policy issues, corrections, or potential disputes (like refund timing), agent should state: ''If you have any concerns about how we''ve handled this, you can make a complaint through our complaints procedure. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. You also have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service if you''re not satisfied with our response.'' This ensures customers know their rights to escalate concerns and provides regulatory protection.',1763115191891);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9je200d1td3ra76yhqar','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','critical','callOpeningCompliance','CONTEXT: This is an internal colleague-to-colleague call, NOT a customer call. Compliance requirements (firm identification, call recording disclosure, GDPR notice) do not apply to internal communications. However, these MUST be present when the agent calls the customer back.','ICOBS 4.2.1R, GDPR Article 13 (applies to customer calls only)',0,'When calling Mr. Ben Williams back, the agent MUST provide a compliant call opening. ICOBS 4.2.1R and GDPR Article 13 require: ''Good morning, Mr. Williams, this is [Agent Name] calling from [Company Name], we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures the customer knows who is calling, that they''re regulated, and that their data is protected.',1763115195242);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9je200d2td3riqxlwnlm','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','CONTEXT: No DPA verification conducted, but this is an internal call between colleagues. When the agent calls the customer back, DPA verification (name + DOB minimum) MUST be completed BEFORE accessing or discussing any policy details.','GDPR Article 5, Data Protection Act 2018',NULL,'GDPR Article 5 requires lawful processing and data security. Before discussing Mr. Williams'' quote details, the agent must verify identity: ''For data protection purposes, can I please confirm your full name and date of birth?'' Only after successful verification should the agent access policy information or discuss quote details. This prevents unauthorized access to personal data and protects customer privacy.',1763115195242);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9je200d3td3rvdpj59vp','cmhyp9jdx00cktd3r01rjzd0k','medium','dataProtectionCompliance','Email system failures mentioned multiple times - emails bouncing, going to archive/deleted folders. This creates risk that customers are not receiving policy documents, which is a regulatory requirement.','ICOBS 6.1.5R - Provision of information',63,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires insurers to provide policy documentation to customers. The email system issues must be escalated immediately to IT and management. Implement a workaround process: ''Mr. Williams, I apologize that you didn''t receive the documents. I''ll email them again now and also send them by post to ensure you receive them. Can you confirm your postal address?'' This ensures compliance with documentation requirements while the technical issue is resolved.',1763115195242);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9k5y00dltd3rkitvjaw8','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer policy data without completing proper DPA verification - only requested name, no date of birth or additional security questions asked before bringing up customer details on system','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and Confidentiality, DPA 2018 Section 2',30,'GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Before accessing ANY customer data on system, agent must verify identity with minimum two data points. Agent must say: ''To access your policy details securely, I need to verify your identity. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Then verify both match system records BEFORE accessing policy information. This prevents unauthorized data access and protects customers from potential fraud or data breaches.',1763115196246);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9k5y00dmtd3ru34lishw','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No call recording disclosure provided at call opening - customer not informed that call is being recorded','GDPR Article 13 - Information to be provided, ICO Guidance on call recording',0,'GDPR Article 13 requires transparency about data processing at point of collection. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance, training, and regulatory purposes.'' This must be said BEFORE any substantive conversation begins. This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being captured and can object if they wish, fulfilling the transparency principle of data protection law.',1763115196246);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9k5y00dntd3ribq0vadd','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state FCA regulatory status during call opening - firm identification incomplete','ICOBS 4.5.1R - Information about the firm',0,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to provide their name and regulatory status to customers. Agent must state: ''You''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This can be brief but must be included in the call opening. This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and have FCA protections available to them, including access to the Financial Ombudsman Service if needed.',1763115196246);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9k5y00dotd3rhn64eu3i','cmhyp9k5s00d7td3rj77nl533','low','professionalism','Agent used overly familiar language (''my love'') which may be inappropriate in professional financial services context','FCA PRIN 6 - Treating Customers Fairly',50,'While not a direct regulatory breach, FCA Principle 6 requires treating customers fairly with due regard to their information needs. Professional language maintains appropriate boundaries and ensures all customers feel respected regardless of age, gender, or background. Agent should use: ''Is that alright?'' or ''Does that work for you, Dan?'' instead of terms of endearment. This maintains professionalism while still being warm and personable, ensuring fair treatment for all customer demographics.',1763115196246);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9t3v00ectd3r8paq70zj','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any regulatory call opening - no firm identification with FCA status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7',1,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. FCA PRIN 7 requires clear communication. Agent must state: ''Good morning/afternoon, this is [Full Name] calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and what happens to their data - fundamental consumer protections.',1763115207836);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9t3v00edtd3rih5layao','cmhyp9t3p00dutd3r1ajtdz3h','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent collected customer''s personal data (full name) without conducting DPA verification or establishing lawful basis for processing','GDPR Article 6, Data Protection Act 2018, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',145,'GDPR Article 6 requires a lawful basis for processing personal data, and firms must verify identity before accessing or collecting data. Agent must state BEFORE collecting any information: ''Before I can help you today, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? [After receiving] Thank you. And can you confirm your postcode?'' Only after verification should the agent proceed with collecting additional details or discussing the inquiry. This protects both the customer''s data and ensures the firm is speaking to the correct person, preventing fraud and unauthorized disclosure.',1763115207836);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000f5td3rkh3p9qfz','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to identify firm''s regulatory status at call opening','ICOBS 4.5.1R',0,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status before conducting business. Agent must state: ''Hi, it''s Rebecca from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and can verify credentials if needed.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000f6td3rtpz0gp4x','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period for new insurance policy','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before contract conclusion. Agent must state: ''You have 14 days from when your policy starts or when you receive your documents, whichever is later, to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is your cooling-off period.'' This protects customers'' right to reconsider their purchase without penalty.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000f7td3r135d87b9','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to explain complaints procedure and Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to inform customers of their right to complain and access to FOS. Agent must state: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint and we''ll respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights to independent dispute resolution.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000f8td3rm86gsmbs','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide clear price breakdown including premium, IPT, and any fees separately','ICOBS 6.1.5R',NULL,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear disclosure of price components. Agent must state: ''Your total annual premium is X, which includes: insurance premium of Y, Insurance Premium Tax of Z at 12%, and our administration fee of A. For monthly payments, there''s a credit charge of B, making your monthly payment C.'' This transparency allows customers to understand exactly what they''re paying for.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000f9td3rqxmq7p9t','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','high','salesProcessCompliance','Agent attempted to proceed with sale without establishing whether customer could legally purchase due to existing insurance coverage','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',53,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly and avoid selling unsuitable products. Agent must conduct thorough fact-finding before proceeding: ''Before we finalize this quote, I need to confirm your current insurance arrangements. Do you have any existing buildings or contents insurance on this property? What are your mortgage provider''s insurance requirements?'' This prevents potential dual insurance issues and ensures the product is suitable for the customer''s circumstances.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000fatd3rxx60wgvu','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide GDPR privacy notice explaining data processing, customer rights, and retention','GDPR Article 13',0,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact for new business. Agent must state: ''We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance quotes and services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. We retain your information for 7 years in line with regulatory requirements. For our full privacy policy, visit our website at [URL] or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers understand how their data will be used before sharing sensitive information.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000fbtd3rdzg89js9','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','medium','tcfCompliance','Agent continued to push toward sale despite customer expressing confusion and uncertainty about existing coverage arrangements','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',243,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to ensure customers can make informed decisions. When a customer expresses confusion, agent must pause the sales process: ''I can hear you''re uncertain about your existing insurance arrangements. Let''s not proceed with this purchase until you''ve had a chance to check your mortgage documents and current coverage. I don''t want you to buy something that might not be suitable or could cause dual insurance issues. Would you like me to send you a checklist of what to look for?'' This demonstrates fair treatment and prevents potential mis-selling.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyp9wb000fctd3r14xk02gv','cmhyp9wau00ejtd3rjtyysco1','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not conduct adequate needs assessment to understand customer''s rental property requirements and existing coverage','ICOBS 5.2.1R',53,'ICOBS 5.2.1R requires firms to obtain necessary information about customer circumstances. Agent must ask: ''Let me understand your situation fully. Is this property currently rented out or vacant? What insurance do you currently have in place? What does your mortgage require? Are there any claims history I should know about?'' This structured approach ensures the product recommended meets the customer''s actual needs and circumstances.',1763115211980);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypa0o000fxtd3retm70rgw','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any of the required call opening elements: firm identification with regulatory status, call recording disclosure, or GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, DPA 2018',1,'FCA and GDPR regulations require full disclosure at call opening. Agent must state: ''Good morning, this is [name] from Tickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and understand their data rights before sharing any information.',1763115217633);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypa0o000fytd3rv8yxztea','cmhypa0nw00fgtd3r6vpz4c94','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent collected customer email address and discussed policy details without conducting DPA verification (name and date of birth)','GDPR Article 5 (lawfulness, fairness, transparency), DPA 2018, FCA data security requirements',850,'GDPR Article 5 requires lawful processing and verification of identity before accessing personal data. Agent must verify identity BEFORE discussing policy details or taking information. Script: ''Before I can help you today, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Then confirm: ''Thank you, I''ve verified your details and can now access your information.'' This protects both the customer from fraud and the firm from data breaches by ensuring we''re speaking to the correct person.',1763115217633);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypa7gx00gntd3rew051y0n','cmhypa7gs00g4td3r478tnsw7','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at the start of the call','ICOBS 2.2.2R and FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear communication with customers, and FCA guidance mandates disclosure when calls are recorded. The customer must be informed before the recording begins. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to Pickle Insurance, Keith speaking. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded and can consent or object, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring transparency in line with GDPR and FCA conduct rules.',1763115226450);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypaa5800hctd3r6ti70ya5','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements at the start of the call - no firm identification, no FCA authorization statement, no call recording disclosure. These were only provided at timestamp 518 (8 minutes 38 seconds into the call), after policy details had already been discussed and adjusted.','FCA PRIN 2A.2.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13',2,'FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and disclose call recording at the START of every call. Agent must open with: ''Good morning, this is Keith calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority, FCA number [XXX]. This call is being recorded for quality, training, and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal call, we hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with and that the call is recorded before any business is conducted, protecting their rights under GDPR and FCA regulations.',1763115229916);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypaa5800hdtd3rlnnxcxrv','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explicitly mention Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS) rights. While a complaints contact number was provided, the 8-week timeline and FOS referral rights were not clearly stated.','DISP 1.2.1R',453,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to inform customers of their right to refer complaints to the Financial Ombudsman Service. Agent must state: ''If you need to make a complaint, please call us on 0800-254-5171. We''ll aim to resolve it quickly, but if we can''t resolve it within 8 weeks, or if you''re unhappy with our response, you have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers understand their full complaint rights and the independent review process available to them.',1763115229916);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypaa5800hetd3rt3j7fyyb','cmhypaa5300grtd3rnfg2yh74','low','salesProcessCompliance','Agent stated ''We''ve provided a recommendation on this product'' but earlier clearly stated ''we don''t provide any advice or make any specific recommendations'' - this is contradictory and could confuse the customer about the service type.','ICOBS 4.5.1R',441,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires clarity on whether a sale is advised or non-advised. Agent must be consistent and state: ''As I mentioned earlier, we''re providing you with information on a non-advised basis - this means we haven''t made a personal recommendation. We''ve provided sufficient information for you to make your own informed decision about whether this policy meets your needs.'' This ensures customers clearly understand they are responsible for assessing suitability when no advice is given.',1763115229916);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypafov00i5td3rhwiy8zgo','cmhypafop00hktd3rguq4kpkn','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide call recording disclosure at the beginning of the call','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly) and GDPR Article 13',1,'FCA guidance requires firms to inform customers when calls are being recorded. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good afternoon, you''re through to Pickle Insurance, Jasmin speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' This ensures transparency and allows customers to consent to recording before proceeding. While the agent did pause recording for payment details (excellent practice), the initial disclosure was missing.',1763115237104);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypahif00jhtd3rlgt7csoa','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening','ICOBS 2.2.3R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'ICOBS 2.2.3R and FCA Principle 7 require clear communication with customers, including notification of call recording. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded and can object if they wish, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring informed consent.',1763115239464);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypahif00jitd3rsdnnjxoz','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization)','ICOBS 4.5.1R',1,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status to customers. Agent must state: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'' or ''We''re FCA regulated.'' This is a fundamental consumer protection that ensures customers know they''re dealing with a legitimate, regulated insurance intermediary and have access to regulatory protections including the Financial Ombudsman Service.',1763115239464);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypahif00jjtd3r2rxbg76z','cmhypahi700ibtd3rv8gkhw00','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide GDPR privacy notice or acknowledge data already held','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',1,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice when collecting personal data. For existing customer service calls, an abbreviated notice is acceptable. Agent should state: ''Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy'' or ''We''re calling regarding your previous inquiry - we hold your details on file.'' This ensures customers are aware of how their data is being processed and their rights, even in follow-up contacts.',1763115239464);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypahku00jmtd3rr0lk7fcs','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any call opening compliance elements: no call recording disclosure, no FCA regulatory status, and no GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 4.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact explaining data collection purposes and customer rights. Call recording must be disclosed before recording begins. **What to say**: ''Good afternoon, Pickle Insurance, Rebecca speaking. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. We collect your personal data to provide insurance services - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit pickle.co.uk. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and what happens to their personal data - fundamental transparency requirements protecting consumer rights.',1763115239551);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypahku00jntd3rkdjo374i','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not clarify service type (non-advised/information only) when discussing insurance options','ICOBS 4.5.2R, IDD Article 23',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.2R requires firms to state whether they are providing advice or information only. When a customer asks about products, the agent must clarify the service basis. **What to say**: ''Just to let you know, I''m providing information about our products today rather than personal advice. You''ll need to decide if the cover is suitable for your needs, or we can arrange an advised consultation if you''d prefer.'' **Why it matters**: This manages customer expectations about the level of service and protects both parties - customers understand they must assess suitability themselves, and the firm avoids potential mis-selling liability.',1763115239551);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypahku00jotd3rtf95kvdf','cmhypahi700i9td3r6oyjt1p1','low','followUp','No offer to send product information, policy documents, or summary of discussion in writing','ICOBS 6.1.5R (policy documentation), TCF Principle 6',742,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires policy information to be provided in good time before contract conclusion. TCF Principle 6 requires clear information at appropriate times. **What to say**: ''Before you go, can I take your email address? I''ll send you our holiday let insurance product guide, details of the host top-up cover, and a link to get your quote online. You''ll also receive full policy documentation before you purchase.'' **Why it matters**: Written information allows customers to make informed decisions in their own time, review terms carefully, and ensures they have documentation for future reference - supporting fair treatment and informed decision-making.',1763115239551);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypalxf00kftd3rjnhoertd','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide firm identification including regulatory status at call opening','ICOBS 4.5.1R',6,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires insurance intermediaries to disclose their name and regulatory status before conducting business. Agent must state: ''Good morning, I''m Will calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and can verify credentials if needed.',1763115245187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypalxf00kgtd3rk4me111v','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','high','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided at call opening for new business sale','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',6,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact when collecting personal data. Agent must state: ''Before we proceed, I need to let you know we collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website at [URL] or I can send it to you by email or post.'' This ensures customers understand their data rights before sharing sensitive information.',1763115245187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypalxf00khtd3rfgqodym9','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','critical','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period for new policy sale','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights for distance contracts. Agent must state: ''You have 14 days from your policy start date or when you receive your documents, whichever is later, to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period.'' This ensures customers know they can cancel without penalty if they''re not satisfied with the policy.',1763115245187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypalxf00kitd3rdbkssc7k','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','No mention of complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to provide information about their complaints handling procedures. Agent should state: ''If you''re ever unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint by calling us or emailing [complaints email]. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights to independent dispute resolution.',1763115245187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypalxf00kjtd3rhcfou8f0','cmhypalx700jstd3rzrdbbzlw','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Subsidence postcode check not completed during initial quote preparation, causing customer inconvenience','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',407,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly throughout the product lifecycle. Agent must complete all underwriting checks BEFORE presenting quotes to customers. Implement a pre-quote checklist including: subsidence postcode verification, flood zone checks, claims history validation, and occupancy confirmation. This prevents customer disappointment and demonstrates professional service standards.',1763115245187);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypb2rt00l7td3ricimsps7','cmhypb2ro00kntd3r78ytjcdd','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide call recording disclosure or FCA regulatory status at the start of the call. While FCA authorization was mentioned later (timestamp 835), best practice requires this in the opening.','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty - Consumer Understanding), ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'FCA regulations require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at first contact. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear disclosure of call recording. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good afternoon, Pickle Insurance in partnership with Go Compare. We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality, training, and regulatory purposes. This is Rebecca, how can I help?'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with and that the call is recorded from the outset, supporting transparency and consumer protection.',1763115267018);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypb4c700lvtd3rk6losmvs','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty - Act in good faith)',0,'FCA regulations require transparency about call recording. Agent must state immediately after greeting: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being monitored and can object if they wish, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring informed consent.',1763115269048);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypb4c700lwtd3rcgrkpf5a','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','high','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided at first contact for new business sale','GDPR Article 13 / Data Protection Act 2018',0,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact when collecting personal data. Agent must state: ''We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website at [URL] or ask us to send it by post.'' This ensures customers understand their data rights before sharing sensitive personal and property information.',1763115269048);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypb4c700lxtd3r74pe8pr0','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off period when providing quote for new policy','ICOBS 7.1.4R',1208,'ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before contract conclusion. Agent must state: ''If you decide to purchase this policy, you have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is called your cooling-off period.'' This ensures customers know they can cancel without penalty if they''re not satisfied, promoting fair treatment and informed decisions.',1763115269048);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypb4c700lytd3rxizjo1kc','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights','DISP 1.2.1R / ICOBS 2.3.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to provide information about their complaints handling procedures. Agent must state: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint to us. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights to redress and independent review.',1763115269048);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypb4c700lztd3r8sgejhv0','cmhypb4c100lbtd3r0iyz9nju','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Price quoted without breakdown of premium, Insurance Premium Tax, and fees','ICOBS 6.1.5R / FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1162,'ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear information about price. Agent must break down: ''The total price is 175.88, which includes [X] premium, [X] Insurance Premium Tax at 12%, and [X] broker administration fee.'' This transparency helps customers understand what they''re paying for and compare policies fairly, meeting TCF outcomes.',1763115269048);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhypbe4400motd3r0b0wvf1o','cmhypbe3z00m3td3ry7u0hua5','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide explicit call recording disclosure or GDPR privacy notice at call opening for new business sale','GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',1,'GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with new customers. For new business sales calls, agent must state at opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes. Before we proceed, I need to inform you that we''ll collect and process your personal data to provide your insurance quote and policy. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, please visit our website at [URL] or ask us to send it to you.'' This ensures customers understand their data rights before sharing sensitive personal and financial information, and provides transparency about call recording.',1763115281716);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq7rqd00netd3r5l58ut23','cmhyq7rqa00n8td3r6gga97pj','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','No call recording available - potential breach of FCA record-keeping requirements and inability to verify compliance with any regulatory obligations','FCA SYSC 9.1.1R - Record Keeping Requirements',NULL,'FCA SYSC 9.1.1R requires firms to maintain adequate records of all customer interactions for regulatory purposes. Technical systems must be in place to ensure: 1) All calls are recorded from start to finish, 2) Recordings are stored securely and retrievably for minimum 3 years (5 years for MiFID business), 3) Quality assurance can verify compliance. IT department must investigate why this call was not recorded. This protects both customers (evidence of what was said) and the firm (regulatory compliance proof).',1763116792357);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq7xnz00o0td3r1n13df1u','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening','ICOBS 4.5.2R, FCA PRIN 11 (Relations with regulators)',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.2R and FCA principles require firms to inform customers that calls are being recorded. **What to say**: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This must be stated immediately after the greeting and before any business is conducted. **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded and can consent or object, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring evidential records are obtained lawfully.',1763116800047);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq7xnz00o1td3rdbeqmnv4','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization)','ICOBS 4.5.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.2R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status to customers at first contact. **What to say**: ''Pikl Insurance is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority'' or ''We''re FCA regulated.'' This should be included in the opening script. **Why it matters**: This disclosure ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and have access to regulatory protections including the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763116800047);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq7xnz00o2td3rcm7el1pe','cmhyq7xnu00nqtd3rfcwu1f14','high','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide GDPR privacy notice at call opening','GDPR Article 13, Data Protection Act 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires controllers to provide privacy information at the point of data collection. For new contacts, a full notice is required. **What to say**: ''We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website at [URL] or ask us to send it by post.'' For existing customers or renewals, an abbreviated notice is acceptable. **Why it matters**: This ensures customers understand how their personal data will be used and their rights under data protection law before they share sensitive information.',1763116800047);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq82f300oktd3rwgw5qp8h','cmhyq82f000o8td3rnyg3gqll','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, firm regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R, GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA regulations require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Call recording must be disclosed before substantive conversation begins. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Jess at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is recorded, and how their data is being used - fundamental transparency requirements for customer protection.',1763116806208);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq85ov00p1td3rrkc594kc','cmhyq85os00ootd3r8iwgpwmj','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide firm identification, regulatory status, call recording disclosure, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy notice)',1,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status at the start of every call. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice when processing personal data. Call recording must be disclosed. **What to say**: ''This is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is being recorded, and how their data is being used - fundamental transparency requirements for customer protection.',1763116810448);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00pvtd3r4z7bjnwg','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent discussed policy details (no claims history, premium information) without conducting any DPA verification to confirm customer identity','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) and Article 32 - Data Protection Act 2018',2,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data including protection against unauthorized processing. Before accessing any policy information, agents must verify the caller''s identity. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only after successful verification should any policy data be discussed. **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized individuals from accessing sensitive personal and financial information, protecting customers from fraud and identity theft.',1763116828190);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00pwtd3ra37cdyb1','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any mandatory call opening disclosures: no firm identification, no FCA regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, no GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection. FCA PRIN 7 requires clear, fair communication. **What to say**: ''Good morning/afternoon, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy - you can find full details on our website or I can send you a copy.'' **Why it matters**: Customers have the right to know who they''re speaking with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded, and how their data is used. This builds trust and ensures transparency.',1763116828190);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00pxtd3r0j5l1lt8','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','high','tcfCompliance','Agent used dismissive and unprofessional language (''I don''t know what he''s going on about then'') which fails to treat the customer fairly and respectfully','FCA Principle 6 - Treating Customers Fairly (TCF)',13,'**What the law requires**: FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly at all stages of the relationship. This includes respectful, professional communication that addresses customer concerns seriously. **What to say**: ''Let me review your policy details to understand the premium changes and explain them clearly to you'' or ''I can see there''s been some confusion about your premium. Let me look into this for you and provide a clear explanation.'' **Why it matters**: Dismissive language undermines customer trust and suggests the firm is not taking customer concerns seriously, which is a core TCF failure. Customers deserve respectful treatment and clear explanations of their insurance arrangements.',1763116828190);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8jdp00pytd3r2jlxkqmx','cmhyq8jdm00pftd3rcr867vl1','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','No explanation provided about the premium calculation or factors affecting the price, leaving customer without clear understanding','ICOBS 6.1.5R - Information about price',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires clear information about the price payable. When customers query premium changes, agents should explain the factors affecting pricing. **What to say**: ''Your premium is calculated based on several factors including your claims history, the level of cover, any changes to risk factors, and market conditions. Although you''ve had no claims, [explain specific factors that affected this premium]. Let me break down the costs for you: the premium is X, Insurance Premium Tax is Y, and any fees are Z, giving a total of [total].'' **Why it matters**: Customers need to understand what they''re paying for and why prices change, enabling them to make informed decisions about their insurance.',1763116828190);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8m1l00qjtd3r8j5qi768','cmhyq8m1i00q4td3r1s1o8a2v','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Complete absence of mandatory call opening elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.2.1R (Senior Managers & Certification Regime), GDPR Article 13, FCA Handbook GEN 4 (Statutory status disclosure)',1,'FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status, GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection, and call recording must be disclosed. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded, and how their data is used - fundamental transparency requirements.',1763116831642);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8mgu00r6td3rybb4lqw5','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Call recording disclosure made at 36 seconds into the call, AFTER data protection verification (address and date of birth) had already been collected. Recording disclosure must be made at the very start of the call before any personal data is discussed.','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), GDPR Article 6 (Lawful basis for processing)',36,'FCA and GDPR require customers to be informed they are being recorded BEFORE the recording captures any personal data or policy discussion. Agent must state immediately after greeting: ''This call is being recorded for training, monitoring, and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures the customer has the opportunity to consent or object before their data is processed via recording. Without this, the firm risks processing personal data unlawfully and breaching customer trust.',1763116832190);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8mgu00r7td3rqim9zw9i','cmhyq8mgr00qntd3rbabobqk4','high','callOpeningCompliance','No firm identification or regulatory status disclosed. Agent did not state company name clearly or mention FCA authorization.','ICOBS 4.5.1R (Disclosure of status)',4,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires insurance intermediaries to disclose their name and regulatory status to customers. Agent must state at call opening: ''This is Rebecca calling from Pikl Insurance. We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This ensures customers know who they are dealing with and that the firm is properly regulated, protecting them from potential fraud and building confidence in the transaction.',1763116832190);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8oub00rttd3rcp0p73o8','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Complete absence of mandatory call opening elements: no firm identification, no regulatory status disclosure, no call recording notification, and no GDPR privacy notice','ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 6',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with data subjects. FCA PRIN 6 requires treating customers fairly with transparent communication. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or I can send it to you. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated and accountable, that their conversation is recorded, and that they understand their data rights before sharing personal information.',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8oub00rutd3rs2wekeok','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','No DPA verification conducted before discussing customer details, policy information, or accessing customer records','GDPR Article 5(1)(f), Data Protection Act 2018, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires data to be processed securely with protection against unauthorized access. Firms must verify identity before disclosing personal data to prevent data breaches. **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? Thank you. And can you confirm the first line of your address?'' Only after successful verification: ''Thank you, that''s all verified. Now, how can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized access to customer data, protects against fraud and identity theft, and ensures compliance with GDPR security requirements. Failure to verify can result in ICO enforcement action and significant fines.',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8oub00rvtd3r1210fsn0','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','high','professionalism','Highly unprofessional communication throughout call with casual language, unclear conversation flow, and no structured business approach','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), ICOBS 2.2.1R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: FCA PRIN 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly, which includes professional, clear communication. ICOBS 2.2.1R requires communications to be clear, fair and not misleading. **What to say**: Use structured, professional language: ''Thank you for calling Pikl Insurance. I can see you''re enquiring about a quote for a Coach House property. Let me review the details on our system. Can you tell me a bit more about the property and your insurance requirements?'' **Why it matters**: Professional communication builds customer trust, ensures clarity, reduces misunderstandings, and demonstrates the firm takes its regulatory obligations seriously. Casual or unclear communication can lead to customer detriment and TCF failures.',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8oub00rwtd3r0meb6asj','cmhyq8ou800rdtd3r79lhyjit','medium','tcfCompliance','No customer-centric approach demonstrated - transactional interaction with no needs assessment or attempt to ensure customer understanding','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',NULL,'**What the law requires**: FCA PRIN 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly throughout the customer journey, including understanding their needs and ensuring appropriate outcomes. **What to say**: ''I can see you have a quote for a Coach House property. Before we proceed, can I ask a few questions to make sure we have the right coverage for your needs? Is this your main residence or a second home? What level of cover are you looking for? Do you have any specific concerns or requirements?'' **Why it matters**: TCF requires firms to put customers at the heart of their business. Understanding needs ensures customers get appropriate products, prevents mis-selling, and demonstrates the firm is acting in the customer''s best interests.',1763116835267);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8qh600setd3ruu4gjhhp','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any required call opening elements: no firm identification with regulatory status, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13 (Privacy information)',1,'FCA and ICOBS require firms to identify themselves clearly, including regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to Jess at Pickle Insurance, we''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data for insurance purposes - you have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. For our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the call is recorded, and understand their data rights before sharing information.',1763116837387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8qh600sftd3rrsdlozqb','cmhyq8qgw00s0td3rng6ckkl4','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed customer''s policy data (quote reference and confirmed customer name ''Daniel'') without conducting DPA verification first - no identity check performed before accessing personal information','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018 Section 2, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R (Data security)',25,'GDPR Article 5 requires that personal data is processed securely and only disclosed to authorized individuals. Agent must verify identity BEFORE accessing any policy information. Required script: ''Before I can access your quote details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' [Verify against system] ''Thank you, that''s confirmed. Now let me pull up your quote.'' This protects customer data from unauthorized access and ensures compliance with data protection law. Accessing data without verification is a serious breach that could result in ICO enforcement action and FCA sanctions.',1763116837387);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8tr500sytd3re1pd7sm0','cmhyq8tr200sntd3r146nzk0e','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy data using policy number without conducting DPA verification (name + date of birth). This is a fundamental data protection breach.','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and Confidentiality, DPA 2018, FCA SYSC 3.2.20R',10,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security of personal data, including protection against unauthorised processing. Firms must verify caller identity before accessing any personal or policy data. **What to say**: ''Thank you for your policy number. Before I access your account, I need to verify your identity for data protection. Can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' Only after receiving and confirming these details should you access the policy. **Why it matters**: This prevents fraudsters from accessing customer data using stolen policy numbers, protecting customers from identity theft and unauthorised policy changes.',1763116841633);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8tr500sztd3rbi5c1an4','cmhyq8tr200sntd3r146nzk0e','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide mandatory call opening disclosures: no call recording notification, no regulatory status statement, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA SYSC 9.1.1R (call recording), ICOBS 2.2.2R (firm identification), GDPR Article 13 (privacy information)',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to notify customers of call recording, identify themselves with regulatory status, and provide privacy information. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: Call recording disclosure ensures customers know their conversation is monitored (consent requirement). Regulatory status helps customers verify they''re dealing with an authorized firm. Privacy notice fulfills transparency obligations so customers understand how their data is used.',1763116841633);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00tqtd3rtzl0pdwa','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to identify the firm name and regulatory status at call opening. Customer provided recording disclosure, but agent did not state company name or FCA authorization.','ICOBS 4.5.1R, FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients)',1,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to provide their name and regulatory status in communications with customers. Agent must state at call opening: ''You''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with and that the firm is properly regulated, providing essential consumer protection and confidence.',1763116846300);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00trtd3rlvrcxbt2','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain the basis for the 20 cancellation charge or reference policy terms and conditions','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications)',150,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear communication about charges. Agent must state: ''There''s a 20 cancellation charge as set out in your policy terms and conditions. This covers our administrative costs for processing the cancellation.'' This ensures transparency about fees and demonstrates TCF by explaining why charges apply, allowing customers to make informed decisions.',1763116846300);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8xcr00tstd3rlnnfzk92','cmhyq8xco00t5td3r7sfxf0o8','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS) rights at any point during the call','DISP 1.2 (Complaints handling procedures), ICOBS 4.5.2R',NULL,'DISP 1.2 requires firms to make customers aware of their right to complain. Agent must state: ''If you''re unhappy with any aspect of our service, you can make a complaint by calling our complaints team on [number] or emailing [address]. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights and how to escalate concerns, which is fundamental consumer protection.',1763116846300);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq8xtm00u6td3rxb5zn16a','cmhyq8xtj00twtd3rsosgbhn2','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization) at call opening, and call recording disclosure came after DPA verification rather than at the start','ICOBS 2.2.2R - Identification of the firm',10,'ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status before conducting business. Agent must state at call opening: ''Hello, this is Rebecca calling from Kidcol Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for training and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and their rights are protected from the outset of the conversation.',1763116846907);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq99ex00untd3rono74a2l','cmhyq99eu00uctd3rfkp6z6of','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide mandatory call opening disclosures: no call recording notification, no FCA regulatory status mentioned, and no GDPR privacy notice provided','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules require firms to identify themselves with regulatory status. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact (though abbreviated for existing customers). Call recording must be disclosed for transparency. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance, authorized and regulated by the FCA. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, and that their conversation is being recorded and their data protected. It builds trust and meets fundamental transparency requirements.',1763116861930);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9ck500vdtd3r3r5y0zbc','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening - mandatory regulatory requirement','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA rules and GDPR Article 13 require firms to inform customers that calls are recorded and provide transparency about data processing at first contact. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. How can I help?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers are aware their conversation is being recorded and can object if they wish, protecting their privacy rights and ensuring informed consent.',1763116866006);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9ck500vetd3rgl742xfk','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state firm''s regulatory status (FCA authorization) at call opening','ICOBS 2.2.2R (Disclosure of status)',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires insurance intermediaries to disclose their regulatory status before conducting insurance business. **What to say**: ''You''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance, authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' **Why it matters**: This disclosure ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm and have access to regulatory protections including the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763116866006);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9ck500vftd3ricgfsfly','cmhyq9cjv00uvtd3rx7f66kgg','high','dataProtectionCompliance','Incomplete DPA verification - agent only verified name and policy number, missing date of birth before accessing policy data','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Integrity and confidentiality), Data Protection Act 2018',20,'**What the law requires**: GDPR requires firms to verify identity before accessing personal data to prevent unauthorized disclosure. Minimum verification is name + date of birth or postcode. **What to say**: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your full name and date of birth please?'' (After receiving both) ''Thank you, and can you confirm your policy number?'' **Why it matters**: This prevents fraudsters from accessing customer policy information by simply knowing a name and policy number, protecting customers from identity theft and data breaches.',1763116866006);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9k0b00wqtd3ry7ple4p5','cmhyq9k0700w8td3rbuhlwfqw','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, firm regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with data subjects. FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. Call recording must be disclosed before recording begins. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data - for our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it.'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that their conversation is being recorded, and what rights they have over their personal data before sharing sensitive information.',1763116875660);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9k0b00wrtd3r19eohtq8','cmhyq9k0700w8td3rbuhlwfqw','medium','dataProtectionCompliance','No DPA verification conducted before discussing customer''s insurance needs and property details','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) - Integrity and confidentiality, UK GDPR',3,'**What the law requires**: While this was an inbound inquiry call (not accessing existing policy data), best practice requires basic identity confirmation before discussing detailed insurance needs. For new inquiries, minimal verification is acceptable. **What to say**: ''Before we discuss your insurance needs, can I just take your full name and confirm the postcode of the property you''re looking to insure?'' **Why it matters**: This establishes a basic audit trail and ensures the agent is speaking to the genuine customer, protecting both parties. Note: Full DPA verification (name + DOB) is mandatory only when accessing existing policy data.',1763116875660);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9on300xatd3rgdcmnx0z','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No call recording disclosure provided at call opening','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly) and GDPR Article 13',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 and FCA TCF principles require customers to be informed when calls are recorded. **What to say**: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes.'' This must be stated at the very start of the call, before any customer data is discussed. **Why it matters**: Customers have a right to know when their conversations are being recorded and stored. Failure to disclose recording is a data protection breach and undermines customer trust.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9on300xbtd3rsdr2d882','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','critical','callOpeningCompliance','No FCA regulatory status disclosed in call opening','ICOBS 4.5.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 4.5.2R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status to customers. **What to say**: ''You''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance. We are authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This should be included in the opening greeting. **Why it matters**: Customers need to know they''re dealing with a regulated firm, which provides them with regulatory protections including access to the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9on300xctd3ryn4vl0p8','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','high','callOpeningCompliance','No GDPR privacy notice provided at call opening','GDPR Article 13 and Data Protection Act 2018',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with customers. For existing customer service calls, a brief acknowledgment is acceptable. **What to say**: ''Your personal data is held in accordance with our privacy policy. You can find full details on our website or I can send you a copy.'' For new customers, a fuller notice is required covering data use, retention, and rights. **Why it matters**: Customers must understand how their personal data will be used, stored, and their rights to access or delete it before sharing sensitive information.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9on300xdtd3rganr97f6','cmhyq9on000wvtd3rwkw9mnmg','high','dataProtectionCompliance','Incomplete DPA verification before accessing customer quote details - only name and quote number collected, no DOB or postcode verification','GDPR Article 32 (Security of Processing) and Data Protection Act 2018',45,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 32 requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data, including verifying identity before accessing customer records. **What to say**: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your date of birth and postcode please?'' Verify at least two pieces of information (name + DOB, or name + postcode) before accessing policy details. **Why it matters**: Proper DPA verification prevents unauthorized access to customer data and protects against fraud. Accessing data without verification is a data security breach that could result in FCA enforcement action and ICO penalties.',1763116881663);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9p5m00xwtd3rt03pq7xo','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent accessed policy data and confirmed customer details without conducting DPA verification first. Agent looked up policy using reference number and confirmed ''main home and annex'' coverage before verifying customer identity.','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) and DPA 2018 - Data security principle',90,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. Before accessing any policy information, agents must verify the caller''s identity using at least two data points (typically name AND date of birth). **What to say**: ''Before I can access your policy details, I need to verify your identity for data protection purposes. Can I take your full name and date of birth please? Thank you. And can you confirm your postcode?'' Only after verification: ''Thank you, I can now access your policy.'' **Why it matters**: This prevents unauthorized individuals from accessing sensitive policy and personal information by impersonating customers, protecting both the customer and the firm from data breaches and fraud.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9p5m00xxtd3ryp79eznu','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure at call opening. No mention of ''this call is being recorded'' or similar statement.','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (SM&CR Conduct Rules) and GDPR Article 13',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires informing data subjects when their data (including voice recordings) is being collected. FCA conduct rules require transparency in all customer interactions. Agent must state at call opening: ''This call is being recorded for quality assurance and training purposes.'' **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: Customers have a legal right to know when they''re being recorded and can object. Failure to disclose recording may make the recording inadmissible as evidence and breaches customer trust and transparency requirements.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9p5m00xytd3r9s10pco3','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state the firm''s FCA regulatory status during call opening. No mention of ''authorized and regulated by the FCA'' or similar.','ICOBS 2.2.2R - Clear, fair and not misleading communications',0,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 2.2.2R requires firms to communicate their regulatory status clearly. While not required in every sentence, best practice for insurance brokers is to include FCA status in call openings to establish credibility and regulatory protection. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: Informing customers of FCA regulation assures them they''re dealing with a legitimate, regulated firm and have access to regulatory protections including the Financial Ombudsman Service and Financial Services Compensation Scheme.',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9p5m00xztd3r7w3bg2py','cmhyq9p5j00xjtd3rq4cnda62','high','mandatoryDisclosures','No mention of complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service rights during the call, even when customer expressed dissatisfaction with renewal pricing.','DISP 1.2.1R - Complaint handling procedures',NULL,'**What the law requires**: While not every service call requires full complaints disclosure, when a customer expresses dissatisfaction (as this customer did about pricing), best practice is to acknowledge their right to complain. DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to have accessible complaints procedures. **What to say**: When customer expresses concern: ''I understand your concern about the renewal price. We''ll do our best to find you a better quote today. If you''re not satisfied with the outcome, you''re welcome to make a formal complaint and we''ll investigate fully. You also have the right to refer matters to the Financial Ombudsman Service.'' **Why it matters**: Proactively informing customers of complaint rights demonstrates transparency, builds trust, and ensures customers know their regulatory protections. It''s a key element of Treating Customers Fairly (TCF).',1763116882330);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9se500yptd3rn7s4z1nb','cmhyq9se100y3td3re9cg1145','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Call recording disclosure was made after DPA verification and accessing customer records, rather than at the very beginning of the call','GDPR Article 13 - Transparency',40,'GDPR Article 13 requires transparent information about data processing at the point of collection. Agent must state call recording disclosure immediately after introduction, before any data verification: ''Good morning, this is Will from Pikl Insurance. Just to let you know, this call is being recorded for training and monitoring purposes. Now, for security purposes, may I take your date of birth and postcode please?'' This ensures customers are informed about recording before any personal data is discussed or verified, providing transparency from first contact.',1763116886525);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9vbt00zgtd3r99is5oi0','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, firm regulatory status, or any GDPR notice at call opening','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',1,'FCA rules and GDPR Article 13 require transparency at first contact. Agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to [name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with, that the call is recorded, and their data rights are acknowledged.',1763116890329);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9vbt00zhtd3rzfo9df1n','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS) rights at any point in the call','DISP 1.2.1R',NULL,'DISP 1.2.1R requires firms to provide complaints information to customers. Agent must state at call close: ''If you''re unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint by calling us on [number] or writing to our complaints team. We''ll investigate and respond within 8 weeks. If you''re not satisfied with our response, you can refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service free of charge.'' This ensures customers know their rights to redress and independent review.',1763116890329);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9vbt00zitd3r6depxi7z','cmhyq9vbp00yvtd3r7ff8cvje','medium','followUp','No documented follow-up action or clear next steps confirmed with customer regarding renewal decision','FCA PRIN 6 (Treating Customers Fairly)',330,'FCA Principle 6 requires firms to treat customers fairly throughout the relationship. Agent should state: ''Let me note on your file that you''re considering your options due to the house sale. Your renewal is due on [date]. Would you like me to call you back in [timeframe], or will you contact us when you''re ready to decide? I''ll also send you a confirmation email with the refund information we discussed.'' This ensures clear communication, documented actions, and supports informed customer decision-making.',1763116890329);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9xbp0107td3raylaw64v','cmhyq9xbm00zmtd3r00m0t63h','low','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not provide explicit GDPR acknowledgment at call opening, though this is acceptable for renewal calls where customer relationship exists','GDPR Article 13',19,'GDPR Article 13 requires privacy information at data collection, but for renewals where customer relationship exists, an abbreviated notice is acceptable. Agent should add: ''This is a renewal call, so we already have your details on file which we hold in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This acknowledges data processing without requiring full privacy notice, which is proportionate for existing customer relationships.',1763116892918);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyq9yq3010wtd3rmtvgpdy9','cmhyq9yq0010btd3r8ghly70q','medium','callOpeningCompliance','Call recording disclosure and company identification appear to be provided by customer rather than agent at call opening. Transcript shows customer stating ''calls are recorded for training and monitoring purposes'' at 00:15, which suggests roles may be reversed or transcript labeling is incorrect.','FCA PRIN 2A.5.3R, ICOBS 2.2.2R',15,'FCA PRIN 2A.5.3R requires firms to act with transparency toward customers. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear firm identification. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for training, monitoring and regulatory purposes.'' This ensures customers know who they''re speaking with and that the call is recorded, providing transparency and protecting both parties.',1763116894731);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqa7ym0125td3rvx1u63bg','cmhyqa7yj011ltd3r2elntsjl','low','callOpeningCompliance','Agent did not state FCA regulatory status at call opening, only mentioned it later during pre-contract disclosure','ICOBS 4.5.1R',5,'ICOBS 4.5.1R requires firms to disclose their regulatory status before conducting insurance business. Agent should state at call opening: ''This is Jess from Pickle Insurance, we''re authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.'' This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm from the outset, providing confidence and meeting transparency requirements.',1763116906702);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqacct012ttd3r3fw70uie','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any regulatory call opening - no call recording disclosure, no firm identification with regulatory status, and no GDPR privacy notice','FCA PRIN 2 (Skill, care and diligence), GDPR Article 13, ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: FCA Principle 2 requires firms to conduct business with due skill, care and diligence. GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact. ICOBS 2.2.2R requires clear firm identification. **What to say**: ''Good morning, you''re through to Lauren at Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. Your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy, which is available on our website.'' **Why it matters**: Customers have a legal right to know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded, and how their data is processed. This transparency is fundamental to consumer protection and builds trust.',1763116912397);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqacct012utd3rr8rqi5w5','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','critical','dataProtectionCompliance','Agent only asked for customer''s name without proper DPA verification (no DOB, postcode, or policy number) before discussing policy details and making recommendations','GDPR Article 5(1)(f) (Security of processing), Data Protection Act 2018',15,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 5(1)(f) requires appropriate security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access. This includes verifying identity before accessing customer records. **What to say**: ''For data protection purposes, can I take your full name and date of birth please? [Customer responds] Thank you. And can you confirm your postcode? [Customer responds] Perfect, I can see your policy here with Will''s quote.'' **Why it matters**: Without proper verification, you could be disclosing policy information to an unauthorized person (fraud risk) or accessing the wrong customer''s data. This protects both the customer and the firm from data breaches.',1763116912397);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqacct012vtd3rhd78w5sp','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explain 14-day cooling-off rights when directing customer to purchase new policy online','ICOBS 7.1.4R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights before or on conclusion of the contract. Even for online purchases, telephone agents must disclose this. **What to say**: ''When you purchase online, you''ll have 14 days from your policy start date to cancel for a full refund if you change your mind. This is your cooling-off period.'' **Why it matters**: Cooling-off rights are a fundamental consumer protection allowing customers to reconsider purchases without penalty. Customers cannot exercise rights they don''t know they have.',1763116912397);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqacct012wtd3ryl2pombz','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','high','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not provide complaints procedure or Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS) rights information','DISP 1.2.1R, ICOBS 6.1.5R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: DISP 1.2.1R and ICOBS 6.1.5R require firms to provide information about their complaints handling procedures. **What to say**: ''If you''re ever unhappy with our service, you can make a complaint by calling us or visiting our website. If we can''t resolve it, you have the right to refer it to the Financial Ombudsman Service, which is a free independent service.'' **Why it matters**: Customers must know how to complain and access independent redress. This is a key consumer protection ensuring firms are held accountable.',1763116912397);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqacct012xtd3rgrhji7s3','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not clarify whether quoted prices include Insurance Premium Tax (IPT) or provide price breakdown','ICOBS 6.1.9R',77,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.9R requires the price to be clearly disclosed, and best practice is to break down premium, IPT, and any fees separately. **What to say**: ''The annual option is 99.99 total, which includes Insurance Premium Tax. There are no additional fees.'' **Why it matters**: Price transparency allows customers to understand exactly what they''re paying for and compare products fairly. Hidden charges undermine trust and TCF principles.',1763116912397);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqacct012ytd3rad2fxw5w','cmhyqaccq0129td3rsakcoz3n','medium','salesProcessCompliance','Agent did not confirm that policy documentation would be provided or explain how customer would receive it','ICOBS 6.1.5R',NULL,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 6.1.5R requires customers to receive policy documentation in good time before or on conclusion of contract. **What to say**: ''Once you complete your purchase online, you''ll receive your policy documents by email immediately. Please read them carefully, especially the terms and conditions, and contact us if you have any questions.'' **Why it matters**: Policy documents contain crucial information about cover, exclusions, and obligations. Customers must know to expect them and read them to understand what they''ve purchased.',1763116912397);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqajaj013otd3rpqsl2a0o','cmhyqajag0132td3r1e1mwof2','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide any required call opening disclosures: no firm identification, no FCA authorization status mentioned, no call recording disclosure, and no GDPR notice (even abbreviated for renewal)','FCA PRIN 7 (Communications with clients), ICOBS 2.2.2R (Clear, fair and not misleading communications), GDPR Article 13',1,'FCA PRIN 7 and ICOBS 2.2.2R require clear identification of the firm and its regulatory status at first contact. GDPR Article 13 requires acknowledgment of data processing. For renewal calls, agent must state: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and training purposes. As this is a renewal, we already hold your details in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with, that the firm is regulated, that the call is recorded, and that their data is being processed lawfully. These disclosures protect customers by establishing the firm''s accountability and the customer''s rights from the outset.',1763116921388);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqaz87014etd3rksy4pktl','cmhyqaz84013std3rkl6g09ne','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide mandatory call opening disclosures. The customer (not the agent) stated the call recording notice and data protection information. Agent must provide firm identification, FCA authorization status, and call recording disclosure at the start of every call.','FCA PRIN 2A.5.1R (Consumer Duty), ICOBS 2.2.2R, GDPR Article 13',17,'ICOBS 2.2.2R and FCA regulations require firms to identify themselves and disclose call recording at call commencement. Agent must state at call opening: ''Good morning, you''re through to [Agent Name] at Pikl Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality assurance and regulatory purposes. For renewals, your data is held in accordance with our privacy policy.'' This ensures customers know who they''re dealing with and that the firm is regulated, providing essential consumer protection. The agent should NEVER rely on the customer to provide these disclosures.',1763116942039);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqb8xb0153td3r490royvs','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','critical','callOpeningCompliance','Agent failed to provide call recording disclosure, FCA regulatory status, or GDPR privacy notice at call opening','GDPR Article 13, FCA PRIN 2 (Due Skill, Care and Diligence), ICOBS 2.2.2R',0,'**What the law requires**: GDPR Article 13 requires a privacy notice at first contact with new data collection. FCA rules require firms to identify themselves and their regulatory status. Call recording must be disclosed before recording begins. **What to say**: ''Good morning, Euphrates Willett Pickle Insurance. We''re authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. This call is being recorded for quality and regulatory purposes. We collect and process your personal data to provide insurance services. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data - for our full privacy policy, visit our website or ask us to send it by post. How can I help you today?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers know they''re dealing with a regulated firm, understand their call is being recorded, and are informed of their data rights before sharing sensitive personal and financial information.',1763116954608);
INSERT INTO ComplianceIssue VALUES('cmhyqb8xb0154td3rpr0alhou','cmhyqb8x8014itd3rp2ndmgt9','medium','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent did not explicitly state the 14-day cooling-off period at the point of sale, only mentioning it in the lengthy regulatory script near the end','ICOBS 6.1.5R, ICOBS 7.1.4R',1952,'**What the law requires**: ICOBS 7.1.4R requires insurers to inform customers of their cancellation rights clearly and prominently before the contract is concluded. **What to say**: After agreeing the price and before taking payment, state: ''Before we proceed, I need to let you know you have a 14-day cooling-off period from today. That means if you change your mind for any reason, you can cancel within 14 days for a full refund, minus any days you''ve been covered. After 14 days, there''s a 30 cancellation fee. Are you happy to proceed?'' **Why it matters**: This ensures customers make informed decisions and know they can cancel without significant penalty if they''re not satisfied, supporting Treating Customers Fairly principles.',1763116954608);
