INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvbg00033j6gwjl52dwg','call_1763069243573_u6xbskp','new_business_sales',7.679999999999998828,8.142857142857142349,6.599999999999999645,'Agent demonstrated excellent product knowledge and problem-solving skills, successfully identifying and resolving the online quote issue related to property type classification. However, critical compliance gaps exist: no call opening disclosures (recording notice, regulatory status, GDPR notice) and no cooling-off rights explained. The agent provided good customer service with clear explanations of flood cover options and maintained professionalism throughout.','Quote provided - customer to confirm purchase after consulting spouse',62014,1763114604172,1763114604172);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvbn000u3j6gm177ese6','call_1763069242348_296uft5','new_business_sales',7.299999999999998935,7.857142857142856762,6.0,'This was a new business sales follow-up call where the agent discussed payment options for a previously quoted policy. While the agent demonstrated good rapport, excellent follow-up skills, and proper data protection verification, there were critical compliance failures including no call opening disclosures (firm name, FCA status, call recording, GDPR notice), no cooling-off rights explained, and no complaints procedure provided. The agent handled the customer''s financial objection professionally and scheduled an appropriate callback.','Follow-up scheduled for 27th November - customer needs to wait for payday before proceeding with purchase',63553,1763114604180,1763114604180);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvbs001q3j6ghltpxh23','call_1763069241779_xxlhbvu','new_business_sales',7.719999999999998864,7.857142857142856762,7.400000000000000355,'Agent successfully completed a new business holiday home insurance sale with good product knowledge and customer service. However, a critical compliance breach occurred at call opening with no call recording disclosure, regulatory status, or GDPR notice provided. The agent recovered well with strong DPA verification, mandatory disclosures mid-call, and excellent TCF practices. Needs discovery could have been more thorough earlier to identify the buy-to-let nature upfront.','Sale completed - customer purchased holiday home/buy-to-let property insurance policy starting 7th, paid in full',55721,1763114604185,1763114604185);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvbx002d3j6glwkqw32k','call_1763069241196_6mb4f64','renewals',7.659999999999999253,7.857142857142856762,7.200000000000000177,'This renewal call was completed successfully with strong TCF compliance and good customer service. However, there was a critical compliance failure at call opening - the agent did not provide firm identification, FCA authorization status, call recording disclosure, or GDPR notice. The agent demonstrated good product knowledge, conducted proper DPA verification, provided comprehensive mandatory disclosures during the sales process, and respected customer choices throughout. Professional communication was generally good but had minor technical execution issues during data capture.','Renewal completed - customer renewed home insurance policy with payment taken in full',52040,1763114604190,1763114604190);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvc200343j6gm21e0kge','call_1763069240608_oil2kdb','mid_term_adjustment',6.724999999999999645,8.0,3.75,'Agent handled a mid-term adjustment for property changing from tenanted to unoccupied status. Demonstrated good product knowledge explaining unoccupancy options and provided transparent pricing. However, CRITICAL compliance failures: no call opening compliance (missing firm ID, FCA status, recording disclosure, GDPR notice) and accessed policy data before completing DPA verification, which is a fundamental GDPR breach.','MTA in progress - agent to call back with final premium for Level 2 unoccupancy cover after contacting insurer',57603,1763114604195,1763114604195);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvc6003w3j6g51fbag92','call_1763069245242_1kda914','mid_term_adjustment',7.625,8.0,6.75,'Agent handled a mid-term adjustment efficiently with strong product knowledge, thorough needs discovery, and comprehensive mid-call disclosures. However, a critical compliance breach occurred at call opening with no call recording disclosure, regulatory status, or GDPR acknowledgment. The agent demonstrated excellent customer service and completed all necessary underwriting questions and security checks appropriately.','MTA completed - policy amended from short-term let to long-term let, customer charged 79.33',56151,1763114604199,1763114604199);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvca004n3j6glcvdrqda','call_1763069244679_e1joagu','mid_term_adjustment',6.974999999999999645,7.714285714285714413,5.25,'Agent handled a mid-term cancellation with good rapport and appropriate DPA verification, but committed critical compliance breaches by completely omitting call opening requirements (company identification, call recording disclosure, regulatory status). The agent also failed to provide mandatory complaints procedure information. Product knowledge was adequate but showed uncertainty about cancellation fee processes.','Policy cancellation completed - no refund due to cancellation fee offsetting remaining premium',54451,1763114604203,1763114604203);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvce005g3j6gmw9vzplg','call_1763069242898_rdxi6v2','claims_inquiry',6.799999999999999823,8.0,4.0,'This was a claims inquiry call where the agent assisted with providing policy documentation for a malicious damage claim. While the agent demonstrated good rapport, product knowledge, and follow-up skills with clear timeframes, there were two critical compliance breaches: complete absence of call opening compliance elements (no firm identification, call recording disclosure, or GDPR notice) and failure to conduct DPA verification before accessing and discussing claim information. The agent handled the service request professionally and committed to resolving document retrieval challenges.','Document request acknowledged - agent committed to sending policy documents by end of day or next morning',52994,1763114604207,1763114604207);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvci00643j6glfgsve6e','call_1763069244124_6bwbyx6','general_inquiry',7.374999999999999111,7.857142857142856762,6.25,'This was a straightforward refund processing call for a cancelled policy. The agent handled the service request efficiently with good DPA verification and clear communication about refund timing. However, there was a critical compliance breach with no proper call opening (missing FCA regulatory disclosure, call recording notice, and firm identification), and the greeting was unprofessional. The agent demonstrated good customer service skills and TCF principles throughout the remainder of the call.','Refund processed - agent collected bank details and sent to accounts team for 142.99 refund',40033,1763114604211,1763114604211);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvcl006r3j6gvnjrps9m','call_1763069240023_w7t58p9','claims_inquiry',8.224999999999999645,8.0,8.75,'Professional B2B claims inquiry call between MGA claims handler and broker. Agent demonstrated excellent data protection compliance with proper verification, clear product knowledge regarding policy coverage hierarchy, and appropriate escalation of an unclear claim. All regulatory requirements met with strong TCF principles applied throughout.','Inquiry resolved - agent to escalate unclear claim to senior colleague (Mark) and review at renewal',32797,1763114604214,1763114604214);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvcp00743j6gimllh6uy','call_1763069122411_afj2az4','new_business_sales',6.700000000000000177,7.428571428571428826,5.0,'New business sales call for holiday let insurance where agent demonstrated good rapport, needs discovery, and product knowledge but had critical compliance failures. Agent failed to provide proper call opening disclosures (no firm ID, recording notice, or GDPR notice), collected personal data before DPA verification (serious breach), and missed mandatory disclosures including cooling-off rights and price breakdown. Customer declined due to cheaper quote elsewhere (403 vs 750), and agent''s objection handling was weak. No sale completed.','No sale - customer declined due to price, had cheaper quote elsewhere at 403',78685,1763114604217,1763114604217);
INSERT INTO Analysis VALUES('cmhyowvct00823j6gdt2yk1hz','call_1763069121801_8456pk3','renewals',8.0,8.0,8.0,'Renewal call handled professionally with strong needs discovery, product knowledge, and TCF compliance. Agent identified and corrected policy discrepancies, provided creative solutions for future guest cover, and delivered comprehensive regulatory disclosures. Critical gap: missing call recording disclosure at opening. Overall, competent renewal processing with good customer service.','Renewal completed - customer renewed buildings, contents, and guest cover (annex only) with new insurer Aviva at reduced premium',60171,1763114604221,1763114604221);
